    소녀 "\"So now, where should we go?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:93
translate english chapter3_0f854cb1:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀는 다시 걸음을 한 발짝 내디디고서는, 아주 약간 높아진 톤으로 내게 말을 건넸다."
    voice ""
    "Taking a step forward again, the girl spoke to me in a slightly raised tone."

# game/chapter3.rpy:95
translate english chapter3_1902dc05:

    # "어쩌다 보니 제법 무거워져 버린 분위기를 풀고자 하는 소녀 나름대로의 노력이었으리라."
    "It must have been the girl's own effort to lighten the atmosphere that had somehow become quite heavy."

# game/chapter3.rpy:97
translate english chapter3_15ba224b:

    # 나 "“마지막으로 근처에 있는 주택가 쪽으로 가 보려고. 그쪽에서도 1년 전에 화재가 일어났거든.”"
    나 "\"I was thinking of going to a nearby residential area last. There was also a fire there a year ago.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:99
translate english chapter3_f497c104:

    # voice "voices/gc10.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“여기서 그리 먼 곳은 아닌가 보네요.”"
    voice "voices/gc10.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It seems it's not far from here.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:102
translate english chapter3_d28cbfbd:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“으응, 걸어서 30분 정도면 도착할 거야.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Um, it should take about 30 minutes on foot.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:105
translate english chapter3_f94eb1e4:

    # "아마도 오늘의 마지막 경유지가 될 장소로 향하는 길."
    "Heading towards what would likely be our last stop for the day."

# game/chapter3.rpy:106
translate english chapter3_b9551de1:

    # "그곳에서 일어날 일이 긍정적인 쪽이었으면 좋겠다고 생각하다 말고, 묘한 딜레마에 빠진다."
    "I found myself caught in a strange dilemma, hoping that what would happen there would be positive."

# game/chapter3.rpy:110
translate english chapter3_8d678abe:

    # "소녀가 이야기했던 것처럼, 왠지 쌀쌀한 기분이었다."
    "As the girl had mentioned, I felt an inexplicable chill."

# game/chapter3.rpy:115
translate english chapter3_bcc2caaa:

    # "주택가에 도착하자, 늘어져 있는 3층 정도 높이의 맨션과 허름해 보이는 주택들이 눈에 들어왔다."
    "Upon arriving at the residential area, my eyes were drawn to the sprawling three-story mansions and dilapidated houses."

# game/chapter3.rpy:116
translate english chapter3_2dcfa736:

    # "듬성듬성 오가는 사람들이 간혹 혼잣말처럼 이야기를 중얼대는 나를 힐긋 바라보긴 했지만, 그뿐이었다."
    "The scattered passersby occasionally glanced at me as I mumbled to myself, but that was all."

# game/chapter3.rpy:117
translate english chapter3_1e55b427:

    # "지도에 나타난 대로 세 번째 모퉁이에 접어들자, 좁다란 골목이 나타났다."
    "As indicated on the map, when we turned the third corner, a narrow alleyway appeared."

# game/chapter3.rpy:118
translate english chapter3_08746cdd:

    # "더 이상의 자세한 정보가 지도에 나타나 있지는 않았지만, 화재가 일어났던 장소를 찾는 건 그리 어려운 일이 아니었다."
    "While no further details were shown on the map, finding the site of the fire wasn't particularly difficult."

# game/chapter3.rpy:119
translate english chapter3_60821b9a:

    # "두어 블록 정도를 더 걸어가서, 나와 소녀는 화재가 일어났던 것으로 추정되는 장소에 다다를 수 있었다."
    "After walking a few more blocks, the girl and I were able to reach what we presumed to be the site of the fire."

# game/chapter3.rpy:121
translate english chapter3_dbed4a05:

    # 나 "“사람이 사는 것 같아 보이진 않지?”"
    나 "\"It doesn't look like anyone lives here, does it?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:123
translate english chapter3_3607383b:

    # "여전히 불에 그을린 흔적이 남아있는 벽면을 힐긋 바라보며, 나는 소녀에게 물었다."
    "While observing the wall still bearing the scars of fire, I asked the girl."

# game/chapter3.rpy:125
translate english chapter3_e0472636:

    # voice "voices/gc11.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그러게요.”"
    voice "voices/gc11.ogg"
    소녀 "\"That's true.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:130
translate english chapter3_ae925b64:

    # voice ""
    # "화재의 흔적은 생각했던 것보다 길게 이어져, 서너 가구의 벽면을 검게 칠해 놓고 있었다."
    voice ""
    "The traces of the fire extended longer than I had thought, blackening the walls of several houses."

# game/chapter3.rpy:132
translate english chapter3_23cd5183:

    # "화재가 일어난 곳이 한 군데였던 것만은 아닌 모양이었다."
    "It seemed that the fire hadn't started in just one place."

# game/chapter3.rpy:134
translate english chapter3_3e0e9f64:

    # 나 "“불이 제법 크게 번졌나 봐.”"
    나 "\"Looks like the fire spread quite a bit.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:136
translate english chapter3_224cf543:

    # "불길의 흔적이 이어진 곳을 찬찬히 바라보며, 익숙한 장소를 찾아온 것처럼 발걸음을 옮겼다."
    "I moved my gaze slowly over the places where the signs of flames continued, moving as if I had returned to a familiar place."

# game/chapter3.rpy:137
translate english chapter3_16fecc88:

    # "실제로는 단 한 번도 와 본 적 없는 낯선 곳임에도 불구하고, 어딘가 정겨운 구석이 느껴지는 모습이었다."
    "Despite it being a strange place I had never visited before, there was a sense of familiarity about it."

# game/chapter3.rpy:138
translate english chapter3_0666619c:

    # "어쩌면 그 정겨운 것처럼 느껴지는 감각을, 나는 그리워하고 있었는지도 모르겠다."
    "Perhaps I was longing for that sense of familiarity."

# game/chapter3.rpy:142
translate english chapter3_ab561af0:

    # 나 "“여기까지 번졌었나 보네.”"
    나 "\"It seems it spread up to here.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:144
translate english chapter3_c63df49a:

    # "나와 소녀의 발걸음이 짙은 회색의 상처가 끊어진 지점에서 멈춰 섰다."
    "The girl and I stopped where the deep grey scars of the fire ended."

# game/chapter3.rpy:145
translate english chapter3_94435433:

    # "건너편 집에서는 주말 오후를 함께 보내는 가족 간의 행복한 이야기 소리가 들려오고 있었다."
    "From a house across the street, we could hear the happy chatter of a family spending their weekend afternoon together."

# game/chapter3.rpy:147
translate english chapter3_acf31ba4:

    # "불에 타 껍데기만 남은 이쪽의 풍경과는 상반된 것처럼 느껴지는 화기애애한 분위기였다."
    "In stark contrast to our surroundings that were left charred by the fire, there was a warm and friendly atmosphere."

# game/chapter3.rpy:148
translate english chapter3_495c00e1:

    # "나는 다시금 시선을 무채색의 공간 속으로 옮겼다."
    "I shifted my gaze back into the monochrome space."

# game/chapter3.rpy:150
translate english chapter3_bda82192:

    # 나 "“사람이 살고 있는 것 같진 않지만…… 그래도 내가 들어가면 좀 수상해 보이겠지?”"
    나 "\"It doesn't look like anyone's living here... but it would look suspicious if I went in, right?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:152
translate english chapter3_e73f26df:

    # voice "voices/gc12.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“저 혼자서도 괜찮아요.”"
    voice "voices/gc12.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I'll be fine on my own.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:154
translate english chapter3_c63441d8:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그럼, 여기서 기다리고 있을게.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Alright, I'll wait here then.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:162
translate english chapter3_01a4ea32:

    # "나는 소녀가 반쯤 폐가처럼 변한 집으로 들어가는 것을 확인하고는, 슬며시 고개를 돌려 벽에 몸을 기대었다."
    "After confirming the girl entering the house that was halfway to becoming a ruin, I slowly turned my head and leaned against the wall."

# game/chapter3.rpy:164
translate english chapter3_a6469bee:

    # "무채색의 세계를 등진 나의 눈앞에는 온갖 색으로 덧칠된 세계가 펼쳐진다."
    "In front of my eyes that had turned away from the monochrome world, a world painted with all sorts of colors unfolded."

# game/chapter3.rpy:165
translate english chapter3_a610636f:

    # "아직 해가 지기엔 조금 이른 시간의 하늘은 물감을 풀어놓은 듯한 푸른색으로 칠해져 있었고, 도란도란 이야기 소리가 들려오는 맞은편의 가정집에서는 살갑기 그지없는 장밋빛 색이 새어 나오고 있었다."
    "The sky at a slightly early time for sunset was painted blue as if watercolors had been spread out, and from the house across the street where lively chatter could be heard, an endless warm pink color seeped out."

# game/chapter3.rpy:166
translate english chapter3_8b2f33ea:

    # "내가 그리워하던 감각이란 이런 것이었을까."
    "Could this have been the sensation I had been longing for?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:168
translate english chapter3_26f78543:

    # "가족."
    "Family."

# game/chapter3.rpy:169
translate english chapter3_7d31936d:

    # "가족이라는 단어가 나의 머릿속을 맴돌기 시작하자, 오래된 고민들이 하나둘씩 기다렸다는 듯 나의 앞에 모습을 드러냈다."
    "As the word 'family' began to circulate in my head, old worries began to reveal themselves one by one in front of me as if they had been waiting."

# game/chapter3.rpy:171
translate english chapter3_b1cc8f63:

    # 나 "‘엄마랑 아빠는 어떻게 됐으려나…….’"
    나 "'I wonder what happened to mom and dad...'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:173
translate english chapter3_851fcc06:

    # "잘 지내고 있을까?"
    "Are they doing well?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:174
translate english chapter3_39172550:

    # "아니, 어쩌면 ‘잘 지냈을까?’라고 묻는 것이 옳은 것일지도 모르겠다."
    "No, perhaps it would be more accurate to ask 'Have they been doing well?'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:175
translate english chapter3_00cf9476:

    # "불현듯 가게에서 보았던 노파의 얼굴이 다시 한번 떠올랐다."
    "Suddenly, the face of the old woman I saw in the store came to mind once again."

# game/chapter3.rpy:177
translate english chapter3_f351eaa5:

    # 나 "‘…… 잘 지낼 리가 없지.’"
    나 "'...They couldn't have been doing well.'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:183
translate english chapter3_07025c68:

    # "마치 꿈속에 들어있기라도 한듯, 나는 손을 펼쳐 손바닥을 빤히 바라보았다."
    "As if I was in a dream, I spread my hand and stared intently at my palm."

# game/chapter3.rpy:184
translate english chapter3_6346637c:

    # "나의 몸이 아니지만, 나는 나다."
    "It's not my body, but I am me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:185
translate english chapter3_b0445de2:

    # "나라고 자각할 수 있는, 틀림없는 ‘나’이다."
    "The unmistakable 'me' that can recognize myself as 'me'."

# game/chapter3.rpy:189
translate english chapter3_4779f5c5:

    # "그렇다면 원래의 나는 어떻게 된 걸까?"
    "Then what happened to the original me?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:190
translate english chapter3_837d6f22:

    # "정말로 빈 껍데기만 남게 된 걸까?"
    "Did I really become just an empty shell?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:191
translate english chapter3_4b92bd48:

    # "나는, 죽은 건가?"
    "Am I... dead?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:193
translate english chapter3_2a70c11b:

    # "하지만 나라고 자각하는 존재가 이렇게 멀쩡히 살아있는데?"
    "But how can an entity that recognizes itself as 'me' be so alive?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:195
translate english chapter3_1e270fb3:

    # 나 "“하아…….”"
    나 "'Sigh...'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:197
translate english chapter3_b1090ef5:

    # "플라나리아처럼 내 영혼이 두 쪽이 나 갈라진 게 아니라면, 껍데기만 남은 내 몸체는 분명 죽은 것이나 다름없겠지."
    "Unless my soul has split in two like a planarian, my body that's left as an empty shell must be as good as dead."

# game/chapter3.rpy:198
translate english chapter3_1cb09df5:

    # "한숨이 절로 새어 나왔다."
    "A sigh escaped from me involuntarily."

# game/chapter3.rpy:200
translate english chapter3_40c09318:

    # "걱정이 안 될래야 안 될 수가 없는 상황이었지만, 걱정한다고 해서 달라질 것도 없는 씁쓸한 상황이기도 했다."
    "It was a situation where I couldn't help but worry, yet worrying wouldn't change the bitter reality."

# game/chapter3.rpy:201
translate english chapter3_f4b745c6:

    # "나는 벽에 기대어 선 채, 오랜만에 가족과 있었던 일들을 어렴풋이 회상했다."
    "Leaning against the wall, I vaguely recalled the times I had spent with my family after a long time."

# game/chapter3.rpy:202
translate english chapter3_150fc2ab:

    # "군데군데 기억이 흐릿해진 곳이 있긴 했지만, 전체적으로 가족에 관한 기억은 다른 기억들에 비해 비교적 또렷이 남아있었다."
    "There were parts where my memory was blurred, but overall, my memories regarding my family remained relatively clear compared to others."

# game/chapter3.rpy:206
translate english chapter3_396673fa:

    # 나 "“…….”"
    나 "\"...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:208
translate english chapter3_fa82d3f6:

    # "미묘했다."
    "It was subtle."

# game/chapter3.rpy:209
translate english chapter3_b27c2dbc:

    # "기억 속에서 앵무새처럼 돌아가야 한다고 말하던 무언의 아우성이 흐릿하게 들려왔다."
    "From within my memories, I faintly heard the wordless outcry saying that I should go back like a parrot."

# game/chapter3.rpy:210
translate english chapter3_294b3b94:

    # "하지만 그 외침이 들려온 곳은 미묘하기 짝이 없게도, 흐릿해진 기억의 틈 사이에서였다."
    "But the place from where that cry came was subtly elusive, from between the blurred memories."

# game/chapter3.rpy:211
translate english chapter3_62158964:

    # "내가 기억하지 못하고 있는 내가 나를 부르는 것만 같은, 바보가 된 기분이었다."
    "It felt like I had become a fool, as if the me that I couldn't remember was calling out to me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:212
translate english chapter3_aab640ff:

    # "그리고 그 목소리는, 어째서인지 바로 나의 등 뒤에서 들려오고 있었다."
    "And that voice was coming from right behind me for some reason."

# game/chapter3.rpy:214
translate english chapter3_ff7165a9:

    # "목소리가 선을 그렸다."
    "The voice drew a line."

# game/chapter3.rpy:215
translate english chapter3_4ff9c27c:

    # "여태껏 희미한 점선으로밖에 그려지지 않던 목소리의 흐름이, 웬일인지 오늘따라 또렷한 직선을 이루고 있었다."
    "The flow of the voice, which had only been faintly drawn as a dotted line until now, was forming a clear straight line for some reason today."

# game/chapter3.rpy:219
translate english chapter3_f50c2633:

    # "마치, 누군가와 나를 이어주려는 것처럼……."
    "As if it was trying to connect someone and me..."

# game/chapter3.rpy:230
translate english chapter3_d5a382cb:

    # "기억 속의 나는 불길 속에서 왼손을 뻗어, 누군가의 손을 붙잡았다."
    "In the memory, I reached out my left hand in the flames and grabbed someone's hand."

# game/chapter3.rpy:231
translate english chapter3_2e8c4425:

    # "불길에 그을린 듯한 오래된 기억이, 어렴풋이 나를 스쳐 지나가는 듯했다."
    "An old memory, as if scorched by the flames, seemed to brush past me faintly."

# game/chapter3.rpy:233
translate english chapter3_af348e35:

    # 나 "“괜찮아?! 정신이 들어?!”"
    나 "'Are you okay?! Have you come to?!'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:235
translate english chapter3_fa7a516d:

    # "희미해지는 나의 목소리가 기억 속에서 점점 커지는 소방차의 사이렌 소리에 뒤섞인다."
    "My fading voice got mixed in with the increasingly loud siren sound of a fire truck in my memory."

# game/chapter3.rpy:237
translate english chapter3_b718546e:

    # "그런 일이 있었지."
    "There was such an incident."

# game/chapter3.rpy:238
translate english chapter3_b2bcdcce:

    # "그을린 벽을 바라보며, 나는 난데없이 떠오른 기억 하나를 멍하니 곱씹었다."
    "Looking at the scorched wall, I blankly chewed on a memory that suddenly popped up."

# game/chapter3.rpy:252
translate english chapter3_923db7fc:

    # voice "voices/gc13.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“뭘 그리 보고 있나요?”"
    voice "voices/gc13.ogg"
    소녀 "'What are you looking at so intently?'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:255
translate english chapter3_42d3ac6b:

    # voice ""
    # "나를 부르는 또렷한 목소리에 고개를 돌린다."
    voice ""
    "I turned my head at the clear voice calling for me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:257
translate english chapter3_d6ccdecf:

    # "그곳에는 분명히 그 자리에 존재해 나를 빤히 바라보는 소녀가 있었다."
    "There, unmistakably, was the girl who existed in that place, staring intently at me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:259
translate english chapter3_2d5cfe60:

    # 나 "“아, 아무것도 아냐. 그냥 옛날 생각하고 있었어.”"
    나 "\"Ah, it's nothing. I was just reminiscing about the past.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:261
translate english chapter3_48d0fb5b:

    # voice "voices/gc14.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그랬군요.”"
    voice "voices/gc14.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I see.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:264
translate english chapter3_1c970703:

    # voice ""
    # "나는 벽에 기대어 있던 자세를 고쳐 잡았다."
    voice ""
    "I corrected my posture that had been leaning against the wall."

# game/chapter3.rpy:267
translate english chapter3_2cc636f1:

    # 나 "“어때? 기억나는 건 있었어?”"
    나 "\"How about you? Did you remember anything?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:271
translate english chapter3_ad0602b2:

    # voice "voices/gc15.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“아뇨, 저기가 아니었나 봐요. 아무리 둘러봐도 죽음의 색은 보이지 않았어요.”"
    voice "voices/gc15.ogg"
    소녀 "\"No, it seems that wasn't the place. No matter how much I looked around, I couldn't see the color of death.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:274
translate english chapter3_3e8d3952:

    # voice ""
    # "그런 이야기와 함께 표정을 감추고 싶기라도 한 듯 뒤를 홱 돌아보는 소녀."
    voice ""
    "With that said, the girl turned around abruptly as if she wanted to hide her expression."

# game/chapter3.rpy:276
translate english chapter3_ab7277c8:

    # "죽음의 색이라."
    "'The color of death.'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:277
translate english chapter3_afa0baf3:

    # "주변을 아무리 훑어보아도 나는 발견할 수 없는 색이겠지만, 소녀의 말대로 그녀가 방금 둘러보고 나온 집에서는 아무런 색채도 느껴지지 않았다."
    "No matter how much I scanned the surroundings, it must be a color I couldn't find; but as the girl said, I felt no color at all from the house she had just looked around."

# game/chapter3.rpy:278
translate english chapter3_06ddbf1e:

    # "실처럼 이어진 목소리가 들려오긴 했지만, 소녀가 느꼈던 그 색채와는 전혀 다른 무언가였겠지."
    "'The voice linked like a thread did reach my ears but it must have been something entirely different from the color the girl felt."

# game/chapter3.rpy:279
translate english chapter3_2b717863:

    # "소녀가 바라본 그 색채가 궁금하긴 했지만, 애써 알고 싶지는 않았다."
    "Although I was curious about the color the girl saw, I didn't really want to know."

# game/chapter3.rpy:286
translate english chapter3_39f04aae:

    # voice "voices/gc16.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그럼, 저쪽으로 한 번 갔다 와볼게요.”"
    voice "voices/gc16.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Then, I'll go over there and take a look.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:293
translate english chapter3_088d0688:

    # voice ""
    # "불길의 흔적이 이어진 옆집으로 몇 걸음 정도 더 걸어가, 이번에도 인기척이 전혀 느껴지지 않는 집 안으로 들어가는 소녀의 뒷모습을 바라보았다."
    voice ""
    "I watched the girl's back as she walked a few steps further to the neighboring house connected by traces of a fire, and entered into a home where no signs of life could be felt."

# game/chapter3.rpy:295
translate english chapter3_bf90730d:

    # "천천히 무채색의 세계 속으로 사라지는 소녀의 뒷모습에서는, 묘하게 쌀쌀한 기운이 감돌았다."
    "From the slowly disappearing figure of the girl into the colorless world, a strangely chilly aura was swirling around."

# game/chapter3.rpy:296
translate english chapter3_a88528b0:

    # "반쯤 열려 있는 대문과 작동할 것 같아 보이지 않는 초인종을 위아래로 훑어보며, 나는 잠시 생각에 잠겼다."
    "Looking up and down at the half-open gate and the doorbell that didn't seem to work, I lost myself in thought for a moment."

# game/chapter3.rpy:297
translate english chapter3_1450b4ae:

    # "초인종 옆에는 잔뜩 그을려 글씨를 알아볼 수 없는 명패가 걸려 있었다."
    "Next to the doorbell hung a nameplate so scorched that one couldn't make out the writing."

# game/chapter3.rpy:301
translate english chapter3_f99649d4:

    # "혹시나 새까맣게 묻어있는 그을음을 손으로 지워내 보면 이름을 확인할 수 있지 않을까 하는 생각과 함께 명패로 손을 뻗으려는데, 옆에서 시선이 느껴졌다."
    "As I thought about wiping off the pitch-black scorch marks with my hand to see if I could verify a name, I felt someone's gaze from beside me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:303
translate english chapter3_396673fa_1:

    # 나 "“…….”"
    나 "\"...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:308
translate english chapter3_abbc0548:

    # "나를 이상하다는 듯 빤히 쳐다보는 한 여학생."
    "A female student was staring at me as if I was strange."

# game/chapter3.rpy:309
translate english chapter3_77062e61:

    # "교복 차림은 아니었지만, 아마 중학생 정도가 아니었을까 추측되는 키와 외모였다."
    "She wasn't in a school uniform but her height and appearance suggested she might be around middle school age."

# game/chapter3.rpy:310
translate english chapter3_a1d8df5a:

    # "이번에도 내 주변을 스쳐 지나가는 사람 중 한 명이겠거니 하고 생각하고는, 명패에 가져대려던 손을 내리곤 아무 일도 없었다는 듯 시선을 돌렸다."
    "Thinking she was just another person passing by me, I lowered my hand that had been reaching for the nameplate and shifted my gaze as if nothing had happened."

# game/chapter3.rpy:311
translate english chapter3_792af692:

    # "괜히 수상하게 보일 만한 일은 하지 않는 게 좋을 테니까."
    "It would be better not to do anything that might seem suspicious."

# game/chapter3.rpy:313
translate english chapter3_c1e56ef8:

    # voice "voices/c1.ogg"
    # who "“여기서 뭐 하는 거예요?”"
    voice "voices/c1.ogg"
    who "\"What are you doing here?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:316
translate english chapter3_8751f048:

    # voice ""
    # "아주 잠깐, 정적이 흐른다."
    voice ""
    "For a brief moment, silence ensued."

# game/chapter3.rpy:319
translate english chapter3_ab692cdb:

    # 나 "“응? 아무것도…….”"
    나 "\"Huh? Nothing...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:324
translate english chapter3_8bd8e14c:

    # voice "voices/c2.ogg"
    # who "“거짓말. 아까부터 지켜보고 있었다고요. 계속 혼잣말만 중얼거리고, 여기 무슨 볼일이라도 있어서 온 거예요?”"
    voice "voices/c2.ogg"
    who "\"You're lying. I've been watching you since earlier. You've been muttering to yourself. Did you come here because you have something to do?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:326
translate english chapter3_97c566de:

    # voice ""
    # "그 여자아이의 눈에 나는 이미 이상한 사람으로 낙인찍혀 있었던 모양이었다."
    voice ""
    "In the eyes of that girl, it seemed I was already branded as a peculiar person."

# game/chapter3.rpy:329
translate english chapter3_1227fdbc:

    # "해가 지지 않은 주택가의 골목길은 여전히 더웠다."
    "The alleyway of the residential area where the sun had not yet set was still hot."

# game/chapter3.rpy:330
translate english chapter3_19f85936:

    # "다시 말해, 나의 사고 회로를 날카롭게 만들 수 있는 환경이 아니라는 뜻이었다."
    "In other words, it was not an environment that could sharpen my thought process."

# game/chapter3.rpy:332
translate english chapter3_b501945a:

    # 나 "“아…… 그게. 실은, 예전에 여기 살던 여자애랑 같은 반 친구였거든.”"
    나 "\"Ah... well, actually I used to be classmates with a girl who lived here.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:334
translate english chapter3_75278cac:

    # "무의식적으로 여자아이의 시선을 마주 보는 것을 피하고선, 나는 그렇게 말했다."
    "Avoiding the girl's gaze unconsciously, I said so."

# game/chapter3.rpy:335
translate english chapter3_d973c175:

    # "결국 내가 택한 것은 아까 가게에서 급히 생각해냈던 거짓말을 재활용하는 쪽이었다."
    "In the end, what I chose was to recycle the lie I had hastily thought up at the store earlier."

# game/chapter3.rpy:340
translate english chapter3_b8800c1d:

    # voice "voices/c3.ogg"
    # who "“아하, 저쪽 집에 살던 언니 말하는 거죠?”"
    voice "voices/c3.ogg"
    who "\"Ah, you mean the sister who lived in that house over there?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:342
translate english chapter3_ef9d2df5:

    # voice ""
    # "의외로 그 여자아이의 얼굴에 서려 있던 ‘당신, 수상해요’라고 말하는 듯한 표정은 금세 반쯤 사그라들었다."
    voice ""
    "Surprisingly, the 'you're suspicious' expression that was frozen on the girl's face quickly softened by half."

# game/chapter3.rpy:344
translate english chapter3_56781845:

    # "다만, 그녀가 가리킨 곳은 내가 서 있던 집 앞이 아닌, 한 칸 떨어진 곳에 위치한 2층짜리 주택이었다."
    "However, the place she pointed to was not in front of the house where I was standing, but a two-story house located a block away."

# game/chapter3.rpy:346
translate english chapter3_3fd3451b:

    # 나 "“으, 으응. 맞아.”"
    나 "\"Uh, yeah. That's right.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:350
translate english chapter3_0138c967:

    # voice "voices/c4.ogg"
    # who "“그런데 왜 그쪽 주변을 서성이고 있던 거예요?”"
    voice "voices/c4.ogg"
    who "\"But why were you hanging around there?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:352
translate english chapter3_33ea8265:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“여기 들르는 건 오랜만이라서. 예전에 먼 학교로 전학을 간 바람에, 옛날 생각이 나서 둘러보고 있었어.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"It's been a while since I stopped by here. I was reminiscing about the old times because I had transferred to a faraway school back then.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:354
translate english chapter3_34ca4ea4:

    # voice "voices/c5.ogg"
    # who "“하긴…… 생각해보니까 여기에 수상한 사람이 올 리는 없겠네요.”"
    voice "voices/c5.ogg"
    who "\"Well... now that I think about it, it wouldn't make sense for any suspicious people to be here.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:357
translate english chapter3_67f82946:

    # voice ""
    # "여자아이는 나에게서 의심의 눈초리를 완전히 거둔 것처럼 보였다."
    voice ""
    "The girl seemed to have completely withdrawn her suspicious gaze from me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:362
translate english chapter3_8aa860f2:

    # voice "voices/c6.ogg"
    # who "“어디서 왔어요?”"
    voice "voices/c6.ogg"
    who "\"Where did you come from?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:364
translate english chapter3_f77e82e2:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“A구역에서 왔어.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"I came from A district.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:369
translate english chapter3_19ccc8e7:

    # voice "voices/c7.ogg"
    # who "“그렇게나 멀리요?”"
    voice "voices/c7.ogg"
    who "\"That far?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:372
translate english chapter3_faa4802d:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“뭐…… 어쩌다 보니.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Well... somehow ended up here.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:375
translate english chapter3_14f6a07b:

    # "A구역에서 왔다는 나의 말에, 나를 보는 소녀의 감상이 수상하다는 쪽에서 신기하다는 쪽으로 바뀐 듯했다."
    "Upon hearing that I came from A district, the girl's impression of me seemed to shift from suspicion to fascination."

# game/chapter3.rpy:376
translate english chapter3_37fbc7b9:

    # "휘둥그레진 그녀의 눈동자가 나를 향했다."
    "Her wide-open eyes were directed at me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:378
translate english chapter3_ec227bc2:

    # 나 "“그 여자애랑은 서로 아는 사이였어?”"
    나 "\"Did you know that girl?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:379
translate english chapter3_dcd0fa94:

    # voice "voices/c8.ogg"
    # who "“조금은요. 그냥 알고 지내던 언니였어요. 그쪽은요?”"
    voice "voices/c8.ogg"
    who "\"A little. She was just an older girl I knew. What about you?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:381
translate english chapter3_909b251c:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“나도 조금. 알고만 지내던 클래스메이트였어.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Same here. She was just a classmate I knew.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:383
translate english chapter3_3fb14a58:

    # voice "voices/c9.ogg"
    # who "“흐음…… 그래요?”"
    voice "voices/c9.ogg"
    who "\"Hmm... Is that so?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:385
translate english chapter3_e9333b68:

    # voice ""
    # "어딘가 믿기지 않는다는 표정을 지어 보이며, 소녀는 고개를 갸웃거렸다."
    voice ""
    "She tilted her head with a somewhat incredulous expression."

# game/chapter3.rpy:387
translate english chapter3_a440479a:

    # "약간은 부담스럽게 느껴지기도 하는 소녀의 눈빛에, 나는 살짝 시선을 틀어 마른침을 꿀꺽 삼켰다."
    "Feeling somewhat overwhelmed by the girl's gaze, I averted my eyes and swallowed my dry saliva."

# game/chapter3.rpy:388
translate english chapter3_f436e0bf:

    # "잠깐 침묵이 감돌았다."
    "A moment of silence ensued."

# game/chapter3.rpy:389
translate english chapter3_eddfc08c:

    # "옆을 힐긋 바라보았지만, 이 여자아이는 갈 생각도 없는지 여전히 나를 빤히 바라볼 뿐이었다."
    "I glanced to the side, but this girl showed no sign of leaving and continued to stare at me intently."

# game/chapter3.rpy:391
translate english chapter3_9200edd0:

    # 나 "“…… 그래서 말인데, 혹시 무슨 일이 있었는지 알 수 있을까?”"
    나 "\"...So anyway, would it be possible for you to tell me what happened?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:393
translate english chapter3_3e125ede:

    # voice "voices/c10.ogg"
    # who "“보다시피요. 큰불이 났었거든요.”"
    voice "voices/c10.ogg"
    who "\"As you can see. There was a big fire.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:396
translate english chapter3_8743b885:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“역시 그랬구나.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"I thought as much.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:399
translate english chapter3_9229a4bc:

    # "최대한 어색하지 않은 연기톤으로, 나는 혼잣말을 하듯 여자아이의 말에 대답했다."
    "In as natural a tone as possible, I responded to the girl's words as if talking to myself."

# game/chapter3.rpy:403
