    # 나 "“그 여자애는 어떻게 됐는지 알고 있어?”"
    나 "\"Do you know what happened to that girl?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:404
translate english chapter3_e95d6bc6:

    # voice "voices/c11.ogg"
    # who "“…… 미나 언니요?”"
    voice "voices/c11.ogg"
    who "\"... Mina unnie?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:409
translate english chapter3_b8b1f1ac:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“으응, 이제 여긴 안 사는 거 같아서.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Yeah, she doesn't seem to live here anymore.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:412
translate english chapter3_091b24ab:

    # voice "voices/c12.ogg"
    # who "“그 언니, 다른 곳으로 이사 갔어요.”"
    voice "voices/c12.ogg"
    who "\"She moved to another place.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:414
translate english chapter3_9e44daa6:

    # voice "" 
    # 나 "“…{w=1.3} 그렇구나.”"
    voice "" 
    나 "\"...{w=1.3} I see.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:417
translate english chapter3_058670a5:

    # "잠깐의 텀을 두고, 나는 그렇게 대답했다."
    "After a brief pause, I responded as such."

# game/chapter3.rpy:419
translate english chapter3_3841445f:

    # 나 "“그럼, 어디로 이사 갔는지도 혹시 알고 있어?”"
    나 "\"Then, do you happen to know where she moved to?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:420
translate english chapter3_83de1e2d:

    # voice "voices/c13.ogg"
    # who "“알고 있지만, 비밀이에요.”"
    voice "voices/c13.ogg"
    who "\"I know, but it's a secret.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:423
translate english chapter3_573041e1:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀는 거기까지 이야기하고선, 뒤로 한 발짝 발걸음을 물렸다."
    voice ""
    "With that, the girl took a step back and stopped talking."

# game/chapter3.rpy:426
translate english chapter3_47749bdc:

    # voice "voices/c14.ogg"
    # who "“전 바빠서 이만 가볼래요.”"
    voice "voices/c14.ogg"
    who "\"I'm busy, so I have to go now.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:429
translate english chapter3_e4d12475:

    # voice ""
    # "길 건너편으로 총총걸음을 하며 사라지는 여자아이에게, 나는 손을 흔들어 주었다."
    voice ""
    "As the girl disappeared across the street with quick steps, I waved at her."

# game/chapter3.rpy:431
translate english chapter3_281dfb33:

    # "그러곤 벽에 기대어, 저만치에서 모습을 감춘 소녀가 내게 마지막으로 건넸던 거짓말들을 곱씹어 보았다."
    "Leaning against the wall, I mulled over the lies that the girl had last told me before she disappeared into the distance."

# game/chapter3.rpy:437
translate english chapter3_2471d2bc:

    # "여자아이와 내가 주고받은 몇 마디의 거짓말."
    "The few exchanges of lies between the girl and me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:438
translate english chapter3_9637f5a9:

    # "하지만 그 거짓말들의 색은 완벽히 상반되어 있었다."
    "However, the colors of those lies were completely different."

# game/chapter3.rpy:440
translate english chapter3_32f591c2:

    # "나의 새까만 거짓말과는 달리, 방금 그 소녀는 분명 나와 미나라는 여학생이 각별한 사이였다고 착각한 나머지 새하얀 거짓말을 내뱉은 거겠지."
    "Unlike my dark lies, it seemed that the girl had just spat out a pure white lie out of her mistaken belief that Mina and I were in a special relationship."

# game/chapter3.rpy:441
translate english chapter3_bd26c741:

    # "그게 아니고서야 굳이 A구역이라는 먼 곳에서 와서는 이런 주택가를 기웃거리고 있을 리가 없을 테니까 말이다."
    "Otherwise, there's no reason for her to be lurking around this residential area all the way from a distant place called A district."

# game/chapter3.rpy:443
translate english chapter3_63d53343:

    # 나 "‘…… 다른 핑곗거리를 지어내야 하려나.’"
    나 "'... Maybe I need to come up with another excuse.'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:448
translate english chapter3_ef6240c0:

    # "아무래도 나를 죽은 사람과 알고 지냈던 사람이라고 얼버무리는 건, 나쁜 임시방편이었던 것 같다."
    "It seemed like a bad temporary solution to fumble around saying that I knew a dead person."

# game/chapter3.rpy:450
translate english chapter3_0f800cdf:

    # "문득 그런 생각이 들었다."
    "Suddenly such a thought occurred to me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:451
translate english chapter3_55fcbfe4:

    # "어쩌면 거짓말을 했던 건, 나 혼자뿐이었던 건 아닐까."
    "Perhaps, I was the only one who had lied."

# game/chapter3.rpy:452
translate english chapter3_2580b118:

    # "나는 잠시 흘러가는 구름을 바라보며 그 미나라는 여학생이 좋은 곳으로 이사 갔길 바라 주었다."
    "I gazed at the drifting clouds for a moment, wishing that this girl named Mina had moved to a better place."

# game/chapter3.rpy:453
translate english chapter3_fb9b6eed:

    # "짤막한 묵념이 끝나고, 마땅히 할 생각이 없어진 나는 유령 소녀가 돌아오기만을 기다렸다."
    "When my brief moment of silence ended and I found myself with nothing to do, I could only wait for the ghost girl to return."

# game/chapter3.rpy:460
translate english chapter3_b61e6454:

    # "시간은 어느새 20여 분을 훌쩍 넘겨, 혹시 안에서 무슨 일이 일어난 건 아닐까 하는 걱정이 들기 시작하는 참이었다."
    "In no time, over 20 minutes had passed and I began to worry if something had happened inside."

# game/chapter3.rpy:461
translate english chapter3_28cc9051:

    # "그 여자애의 말대로라면 유령 소녀가 이곳에서 얻을 수 있는 기억은 딱히 없을 텐데."
    "According to the girl's words, there wouldn't be any memories for the ghost girl to obtain from this place."

# game/chapter3.rpy:462
translate english chapter3_a86f4579:

    # "누가 봐도 수상쩍은 거동으로 근처에 지나가는 사람들을 살피며 집 안으로 들어가 봐야 하나 말아야 하나 고민하던 찰나."
    "As I was contemplating whether to enter the house or not, looking suspiciously at the people passing by."

# game/chapter3.rpy:464
translate english chapter3_9b4228e2:

    # "반쯤 열려 있던 문틈 사이로, 말 그대로 유령처럼 소녀가 소리 없이 모습을 드러냈다."
    "Suddenly, through the half-open door gap, the girl appeared soundlessly like a literal ghost."

# game/chapter3.rpy:468
translate english chapter3_902ffb09:

    # 나 "“생각보다 오래 걸렸네.”"
    나 "'You took longer than I thought.'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:470
translate english chapter3_6b5e5cb9:

    # "소녀는 말없이 고개를 끄덕였다."
    "The girl nodded silently in response."

# game/chapter3.rpy:472
translate english chapter3_ac1f6911:

    # "언뜻 보기엔 들어갔을 때와 별다른 점이 없어 보이는 소녀의 모습이었지만, 어째서인지 그런 소녀의 일면에서는 어렴풋이 공허함이라는 것이 느껴졌다."
    "At first glance, the girl looked no different than before she went in. However, for some reason, I could faintly sense a void in her demeanor."

# game/chapter3.rpy:473
translate english chapter3_820d25ec:

    # "기분 탓일까?"
    "Is it just my imagination?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:474
translate english chapter3_81acbf2a:

    # "나는 건너편에 있는 집을 가리키며, 소녀에게 말했다."
    "I pointed to the house across the street and spoke to the girl."

# game/chapter3.rpy:476
translate english chapter3_4fab0145:

    # 나 "“지나가던 사람한테 들었는데, 우리가 찾던 여학생 집은 저쪽이래.”"
    나 "\"I heard from a passerby that the house of the female student we're looking for is over there.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:478
translate english chapter3_bb03ac15:

    # "그러고는 그쪽을 향해 걸어가려는 나를, 옆에서 들려오는 소녀의 목소리가 붙잡았다."
    "As I was about to walk towards that direction, the girl's voice from my side held me back."

# game/chapter3.rpy:480
translate english chapter3_3dd70a79:

    # voice "voices/gc17.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“괜찮아요. 더 확인해 볼 거 없어요.”"
    voice "voices/gc17.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It's okay. There's no need to check further.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:483
translate english chapter3_65446774:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“어라, 정말? 그래도 돼?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Oh, really? Are you sure?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:486
translate english chapter3_7a9686f3:

    # voice "voices/gc18.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“네. 기억났어요. 무슨 일이 있었는지, 제가 왜 그런 기억을 갖고 있었는지.”"
    voice "voices/gc18.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Yes. I remembered what happened and why I had such a memory.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:489
translate english chapter3_2eeb0fcd:

    # voice ""
    # "어리둥절한 얼굴을 하고 있던 내게 소녀가 담담한 목소리로 말했다."
    voice ""
    "The girl said in a calm voice to me who was looking puzzled."

# game/chapter3.rpy:492
translate english chapter3_3673c8f9:

    # voice "voices/gc19.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“전 화재 때문에 죽은 게 아니었어요.”"
    voice "voices/gc19.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I didn't die because of the fire.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:499
translate english chapter3_2d2e3056:

    # "소녀의 말을 문자 그대로는 이해할 수 있었지만, 이야기의 맥락을 이해하기란 당연히 쉬운 일은 아니었다."
    "Although I could understand the girl's words literally, it was naturally not easy to understand the context of her story."

# game/chapter3.rpy:500
translate english chapter3_f5a0740b:

    # "분명 아까까지만 해도 소녀는 자신의 죽음이 화재와 관련되었을 거라 이야기하지 않았는가."
    "Just a while ago, hadn't she said that her death was related to a fire?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:501
translate english chapter3_1a2b7d48:

    # "어떻게 된 거냐는 말을 꺼내기도 전에 나의 손에 차가운 감촉이 닿는다."
    "Before I could even ask what happened, I felt a cold touch on my hand."

# game/chapter3.rpy:503
translate english chapter3_9b3cf6fd:

    # voice "voices/gc20.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“일단은 돌아가요. 가면서 이야기할 테니까요.”"
    voice "voices/gc20.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Let's go back for now. I'll tell you along the way.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:505
translate english chapter3_e246405f_1:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“아, 으응…….”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Ah, um...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:515
translate english chapter3_409a45ff:

    # "20여 분 동안 무슨 일이 있었는지, 소녀가 무엇을 기억해냈는지는 나로선 짐작조차 할 수 없었지만."
    "I couldn't even guess what had happened in the last twenty minutes or what the girl had remembered."

# game/chapter3.rpy:516
translate english chapter3_dcf8ab11:

    # "소녀의 바람대로 일단은 역으로 향하기로 했다."
    "I decided to head back to the station as the girl suggested."

# game/chapter3.rpy:517
translate english chapter3_3066f10b:

    # "역을 향해 걸어가는 동안 소녀는 아무런 말도 하지 않았다."
    "The girl didn't say a word as we walked towards the station."

# game/chapter3.rpy:518
translate english chapter3_2503d856:

    # "그렇다고 묵비권을 행사하는 건 아닌 것 같아 보였고, 아무래도 소녀에게는 생각을 정리할 시간이 필요한 모양이었다."
    "It didn't seem like she was exercising her right to silence; rather, she seemed to need time to organize her thoughts."

# game/chapter3.rpy:519
translate english chapter3_2e1e7069:

    # "정면을 바라보고 걸었다."
    "I walked straight ahead."

# game/chapter3.rpy:520
translate english chapter3_221ff0de:

    # "목소리도, 발걸음 소리도, 어떤 소리도 들려오지 않는 바람에 홀로 낯선 길을 걷는 것만 같은 기분이 들곤 했다."
    "I often felt as if I was walking alone on a strange path where no voices, footsteps, or any other sounds could be heard."

# game/chapter3.rpy:521
translate english chapter3_601abe8c:

    # "물론 그럴 때마다 손바닥에 느껴지는 서늘한 감촉이 소녀의 존재를 이야기해주었지만 말이다."
    "Of course, every time that happened, the cold sensation on my palm reminded me of the girl's presence."

# game/chapter3.rpy:525
translate english chapter3_88a1dfbf:

    # "역에 도착할 때까지도 소녀는 생각에 잠겨있는 듯해 보였다."
    "Even when we arrived at the station, the girl seemed lost in thought."

# game/chapter3.rpy:526
translate english chapter3_388841a8:

    # "소녀가 생각에 잠겨있을 때 입술을 깨무는 버릇이 있다는 걸 알게 된 것도 그때의 일이었다."
    "It was then that I noticed that she had a habit of biting her lip when she was deep in thought."

# game/chapter3.rpy:532
translate english chapter3_4035e1d1:

    # "역내 의자에 앉아 전철을 기다리고 있는데, 소녀의 목소리가 들려왔다."
    "As I sat on a bench in the station waiting for the subway, I heard the girl's voice."

# game/chapter3.rpy:534
translate english chapter3_57c54074:

    # voice "voices/gc21.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“죽음의 색이라는 거, 궁금하진 않아요?”"
    voice "voices/gc21.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Aren't you curious about the color of death?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:536
translate english chapter3_9c02c5ea:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“궁금하긴 한데, 굳이 애써서까지 알고 싶은 건 아냐.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"I am curious, but not so much that I'd go out of my way to find out.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:539
translate english chapter3_b919d47b:

    # voice "voices/gc22.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그런가요.”"
    voice "voices/gc22.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I see.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:542
translate english chapter3_41443c66:

    # voice ""
    # "솔직한 대답이었다."
    voice ""
    "It was an honest answer."

# game/chapter3.rpy:544
translate english chapter3_72831887:

    # "소녀도 그런 반응을 원했던 건지 가볍게 고개를 끄덕였다."
    "Perhaps the girl wanted such a response; she lightly nodded her head."

# game/chapter3.rpy:545
translate english chapter3_db5d3a4f:

    # "소녀는 고개를 슬며시 들어 주변을 둘러보더니, 이내 시선을 자신의 무릎 쪽으로 떨구었다."
    "The girl slowly lifted her head to look around and then quickly dropped her gaze to her knees."

# game/chapter3.rpy:546
translate english chapter3_15550665:

    # "이 시간대의 대합실에는 구역을 불문하고 오가는 사람들이 제법 많은 듯했다."
    "The waiting area at this time seemed to have quite a number of people passing through regardless of the zone."

# game/chapter3.rpy:547
translate english chapter3_a450e9d4:

    # "그리고 소녀는 그런 시선을 피하고자 하는 쪽이었다."
    "And it seemed like the girl was trying to avoid such gazes."

# game/chapter3.rpy:549
translate english chapter3_c3332eef:

    # voice "voices/gc23.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그나저나, 사람이 많네요.”"
    voice "voices/gc23.ogg"
    소녀 "\"There are so many people.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:551
translate english chapter3_b0fe6813:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“저녁 시간대니까.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"It's the evening rush hour.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:554
translate english chapter3_bcb39c9a:

    # "이번에도 솔직한 대답이었다."
    "This time too, it was a straightforward reply."

# game/chapter3.rpy:555
translate english chapter3_81318a3e:

    # "다만 아까의 대답과 다른 점이라면, ‘그러게’라고 대답해도 충분할 만한 이야기에 굳이 사족을 덧붙였다는 것 정도."
    "The only difference from the previous response was that I unnecessarily added a comment to a conversation that would have been sufficient with a simple 'I see.'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:561
translate english chapter3_a73d94f3:

    # "소녀가 내 쪽으로 고개를 돌렸다."
    "The girl turned her head towards me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:562
translate english chapter3_d91f84ec:

    # "소녀의 눈동자에 내가 투영된다."
    "I was reflected in the girl's eyes."

# game/chapter3.rpy:563
translate english chapter3_03cf3c22:

    # "나의 눈동자에도 그녀가 투영됐겠지."
    "And she must have been reflected in mine."

# game/chapter3.rpy:568
translate english chapter3_5101aad5:

    # "눈동자에 죽음이 투영된다는 건, 상상하기 힘든 그림이다."
    "Imagining death reflected in the eyes is a difficult picture to conjure."

# game/chapter3.rpy:572
translate english chapter3_649af7de:

    # voice "voices/gc24.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“여기서 저랑 이야기하다간 정말 이상한 사람으로 보이지 않을까요?”"
    voice "voices/gc24.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Won't I look really strange if I keep talking to you here?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:574
translate english chapter3_75e35eb3:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“괜찮아. 전화하는 척하면 돼.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"It's okay. Just pretend you're on the phone.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:577
translate english chapter3_42840289:

    # "나는 휴대용 태블릿을 꺼내 들고선 귓가에 갖다 대고는, “자, 됐지?”라며 소녀를 바라보았다."
    "I took out my portable tablet and held it to my ear, looking at the girl and saying, \"See? It's fine now.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:578
translate english chapter3_23c0ef6a:

    # "굳이 그럴 필요까진 없었지만, 소녀에게 정말 괜찮다는 것을 어필하고 싶었던 게 아니었을까 한다."
    "Although there was no real need for that, perhaps I wanted to assure the girl that it was truly okay."

# game/chapter3.rpy:582
translate english chapter3_76c4a930:

    # "소녀는 그런 나를 바라보며 잠깐이지만 가벼운 웃음을 지어 보였다."
    "The girl looked at me and showed a brief but light smile."

# game/chapter3.rpy:584
translate english chapter3_1729816d:

    # "그녀의 평상시 얼굴을 알고 있는 사람만이 간신히 눈치챌 수 있을 정도의 희미한 웃음기를 얼굴에 띤 채, 소녀는 끊겼던 이야기를 다시 이어나갔다."
    "With a faint smile on her face that only those who knew her usual expression could barely notice, the girl resumed the interrupted story."

# game/chapter3.rpy:588
translate english chapter3_310ed904:

    # voice "voices/gc25.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“무서운 색이었어요. 불길 속에서 덮쳐오는 죽음의 색은.”"
    voice "voices/gc25.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It was a terrifying color. The color of death that overwhelms from the flames.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:591
translate english chapter3_e246405f_2:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“아, 으응…….”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Ah, um...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:597
translate english chapter3_7e403c40:

    # voice "voices/gc26.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“제가 이렇게 이야기해도, 감 안 잡히겠죠?”"
    voice "voices/gc26.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Even if I talk like this, you wouldn't get it, would you?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:599
translate english chapter3_0c92bf83:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그렇긴 하지.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"That's true.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:601
translate english chapter3_29c1d205:

    # voice "voices/gc27.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“불길 속에서 죽음을 기다리는 거, 되게 끔찍한 일이었나 봐요.”"
    voice "voices/gc27.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Waiting for death in the flames must have been a horrifying experience.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:603
translate english chapter3_cf2a54d8:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“…… 그렇겠지.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"...I suppose so.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:606
translate english chapter3_cdf97d2b:

    # "소녀는 무릎을 위아래로 두어 번 정도 까닥이고는, 이야기를 계속했다."
    "The girl bobbed her knees a couple of times before continuing her story."

# game/chapter3.rpy:608
translate english chapter3_b79b7516:

    # voice "voices/gc28.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“30대 정도로 보이는 아저씨와 아주머니였어요. 품에는 아이를 안고 있었던 것 같은데, 그 아이는 살아서 구조가 된 모양이에요.”"
    voice "voices/gc28.ogg"
    소녀 "\"They were a man and woman who looked to be in their thirties. They seemed to be holding a child in their arms, and it appears that child was rescued alive.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:610
translate english chapter3_c64fcbfe:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“부모님이었나 보네. 그나저나 그 무서운 순간에 아이를 살릴 생각을 하다니, 나였으면…… 으음. 모르겠다.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"They must have been the parents. But to think of saving the child in such a terrifying moment... If it were me... Hmm. I don't know.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:612
translate english chapter3_b985b2e3:

    # voice "voices/gc29.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“흔히들 말하는 모성애나 부성애라는 걸까요.”"
    voice "voices/gc29.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Is that what they often call maternal or paternal love?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:614
translate english chapter3_b9889549:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“아마도. 스토르게(storge)라고 하던가.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Perhaps. They call it storge, don't they?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:619
translate english chapter3_936a8efd:

    # "언젠가 사랑에는 네 가지 종류가 있다는 이야기를 들어본 적이 있었다."
    "I once heard a tale that there are four types of love."

# game/chapter3.rpy:620
translate english chapter3_bb211468:

    # "그중에서도 가족애는 이성을 뛰어넘는 힘을 가지고 있다고, 그 이야기를 꺼낸 선생님이 힘주어 말했었지."
    "Among them, family love, they said, possesses a power that transcends rationality. The teacher who brought up the story emphasized this strongly."

# game/chapter3.rpy:621
translate english chapter3_096c4367:

    # "고개를 돌려 옆에 앉아있는 소녀를 바라보자, 그녀도 모성애나 부성애와 같은 단어를 마음속으로 곱씹고 있는 듯해 보였다."
    "Turning my head to look at the girl sitting next to me, it seemed as if she was also mulling over words like maternal and paternal love in her mind."

# game/chapter3.rpy:626
translate english chapter3_773300db:

    # "생각보다 이른 타이밍에 열차가 역에 도착한다는 안내방송이 흘러나왔다."
    "Sooner than expected, an announcement flowed out indicating the train's arrival at the station."

# game/chapter3.rpy:627
translate english chapter3_01145525:

    # "내가 먼저 의자에서 몸을 일으켰고, 소녀가 뒤따랐다."
    "I was the first to rise from my seat, followed by the girl."

# game/chapter3.rpy:628
translate english chapter3_e558db51:

    # "열차 안에는 좌석에 앉기는 무리 같아 보일 정도의 사람들이 들어차 있었다."
    "Inside the train were enough people to make finding a seat seem impossible."

# game/chapter3.rpy:630
translate english chapter3_6d99bc9a:

    # "열차가 선로에 멈춰 서고, 나와 소녀는 함께 안으로 발걸음을 내디뎠다."
    "The train came to a halt on the tracks and both the girl and I stepped inside."

# game/chapter3.rpy:631
translate english chapter3_c4a9021a:

    # "오는 길에는 좌석이 많이 남았었는데, 돌아가는 길은 입석이었다."
    "\"There were plenty of seats on the way here but now we're standing on our way back."

# game/chapter3.rpy:632
translate english chapter3_15f95b67:

    # "반대로 됐으면 좋았을걸, 하고 생각하며 차창 너머를 바라보았다."
    "\"It would have been better if it were the other way around,\" I thought as I looked out beyond the window."

# game/chapter3.rpy:633
translate english chapter3_6c45eb2f:

    # "아직은 푸르름을 잃지 않은 여름의 하늘이 슬슬 퇴장할 준비를 하고 있었다."
    "The summer sky which had not yet lost its blueness was slowly preparing to make its exit."

# game/chapter3.rpy:637
translate english chapter3_14c11ce3:

    # voice "voices/gc30.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“어쨌거나, 하던 이야기를 마저 하자면.”"
    voice "voices/gc30.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Anyway, to continue where we left off.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:640
translate english chapter3_c6188928:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀가 가볍게 심호흡을 했다."
    voice ""
    "The girl took a light deep breath."

# game/chapter3.rpy:642
translate english chapter3_ba127d6e:

    # "내쉬는 숨이 들이쉬는 숨보다 길게 들려서인지, 소녀의 호흡은 한숨처럼 들리기도 했다."
    "Perhaps because her exhale was longer than her inhale, the girl's breathing sounded almost like a sigh."

# game/chapter3.rpy:644
translate english chapter3_7c14a19c:

    # voice "voices/gc31.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그곳에서 죽음의 색을 보고 난 뒤로 기억이 조금씩 되돌아왔어요. 제가 화재 현장에서 죽지 못했다는 것도, 맨 처음 우리가 갔던 건물에서 떠올렸던 죽음의 색이 제 것이 아니라는 것도.”"
    voice "voices/gc31.ogg"
    소녀 "\"After seeing the color of death there, my memories began to return bit by bit. That I didn't die at the fire scene and that the color of death I first recalled in the building we visited wasn't mine.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:647
translate english chapter3_3f617317:

    # voice ""
    # "죽지 못했다니."
    voice ""
    "'Didn't die.'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:649
translate english chapter3_ffce3416:

    # "의도된 건지, 의도되지 않은 건지는 잘 모르겠지만."
    "I wasn't sure if it was intentional or not."

# game/chapter3.rpy:650
translate english chapter3_b2885dd7:

    # "여하튼 괴상한 단어 선택이라는 생각이 들지 않을 수가 없었다."
    "Anyway, I couldn't help but think it was a strange choice of words."

# game/chapter3.rpy:652
translate english chapter3_38f6f733:

    # 나 "“어떻게 된 일인 건지도 기억나?”"
    나 "\"Do you remember how it happened?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:656
translate english chapter3_09e5d5fe:

    # voice "voices/gc32_1.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“초등학교를 졸업하고 막 중학교에 들어갔을 때쯤이었을 거예요. 꽤 늦은 밤이었던 걸로 기억해요. 어쩌면 새벽이었을지도 모르겠고요.”"
    voice "voices/gc32_1.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It must have been around the time I graduated from elementary school and just entered middle school. I remember it was quite late at night. It might have even been dawn.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:658
translate english chapter3_df5219de:

    # voice "voices/gc32_2.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“여하튼, 시간은 정확하게 기억나지 않지만. 그날 집에 불이 났었어요.”"
    voice "voices/gc32_2.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Anyway, I don't remember the exact time but that day our house caught fire.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:660
translate english chapter3_81895913:

    # voice "voices/gc32_3.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“눈을 떴을 땐 이미 불이 제법 번져서, 숨을 쉴 때마다 기침만 연거푸 해댔던 것 같아요.”"
    voice "voices/gc32_3.ogg"
    소녀 "\"When I opened my eyes, the fire had already spread considerably and every time I breathed, it seemed like I coughed incessantly.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:662
translate english chapter3_7132d07e:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“무서웠겠네.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"That must have been terrifying.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:664
translate english chapter3_3e328bae:

    # voice "voices/gc33.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“…… 잘 모르겠어요. 어쩌면 너무 무서워서 그대로 다시 눈을 감았는지도 모르겠고요.”"
    voice "voices/gc33.ogg"
    소녀 "\"... I'm not sure. Maybe I was so scared that I just closed my eyes again.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:667
translate english chapter3_500dbe52:

    # voice ""
    # "차분한 목소리로 소녀가 말했다."
    voice ""
    "The girl spoke in a calm voice."

# game/chapter3.rpy:669
translate english chapter3_da26474e:

    # "나는 소녀의 이야기를 가만히 듣고 있기만 할 뿐이었다."
    "All I could do was quietly listen to the girl's story."

# game/chapter3.rpy:673
translate english chapter3_f5114451:

    # voice "voices/gc34.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“기억은 잘 나지 않지만, 누군가가 저를 구해줬던 것 같아요.”"
    voice "voices/gc34.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I don't remember well, but I think someone saved me.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:675
translate english chapter3_1255c6ee:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“다행히 소방관이 일찍 도착한 모양이네.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Fortunately, it seems the firefighters arrived quickly.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:677
translate english chapter3_45620e53:

    # voice "voices/gc35.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“안타깝게도 다른 가족들은 그렇지 못했지만요.”"
    voice "voices/gc35.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Sadly, the other family members were not so lucky.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:680
translate english chapter3_4957d899:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀가 말한 ‘안타깝게도’라는 단어가 감정을 싣지 못한 채 흩어져 사라진다."
    voice ""
    "The word 'sadly' she used dispersed without carrying any emotion."

# game/chapter3.rpy:682
translate english chapter3_29c0c950:

    # "무의식중에도 감정이 실린 나의 ‘다행히’라는 단어와는 상반된 느낌이었다."
    "It felt contrary to my word 'fortunately', which unconsciously carried emotion."

# game/chapter3.rpy:683
translate english chapter3_ef38c78e:

    # "무표정한 얼굴로 그런 이야기를 또박또박 건네는 소녀의 모습은, 마치 자신과는 아무런 상관없는 남의 이야기를 하는 것처럼 보이기도 했다."
    "The way the girl delivered such a story with an emotionless face seemed as if she was telling someone else's story that had nothing to do with her."

# game/chapter3.rpy:685
translate english chapter3_ab4cfb13:

    # voice "voices/gc36.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“화재로 죽은 건, 제가 아닌 제 가족이었어요. 제가 기억해 낸 죽음의 흔적은 제가 아닌 제 가족의 것이었던 거죠.”"
    voice "voices/gc36.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It wasn't me who died in the fire, it was my family. The traces of death I remembered were not mine but belonged to my family.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:687
translate english chapter3_8096c2d3:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그랬구나.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"I see.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:689
translate english chapter3_54d092ee:

    # voice "voices/gc37.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“제가 기억하는 건 여기까지예요.”"
    voice "voices/gc37.ogg"
    소녀 "\"That's all I remember.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:692
translate english chapter3_238634ed:

    # voice ""
    # "죽음을 이야기하는 것이 원래 이렇게나 무감각한 일이었을까."
    voice ""
    "Was talking about death always this emotionless?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:694
translate english chapter3_78f8dd8b:

    # "소녀와의 대화는 낮에 보았던 두 사람과 나누었던 대화와 완벽히 상반된 감정선을 이루고 있었다."
    "The conversation with the girl was forming a completely contrasting emotional line to the conversation I had with the two people during the day."

# game/chapter3.rpy:695
translate english chapter3_20cb8123:

    # "소녀는 차창 너머를 우두커니 바라보았다."
    "The girl stared blankly out of the car window."

# game/chapter3.rpy:699
translate english chapter3_69282bb3:

    # voice "voices/gc38.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“다시 원점이네요.”"
    voice "voices/gc38.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Back to square one.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:701
translate english chapter3_6db7d93e:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“꼭 그런 건 아냐. 확실히 아닌 곳을 네 군데씩이나 확인했잖아.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"It's not necessarily so. We've confirmed four places that are definitely not it.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:704
translate english chapter3_b1619eb4:

    # "애초에 이렇게나 쉽게 일이 끝날 거라고 생각하지는 않았다."
    "I didn't think from the beginning that things would end this easily."

# game/chapter3.rpy:705
translate english chapter3_93f2d504:

    # "일단 하루 정도 쉬고 난 뒤에, 다음에 찾아볼 곳을 찾아보자."
    "Let's rest for a day or so and then look for a place to visit next."

# game/chapter3.rpy:706
translate english chapter3_28634a6d:

    # "서두를 필요는 없을 거라 생각했다."
    "I thought there was no need to rush."

# game/chapter3.rpy:707
translate english chapter3_90134969:

    # "신경 쓰이는 건 오히려 다른 쪽의 문제였다."
    "What bothered me was actually a different problem."

# game/chapter3.rpy:708
translate english chapter3_6b04be4a:

    # "어색하게 고개를 돌려, 내 옆에 멍하니 서 있는 소녀를 힐긋힐긋 바라본다."
    "I awkwardly turn my head and gaze at the girl standing blankly by my side."

# game/chapter3.rpy:709
translate english chapter3_a2ebe616:

    # "누가 이 모습을 유심히 보게 된다면, 분명 이상하게 생각하겠지."
    "If anyone were to observe this scene closely, they would certainly find it strange."

# game/chapter3.rpy:711
translate english chapter3_f4fa6b41:

    # voice "voices/gc39.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“화재로 가족이 죽었다는 이야기를 이렇게 아무렇지도 않게 하다니. 저, 진짜 이상하죠?”"
    voice "voices/gc39.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Talking about a family dying in a fire so casually... I'm really strange, aren't I?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:714
translate english chapter3_03ef37ee:

    # voice ""
    # "나의 생각을 읽기라도 한듯, 소녀가 먼저 말을 꺼냈다."
    voice ""
    "As if reading my thoughts, the girl speaks first."

# game/chapter3.rpy:717
translate english chapter3_1e9b9f9c:

    # 나 "“아니, 그런 건 아닌데.”"
    나 "\"No, it's not like that.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:719
translate english chapter3_19d15f66:

    # "솔직하지 못한 대답이 소녀에게 전해진다."
    "My insincere response is conveyed to the girl."

# game/chapter3.rpy:720
translate english chapter3_37678b6c:

    # "그렇다고 말투에 솔직하지 못한 티가 묻어있던 것은 아니었다."
    "That being said, there was no hint of dishonesty in my tone."

# game/chapter3.rpy:722
translate english chapter3_c17155ce:

    # voice "voices/gc40.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“분명 죽음의 색에는 그 당시의 감정도 묻어있을 텐데 말이죠.”"
    voice "voices/gc40.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Surely the color of death would carry the emotions of that time.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:724
translate english chapter3_1fbf0303:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“…….”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:727
translate english chapter3_04c638bc:

    # voice "voices/gc41.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“하지만, 정말 아무것도 기억 안 나는걸요.”"
    voice "voices/gc41.ogg"
    소녀 "\"But I really don't remember anything.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:730
translate english chapter3_b3121501:

    # voice ""
    # "나만이 들을 수 있는 소녀의 목소리가 티 나게 떨렸다."
    voice ""
    "The voice of the girl audible only to me trembled visibly."

# game/chapter3.rpy:732
translate english chapter3_d0a35f47:

    # "두려워하는 걸까?"
    "Is she afraid?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:733
translate english chapter3_abd85583:

    # "기억하지 못하는 현실을?"
    "Of the reality she cannot remember?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:734
translate english chapter3_85fc73ce:

    # "그게 아니라면 그 현실을 기억하지 못하는 소녀 자신을?"
    "Or is it herself, the girl who cannot remember that reality?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:736
translate english chapter3_fa6e7f69:

    # voice "voices/gc42.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“이거 완전, 사람이 아니라 괴물이네요.”"
    voice "voices/gc42.ogg"
    소녀 "\"This is totally... not human, but a monster.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:739
translate english chapter3_82130915:

    # voice ""
    # "‘사라져야 할 이유가 하나 더 생긴 것 같아요’라고 말하는 듯한 얼굴로, 소녀가 나를 빤히 바라보았다."
    voice ""
    "With a face that seemed to say 'I guess there's one more reason to disappear', the girl stared at me intently."

# game/chapter3.rpy:741
translate english chapter3_83c034a6:

    # "그런 소녀의 얼굴을 마주 보고 있을 자신은 없어, 나는 어색하게 반대편으로 고개를 돌렸다."
    "Unable to face the girl's gaze, I awkwardly turned my head the other way."

# game/chapter3.rpy:742
translate english chapter3_15772b53:

    # "하늘에는 조금씩 붉은색 물감이 흩뿌려지고 있었다."
    "The sky was gradually being sprinkled with hues of red."

# game/chapter3.rpy:743
translate english chapter3_9b04741b:

    # "조용히 차창 너머의 풍경만을 바라보고 있자니, 여태껏 무뎌져 있던 감각이 조금씩 원래대로 되돌아오기 시작했다."
    "As I quietly gazed at the landscape beyond the car window, my senses which had been numb up till now started to gradually return."

# game/chapter3.rpy:744
translate english chapter3_9fd374f6:

    # "꼬박 몇 시간을 걸어서 그런가, 가장 먼저 다리 뒤쪽 근육이 욱신거렸다."
    "*Throb* After walking for several hours, the muscles in the back of my legs were the first to start aching."

# game/chapter3.rpy:748
translate english chapter3_5185b2c6:

    # "그 뒤로는 이것저것 찝찝한 감각들이 밀려 들어왔다."
    "Following that, various uncomfortable sensations began to flood in."

# game/chapter3.rpy:749
translate english chapter3_5250a1a2:

    # "등어리에 흘러내렸던 땀 자국이라든가, 신발에 들어온 모래 먼지라든가."
    "The sweat stains trickling down my back or the sand dust that had gotten into my shoes."

# game/chapter3.rpy:750
translate english chapter3_e63ff173:

    # "얼른 집에 도착해 씻고 이부자리에 눕고 싶다는 생각만이 머릿속을 가득 채웠다."
    "All I could think about was getting home quickly, taking a shower, and lying down on my bed."

# game/chapter3.rpy:757
translate english chapter3_1072a77c:

    # "집에 도착했을 땐 예상했던 대로 새까만 하늘을 볼 수 있었다."
    "When I arrived home, as expected, I could see the pitch-black sky."

# game/chapter3.rpy:758
translate english chapter3_04c5e013:

    # "저녁 8시."
    "8 PM."

# game/chapter3.rpy:759
translate english chapter3_7e141a6e:

    # "평소 같았다면 그대로 씻고 잠들기엔 이른 시간이겠지만, 오늘이라면 충분히 그럴 수 있을 것 같았다."
    "Under normal circumstances, it would be too early to simply take a shower and go to sleep at this time. But today, it felt entirely possible."

# game/chapter3.rpy:761
translate english chapter3_97913dfb:

    # "옆을 슬쩍 돌아보니, 소녀도 티는 내지 않으려 하고 있었지만 분명 얼굴에는 피곤한 기색이 역력해 보였다."
    "A quick glance to the side revealed that the girl was trying not to show it, but there was a clear sign of fatigue on her face."

# game/chapter3.rpy:771
translate english chapter3_510ec741:

    # "방에 들어가자마자 에어컨을 켰다."
    "As soon as I entered the room, I turned on the air conditioner."

# game/chapter3.rpy:772
translate english chapter3_d0be17d1:

    # "얼마 지나지 않아 거리에선 느낄 수 없었던 인공적인 찬 바람이 침실을 메웠다."
    "In no time at all, an artificial cool breeze filled the bedroom that couldn't be felt outside."

# game/chapter3.rpy:773
translate english chapter3_1f176bc6:

    # "침대에 앉아있는 소녀는 아까보다는 한층 편안해 보이는 얼굴을 하고 있었다."
    "The girl sitting on the bed looked somewhat more comfortable than before."

# game/chapter3.rpy:775
translate english chapter3_9db12631:

    # 나 "“그럼, 난 씻을게.”"
    나 "\"Well then, I'm going to take a shower.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:777
translate english chapter3_a8fcab72:

    # "가볍게 기지개를 켜며, 나는 욕실로 발걸음을 옮겼다."
    "Stretching lightly, I moved towards the bathroom."

# game/chapter3.rpy:778
translate english chapter3_af903fea:

    # "욕실을 먼저 소녀에게 양보하려는 생각을 하지 않은 건 아니었다."
    "It wasn't that I hadn't thought of letting the girl use the bathroom first."

# game/chapter3.rpy:780
translate english chapter3_a53f94c0:

    # "하지만 그래봤자 소녀로부터는 ‘그럴 필요 없어요’라는 짤막한 대답만이 돌아올 것이 뻔했기에, 빨리 샤워를 끝내는 편이 더 나을 거라는 결론을 내릴 수밖에 없었다."
    "However, it was clear that the only response I would get from the girl was a terse 'no need,' so I had no choice but to conclude that it would be better to finish the shower quickly."

# game/chapter3.rpy:781
translate english chapter3_60035b9c:

    # "따뜻한 물에 하루종일 혹사된 몸을 맡기고 있자니, 이대로 몇 시간이고 따뜻한 물을 뒤집어쓰고 있고 싶다는 생각이 나를 방해하긴 했지만."
    "Immersing my body, tormented all day, in warm water was so soothing that I wanted to stay under the shower for hours. But I resisted the temptation."

# game/chapter3.rpy:783
translate english chapter3_4df9208f:

    # "나는 평소보다 조금 이른 타이밍에 샤워기를 끄고는 욕실 밖으로 나왔다."
    "I turned off the shower a little earlier than usual and stepped out of the bathroom."

# game/chapter3.rpy:785
translate english chapter3_605ff73a:

    # "샤워를 끝내고 방으로 돌아오자, 소녀는 내가 욕실에 들어가기 전과 다름없는 자세로 허공을 응시하고 있었다."
    "When I returned to the room after my shower, the girl was staring into space in much the same position as before I had gone into the bathroom."

# game/chapter3.rpy:789
translate english chapter3_9dde6206:

    # "‘안 씻어?’라고 묻는 대신, 나는 이부자리에 누워 잠을 청하기로 했다."
    "Instead of asking 'Aren't you going to bathe?', I decided to lie down on the bed and try to sleep."

# game/chapter3.rpy:790
translate english chapter3_09dd50fe:

    # "내가 잠에 들면 소녀도 나를 조금은 덜 신경 쓰지 않을까 하는 생각에서였다."
    "I thought that if I fell asleep, the girl might pay less attention to me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:796
translate english chapter3_0863965c:

    # "소녀에게 등을 보인 채 잠들려 하는데, 어째서인지 잠이 잘 오지 않았다."
    "Trying to fall asleep with my back turned to the girl, for some reason sleep did not come easily."

# game/chapter3.rpy:797
translate english chapter3_b434a094:

    # "피곤함에 못 이겨 금세 꿈나라 행 열차를 탈 줄 알았는데."
    "I thought I would fall asleep in an instant due to exhaustion."

# game/chapter3.rpy:798
translate english chapter3_f90a65e2:

    # "하다못해 나는 억지로라도 잠에 들기 위해 양을 세기 시작했다."
    "In desperation, I started counting sheep in an attempt to force myself to sleep."

# game/chapter3.rpy:799
translate english chapter3_6ceaf897:

    # "양이 한 마리, 양이 두 마리……."
    "One sheep, two sheep..."

# game/chapter3.rpy:800
translate english chapter3_6a19e466:

    # "오늘따라 유난히 머릿속을 뛰노는 양들이 활기차 보였다."
    "The sheep running around in my head seemed unusually lively tonight."

# game/chapter3.rpy:804
translate english chapter3_65ae6f01:

    # voice "voices/gc43.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“…… 자요?”"
    voice "voices/gc43.ogg"
    소녀 "“...Are you asleep?”"

# game/chapter3.rpy:807
translate english chapter3_3a14071c:

    # voice ""
    # "머릿속에서 302번째 양을 세었을 때쯤, 소녀의 목소리가 들려왔다."
    voice ""
    "Around the time I was counting the 302nd sheep in my head, I heard the girl's voice."

# game/chapter3.rpy:810
translate english chapter3_8907214d:

    # voice "voices/gc44.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“정말 자는 거 맞죠?”"
    voice "voices/gc44.ogg"
    소녀 "“Are you really asleep?”"

# game/chapter3.rpy:813
translate english chapter3_b9d9877e:

    # voice ""
    # "적당한 크기의 목소리가 기분 좋게 귓가를 간질였다."
    voice ""
    "Her voice of moderate volume pleasantly tickled my ear."

# game/chapter3.rpy:815
translate english chapter3_5d269880:

    # "곧이어 나의 얼굴 위로 희미한 손길이 느껴졌다."
    "Soon after, I felt a faint touch on my face."

# game/chapter3.rpy:816
translate english chapter3_ec52915c:

    # "아마도 소녀가 나의 얼굴 위로 손을 흔들어 보이고 있는 모양이었다."
    "It seemed that the girl was waving her hand over my face."

# game/chapter3.rpy:817
translate english chapter3_1710dfb7:

    # "하마터면 미간을 움츠릴 뻔했지만, 다행히 그런 일은 없었다."
    "I almost furrowed my brow, but fortunately, that didn't happen."

# game/chapter3.rpy:819
translate english chapter3_12a3bce1:

    # "스르륵 소녀가 몸을 일으키는 소리가 들렸다."
    "I heard the sound of the girl getting up smoothly."

# game/chapter3.rpy:820
translate english chapter3_2b91c39f:

    # "눈을 감고 있었지만, 나로부터 조금 떨어진 곳에서 희미한 웃음소리를 찾을 수 있었다."
    "Even though my eyes were closed, I could detect a faint laughter from a little distance away from me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:821
translate english chapter3_347c44d4:

    # "살짝 굵은 숨소리 같은 소녀의 웃음소리를, 나는 어느새 정확히 집어낼 수 있는 모양이었다."
    "The slightly heavy breath-like laughter of the girl... I found myself able to pinpoint it accurately before I knew it."

# game/chapter3.rpy:823
translate english chapter3_e75fbffa:

    # voice "voices/gc45.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“자는 척하는 거라면, 고마워요.”"
    voice "voices/gc45.ogg"
    소녀 "“If you're pretending to be asleep, thank you.”"

# game/chapter3.rpy:826
translate english chapter3_f49db346:

    # voice ""
    # "그런 이야기가 내 귀에 닿은 뒤, 욕실 문이 여닫히는 소리가 들렸다."
    voice ""
    "After such a conversation reached my ears, I heard the sound of the bathroom door opening and closing."

# game/chapter3.rpy:828
translate english chapter3_6a502220:

    # "그리고 얼마 지나지 않아 샤워기에서 물줄기가 떨어지는 소리가 희미하게 들렸다."
    "And not long after, I faintly heard the sound of water falling from the showerhead."

# game/chapter3.rpy:830
translate english chapter3_232b2125:

    # "늦은 밤, 빗방울이 창문을 두드리는 것만 같은 익숙한 음색이었다."
    "Late at night, it was a familiar tone, much like raindrops tapping on the window."

# game/chapter3.rpy:832
translate english chapter3_d1b86ab7:

    # "300마리 언저리에서, 나는 양을 세는 것을 그만둘 수 있었다."
    "Around the count of the 300th sheep, I was able to stop counting."

# game/chapter3.rpy:833
translate english chapter3_368b3bd3:

    # "여지껏 양을 세고 있던 나는 우습게도 그 소리를 신호로 천천히 잠에 들었다."
    "I, who had been counting sheep until now, amusingly fell slowly asleep at that sound as a signal."

# game/chapter3.rpy:840
translate english chapter3_c15647c6:

    # "꿈을 꿨다."
    "I dreamed."

# game/chapter3.rpy:841
translate english chapter3_6232bbef:

    # "전에도 여러 번 꾼 적 있는, 익숙한 꿈이었다."
    "It was a familiar dream that I had had several times before."

# game/chapter3.rpy:845
translate english chapter3_1ec81d5e:

    # "거리를 걸었다."
    "I walked down the street."

# game/chapter3.rpy:846
translate english chapter3_89b24d53:

    # "사람이 없는 거리를, 혼자 걷고 있었다."
    "I was walking alone on a street with no people."

# game/chapter3.rpy:847
translate english chapter3_616216d7:

    # "이상하다는 생각은 전혀 들지 않았다."
    "I didn't find it strange at all."

# game/chapter3.rpy:848
translate english chapter3_09db1222:

    # "오히려 발걸음 소리가 들려올 때마다 느껴지는 고요함이, 더할 나위 없이 어울린다는 생각만이 들 뿐이었다."
    "Rather, every time I heard the sound of my footsteps, I only thought that the quietness felt perfectly fitting."

# game/chapter3.rpy:851
translate english chapter3_7cc141b6:

    # "그곳에는 아무도 존재하지 않았다."
    "There was no one there."

# game/chapter3.rpy:852
translate english chapter3_0fd9e78a:

    # "당연히 그래야 한다는 것처럼, 유미도, 현지도, 그리고 이름 모를 소녀도……."
    "As if it should naturally be so, neither Yumi, Hyeonji, nor the nameless girl were present..."

# game/chapter3.rpy:854
translate english chapter3_81340f99:

    # "나는 이유 모를 쓴웃음을 지었다."
    "I gave a bitter smile for no apparent reason."

# game/chapter3.rpy:860
translate english chapter3_231f240f:

    # "꿈에서 깬 나를 반긴 건 밝아오는 여명이 아닌 한밤중의 어둠이었다."
    "What greeted me upon waking from the dream was not the brightening dawn but the darkness of midnight."

# game/chapter3.rpy:861
translate english chapter3_bdcbc6b7:

    # "새벽 세 시."
    "Three in the morning."

# game/chapter3.rpy:862
translate english chapter3_31c59f74:

    # "아직 해가 뜨기엔 한참이 남은 시각이었다."
    "It was a time when there was still a long way to go before sunrise."

# game/chapter3.rpy:863
translate english chapter3_50223bc4:

    # "목이 텁텁했다."
    "My throat was parched."

# game/chapter3.rpy:867
translate english chapter3_c656a3cf:

    # "요즘 들어 목이 말라 깨는 경우가 잦아진 것 같은데."
    "Lately, it seemed like I've been waking up frequently due to a dry throat."

# game/chapter3.rpy:868
translate english chapter3_eb26d528:

    # "나는 조용히 몸을 일으켜 침대를 힐긋 바라보았다."
    "I quietly sat up and looked at the bed."

# game/chapter3.rpy:870
translate english chapter3_396673fa_2:

    # 나 "“…….”"
    나 "\"...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:872
translate english chapter3_4a7a7f13:

    # "이불을 뒤집어 쓰고 있는 소녀로부터는 희미한 숨소리만이 들려오고 있었다."
    "From the girl who was buried under the blanket, only a faint sound of breathing could be heard."

# game/chapter3.rpy:874
translate english chapter3_95831f07:

    # 나 "‘자고 있는 건가?’"
    나 "'Is she asleep?'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:876
translate english chapter3_114d27af:

    # "목은 말라붙어 있고, 소녀는 이불을 푹 뒤집어쓰고 있고."
    "My throat was parched, and the girl was deeply buried under the blanket."

# game/chapter3.rpy:877
translate english chapter3_8b9cd3c2:

    # "아무래도 에어컨 온도가 너무 낮았던 걸까."
    "Perhaps the air conditioning temperature was too low."

# game/chapter3.rpy:878
translate english chapter3_57ce9119:

    # "종종 목이 말라 밤중에 깼던 게 에어컨 때문일지도 모르겠다는 생각이 들었다."
    "I began to think that my frequent awakenings due to a dry throat might be because of the air conditioner."

# game/chapter3.rpy:879
translate english chapter3_656d2c17:

    # "실내 희망 온도를 살짝 올리고선 냉장고에서 물을 꺼내 마셨다."
    "After slightly raising the desired indoor temperature, I took out some water from the fridge and drank it."

# game/chapter3.rpy:880
translate english chapter3_5e6dbb37:

    # "다시 이부자리로 돌아와 잠을 청하려는데, 침대에서 들려오던 소녀의 숨소리가 미묘하게나마 거칠게 느껴졌다."
    "As I returned to my bed intending to sleep again, I noticed the girl's breathing from the bed seemed subtly rougher."

# game/chapter3.rpy:881
translate english chapter3_f0cab02d:

    # "나는 그대로 몸을 누이려다 말고, 침대 위에서 잠들어 있을 소녀에게 조심스레 다가가 보았다."
    "Instead of lying down as I was, I cautiously approached the girl sleeping on the bed."

# game/chapter3.rpy:883
translate english chapter3_96d9c3c9:

    # 나 "‘…… 어디 아픈가?’"
    나 "'...... Are you feeling unwell?'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:885
translate english chapter3_cc10809e:

    # "소녀의 가녀린 양손이 얇은 여름 이불을 꽉 붙든 채 떨리고 있었다."
    "The girl's slender hands were trembling as they tightly clung onto the thin summer blanket."

# game/chapter3.rpy:886
translate english chapter3_7effe37f:

    # "기분 탓일 거라 생각했던 거친 숨소리도, 확실히 불안정한 주기로 소녀의 입에서 새어나오고 있었다."
    "The ragged breathing that I thought was just my imagination was indeed leaking out from her mouth in an unstable rhythm."

# game/chapter3.rpy:887
translate english chapter3_7cee1373:

    # "너무 오랫동안 걸어 다녀서 몸살에 걸리기라도 한 걸까?"
    "Did she catch a cold from walking around for too long?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:888
translate english chapter3_7a558066:

    # "하지만 유령이 감기나 몸살에 걸린다니, 그런 이야기는 들어 본 적이 없는 것 같았다."
    "However, I couldn't recall ever hearing about a ghost catching a cold or falling ill."

# game/chapter3.rpy:889
translate english chapter3_c9ae4e81:

    # "그러다 문득, 지금의 상황이 언젠가 겪어 본 듯한 기분이 들었다."
    "Suddenly, I felt a sense of {font=fonts/Sarabun-Regular.ttf}déjà vu{/font} with the current situation."

# game/chapter3.rpy:891
translate english chapter3_5b04aee4:

    # 나 "“아, 맞다.”"
    나 "'Ah, that's right.'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:893
translate english chapter3_bec54a86:

    # "어딘가 익숙하다 했더니, 소녀가 이곳에 온 첫날 밤과 똑같은 상황이었다."
    "It felt familiar because it was the exact same situation as the girl's first night here."

# game/chapter3.rpy:894
translate english chapter3_ba99cfdf:

    # "그렇다면 소녀는 지금도 악몽을 꾸고 있는 건가?"
    "Could it be that the girl is having a nightmare again?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:895
translate english chapter3_8f060db6:

    # "이불을 살짝 내려 확인해 본 소녀의 안색은 어둠 속에서도 눈에 띌 정도로 창백해 보였다."
    "Even in the darkness, the girl's complexion was noticeably pale as I lightly pulled down the blanket to check on her."

# game/chapter3.rpy:896
translate english chapter3_2a308ef2:

    # "나는 냉장고에서 한 컵의 물을 더 따라와서는 소녀를 조심스럽게 깨워 보았다."
    "I fetched another cup of water from the fridge and carefully tried to wake her up."

# game/chapter3.rpy:900
translate english chapter3_7ff543aa:

    # 나 "“…… 괜찮아?”"
    나 "'...... Are you okay?'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:901
translate english chapter3_380b443f:

    # voice "voices/gc46.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“아…… 으으…… 우으으…….”"
    voice "voices/gc46.ogg"
    소녀 "'Ah... Ugh... Uuu...'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:904
translate english chapter3_cf2e513e:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀는 나의 조심스러운 부름에도 여전히 잠에서 깨어나지 못하고는 악몽 속을 헤맸다."
    voice ""
    "Despite my gentle call, the girl couldn't wake up from her sleep and continued to struggle in her nightmare."

# game/chapter3.rpy:906
translate english chapter3_7b52ffee:

    # "왜 진작 괜찮냐는 말을 건네지 못했던 걸까."
    "Why hadn't I asked her if she was okay sooner?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:910
translate english chapter3_437ede44:

    # "죽음의 색을 마주할 때마다 소녀로부터 느껴지던 흐릿한 위화감."
    "The vague unease I felt from the girl every time I faced the color of death."

# game/chapter3.rpy:914
translate english chapter3_de311fb7:

    # "여러 색이 뒤섞이면 새까매지는 것과는 달리, 감정이란 뒤섞이면 뒤섞일수록 빛처럼 새하얘져 버리는 걸까."
    "Unlike when various colors mix and turn pitch black, could emotions become brighter the more they mix, like light?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:915
translate english chapter3_5b34c986:

    # "다른 사람과 눈을 마주치지 않기 위해 항상 고개를 푹 숙인 채 길을 걸어 다니던 소녀가 애써 바라본 죽음의 색은 분명 내가 상상하기 힘든 감각들로 물들어 있었을 것이다."
    "The color of death that the girl tried hard to look at, always walking with her head hung low to avoid eye contact with others, must have been dyed with sensations hard for me to imagine."

# game/chapter3.rpy:918
translate english chapter3_7302e05f:

    # "금세 잠에서 깨어났던 그 날과는 달리, 피곤해서인지 소녀는 깊은 잠에 빠진 듯해 보였다."
    "Unlike the day she woke up quickly from sleep, perhaps due to fatigue, the girl seemed to be in a deep sleep."

# game/chapter3.rpy:919
translate english chapter3_88f5dd49:

    # "소녀를 흔들어 깨워야 하나, 아니면 그냥 이부자리로 돌아가는 수밖에 없으려나."
    "Should I shake the girl awake or do I have no choice but to return to my blanket?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:920
translate english chapter3_c57885cb:

    # "슬슬 몰려드는 새벽녘의 수면욕이 나의 선택을 재촉하고 있었다."
    "The gradually encroaching desire to sleep at dawn was hastening my decision."

# game/chapter3.rpy:921
translate english chapter3_467f1b86:

    # "소녀를 깨운다 해도, 다시 잠에 든 소녀가 악몽에 도로 빠져들지 말라는 법은 없을 테고."
    "Even if I wake the girl up, there's no guarantee that she won't fall back into a nightmare once she goes back to sleep."

# game/chapter3.rpy:922
translate english chapter3_bdeb58ba:

    # "어떡하지."
    "What should I do?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:923
translate english chapter3_b0bc3ef2:

    # "어떻게 해야 할까?"
    "What's the best course of action?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:925
translate english chapter3_d589787f:

    # "그 뒤로, 내가 어떤 의식의 흐름에서 그런 선택을 하게 된 건지는 잘 모르겠다."
    "Afterwards, I wasn't quite sure why I made such a choice in the flow of my consciousness."

# game/chapter3.rpy:926
translate english chapter3_a13a4c66:

    # "그저 그랬던 것 같다는 생각이 들었다."
    "I just felt like it had happened that way."

# game/chapter3.rpy:928
translate english chapter3_f8f0e923:

    # "소녀의 옆에 잠시 앉아, 그녀의 머리를 쓰다듬으며."
    "I sat next to the girl for a moment, stroking her hair."

# game/chapter3.rpy:929
translate english chapter3_0a01f6bf:

    # "나는 {color=#00ccff}지금은 존재하지 않을 오래된 팝송 하나{/color}를 조용히 흥얼댔다."
    "I quietly hummed an old pop song that {color=#00ccff}doesn't exist now{/color}."

# game/chapter3.rpy:931
translate english chapter3_045b3827:

    # "모든 것이 다 괜찮아질 거라는 멜로디가 소녀의 귓가에 연주되고, 나의 손은 샴푸 향이 여전히 남아있는 그녀의 머리카락을 천천히 쓰다듬는다."
    "The melody that everything will be fine played in the girl's ear, and my hand slowly stroked her hair that still smelled of shampoo."

# game/chapter3.rpy:932
translate english chapter3_e8264a51:

    # "기억에 남아있는 멜로디가 다 연주 되었을 때쯤, 소녀는 오컬트부실에서 보았던 그 편안한 얼굴을 한 채 새근새근 잠에 들어 있었다."
    "By the time the melody I remembered was played, the girl was sound asleep with the relaxed face I had seen in the occult club room."

# game/chapter3.rpy:939
translate english chapter3_d6cf2ea2:

    # "눈을 떴을 땐 평소같지 않은 빛이 주위를 감싸고 있었다."
    "When I opened my eyes, an unusual light was surrounding me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:940
translate english chapter3_8e713878:

    # "화들짝 놀라 잠에서 깨어난 뒤에야 오늘은 일요일에다가 방학식을 한 뒤라는 것을 깨닫고는 안도했다."
    "After waking up startled, I was relieved to realize that today is Sunday and it was after the holiday ceremony."

# game/chapter3.rpy:942
translate english chapter3_b8906a5f:

    # "더 볼 것도 없이, 해는 중천에 떠 있었다."
    "Without a doubt, the sun was high in the sky."

# game/chapter3.rpy:943
translate english chapter3_582d0263:

    # "새벽에 잠시 깨버려서 그런가, 팔자 좋게 늦잠을 자 버린 모양이었다."
    "It seemed like I had slept in late pleasantly because I woke up briefly at dawn."

# game/chapter3.rpy:944
translate english chapter3_307bc818:

    # "확실히 침대가 아닌 바닥에서 자는 건 익숙하지 않은지, 목을 돌리자 평소엔 느낄 수 없었던 뻐근함이 느껴졌다."
    "Surely sleeping on the floor instead of a bed isn't familiar; when I turned my neck, I felt a stiffness that I couldn't usually feel."

# game/chapter3.rpy:946
translate english chapter3_c3ad0764:

    # "옆을 바라보자 소녀는 지난 새벽에 있었던 일은 아무것도 알아채지 못한 듯 잠에서 막 깨어난 나를 빤히 들여다보고 있을 뿐이었다."
    "Looking to my side, the girl seemed to have no clue about what happened last dawn and was just staring at me who just woke up from sleep."

# game/chapter3.rpy:948
translate english chapter3_afe00b26:

    # "왠지 소녀에게 게으름뱅이 같은 모습을 보여준 것 같아 괜히 머쓱했다."
    "Somehow showing a sloth-like appearance to the girl made me feel awkward."

# game/chapter3.rpy:950
translate english chapter3_71a90b14:

    # 나 "“어, 언제 일어났어?”"
    나 "\"Uh, when did you wake up?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:952
translate english chapter3_f4f4b105:

    # voice "voices/gc47.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“방금요.”"
    voice "voices/gc47.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Just now.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:955
translate english chapter3_22291bb4:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀의 말투가 나를 관찰하는 것처럼 느껴진 건 분명 나만의 착각일 것이다."
    voice ""
    "It must have been my imagination that the girl's tone felt like she was observing me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:957
translate english chapter3_d31997db:

    # "소녀는 자신을 없는 존재 취급하라고 했지만, 현지의 말이 맞았다."
    "The girl insisted on being treated as a non-existent being, but Hyeonji was right."

# game/chapter3.rpy:958
translate english chapter3_56573a16:

    # "어떻게 바로 앞에 있는 사람을 없는 존재 취급할 수 있다는 것인가?"
    "How can one treat someone right in front of them as non-existent?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:959
translate english chapter3_9f46c112:

    # "게다가 나보다 아무리 많아도 한두 살 정도밖에 차이 나지 않는 또래 여학생의 시선을……."
    "Moreover, the gaze of a female student who is at most a year or two older than me..."

# game/chapter3.rpy:964
translate english chapter3_c58986e7:

    # 나 "“배는 안 고파?”"
    나 "\"Are you hungry?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:965
translate english chapter3_f5a60c01:

    # voice "voices/gc48.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“조금요.”"
    voice "voices/gc48.ogg"
    소녀 "\"A little.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:967
translate english chapter3_bc392a98:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“아, 음…… 그럼 아침 준비를…….”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Ah, um... then I'll prepare breakfast...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:970
translate english chapter3_16e9aa2f:

    # "아니, 점심인가."
    "No, it's lunchtime."

# game/chapter3.rpy:971
translate english chapter3_89c24615:

    # "시계를 보니 이미 정오가 코앞이었다."
    "Looking at the clock, it was almost noon."

# game/chapter3.rpy:973
translate english chapter3_90f35c7c:

    # "부엌으로 향하다 보니 배가 꼬르륵거리는 소리가 들려왔다."
    "As I headed towards the kitchen, I heard the sound of my stomach growling."

# game/chapter3.rpy:974
translate english chapter3_8fed0871:

    # "늦게나마 내가 잠에서 깬 것도 배가 고파서였던 걸지도 모르겠다."
    "Perhaps I woke up late because I was hungry."

# game/chapter3.rpy:975
translate english chapter3_069c0269:

    # "어제는 저녁을 좀 일찍 먹기도 했고."
    "I did eat dinner a bit early yesterday."

# game/chapter3.rpy:979
translate english chapter3_2b508a67:

    # "어쩌면 소녀가 ‘조금요’라고 자신의 의견을 조금이나마 내비친 것도 무척이나 배가 고파서 그런 건 아닌가 하는 생각이 들었다."
    "I wondered if the girl's slight admission that she was 'a little' hungry was because she was extremely hungry."

# game/chapter3.rpy:980
translate english chapter3_f6dea031:

    # "아무 생각 없이 냉장고를 열었다가 잊고 있었던 것이 떠올랐다."
    "I opened the fridge without thinking and remembered what I had forgotten."

# game/chapter3.rpy:984
translate english chapter3_c4f897ca:

    # "아 맞다."
    "Oh right."

# game/chapter3.rpy:985
translate english chapter3_bcf8445f:

    # "냉장고에 아무것도 안 남아 있었지."
    "There was nothing left in the fridge."

# game/chapter3.rpy:990
translate english chapter3_e76bedc2:

    # "빈손으로 방으로 돌아오자 소녀의 시선이 그런 나의 뒤를 말없이 따라붙었다."
    "Returning to the room empty-handed, I felt the girl's gaze silently following me from behind."

# game/chapter3.rpy:992
translate english chapter3_06f6ff8a:

    # 나 "“생각해보니 냉장고에 남아있는 게 아무것도 없어서. 마트 금방 갔다 올게.”"
    나 "\"I just remembered that there's nothing left in the fridge. I'll go to the mart quickly and come back.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:994
translate english chapter3_9a64440e:

    # "대충 외출복으로 갈아입은 나는 얼른 마트로 향했다."
    "Quickly changing into casual clothes, I hurried towards the mart."

# game/chapter3.rpy:995
translate english chapter3_e79b106c:

    # "현관을 나선 뒤에야 뒤늦게 소녀에게 점심으로는 뭘 먹고 싶은지 물어볼걸, 하는 생각이 들었지만, 돌아올 대답은 ‘뭐든지 괜찮아요’ 같은 세상에서 가장 간단하면서도 난해한 문장일 게 뻔했다."
    "Only after leaving my front door did it occur to me that I should have asked the girl what she wanted for lunch, but the expected answer would have been something like 'anything is fine', which is one of the simplest yet most complicated sentences in the world."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1003
translate english chapter3_87192e40:

    # "어제보다 한층 더 더워진 건지, 잠깐 걸었을 뿐인데 이마가 땀에 젖었다."
    "Perhaps it was hotter than yesterday, as I had only walked a short distance but my forehead was already damp with sweat."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1004
translate english chapter3_4425b179:

    # "15분 정도를 걸어 항상 식재료를 사러 들리는 집 근처의 작은 마트에 도착했다."
    "After about a 15-minute walk, I arrived at the small mart near my house where I always go to buy groceries."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1013
translate english chapter3_c48edea8:

    # "붉은색 카트를 몰고 식료품 코너 주변을 맴돌기 시작했다."
    "I started to push the red cart around the grocery section."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1014
translate english chapter3_58d8d422:

    # "말은 작은 쇼핑몰이라 했지만 그건 어디까지나 A구역 중심부에 위치한 대형 쇼핑몰과 비교했을 때의 이야기다."
    "Although I call it a small mart, that's only in comparison to the large shopping mall located in the central part of A district."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1015
translate english chapter3_3b5dace2:

    # "비교하자면 이곳은 있을 건 다 있을 곳이고, 대형 쇼핑몰은 없어도 될 것까지 다 있는 곳이라고나 할까."
    "If I were to compare them, this place would have everything necessary and the large shopping mall would have even what is not necessary."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1016
translate english chapter3_4b77ce83:

    # "나는 익숙한 리듬에 맞추어 식료품 코너를 배회했다."
    "I roamed the grocery section following a familiar rhythm."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1023
translate english chapter3_3cf0ce3f:

    # "식료품 코너를 맴돌며 먹을거리들을 쇼핑 카트에 이것저것 담고 난 뒤에서야, 카트에 담긴 것들이라고는 하나같이 냉동식품이나 영양가 없는 즉석식품이라는 것을 절감할 수 있었다."
    "Only after filling my cart with various items while wandering around the grocery corner did I realize that everything in my cart was either frozen food or nutrition-less instant food."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1024
translate english chapter3_195a65fe:

    # "여태껏 익숙해져 있던 몸의 궤적에 나도 모르게 기대어 있던 것이겠지."
    "I must have been unconsciously relying on the trajectory my body had become accustomed to."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1025
translate english chapter3_3543b49a:

    # "잠깐 시야를 의식적으로 넓혀 유령 소녀가 좋아할 만한 것들을 찾아 주변을 둘러보았다."
    "I consciously broadened my view for a moment and looked around for things that the ghost girl might like."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1027
translate english chapter3_611751c8:

    # "소녀는 ‘뭐든지 괜찮아요’라는 말을 항상 반복하겠지만, 그렇게 선택의 폭을 한없이 늘려주는 것이 매번 달갑지만은 않은 법이다."
    "The girl would always repeat 'anything is fine', but it's not always pleasant when she broadens the scope of choice indefinitely."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1029
translate english chapter3_5e993214:

    # "익숙해져 있던 몸의 궤적을 잠시 비틀어볼까 하고 다른 쪽으로 카트를 돌리려는 순간."
    "Just as I was about to deviate from my body's familiar trajectory and turn the cart in another direction..."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1030
translate english chapter3_584ace0c:

    # "나는 다른 쪽 쇼핑 코너에서 걸어오던 누군가와 우연히 눈이 마주친다."
    "I inadvertently locked eyes with someone coming from another shopping corner."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1039
translate english chapter3_da995e78:

    # voice "voices/yc1.ogg"
    # 유미 "“어?!”"
    voice "voices/yc1.ogg"
    유미 "\"Oh?!\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1042
translate english chapter3_8f777877:

    # voice ""
    # "예상하지 못한 곳에서 만나 그런지, 유미는 내게 평소보다 더 환한 얼굴로 손을 흔들었다."
    voice ""
    "Perhaps because we met in an unexpected place, Yumi greeted me with a brighter face than usual."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1048
translate english chapter3_c2f3a341:

    # voice "voices/yc2.ogg"
    # 유미 "“언제 다시 만나나 했는데, 생각보다 금방 다시 보게 됐네?”"
    voice "voices/yc2.ogg"
    유미 "\"I was wondering when we'd meet again, but we ended up seeing each other sooner than I thought!\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1051
translate english chapter3_84487b04:

    # voice ""
    # "나 역시 웃는 얼굴로 그녀에게 인사를 건네지 않을 이유가 없었다."
    voice ""
    "There was no reason for me not to return her greeting with a smile."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1054
translate english chapter3_9e8f0a4c:

    # "“그러게.”라며 유미에게 인사를 건넨 나는 그녀의 오른손에 들려있는 쇼핑 바구니를 힐긋 살폈다."
    "\"Indeed.\" As I greeted Yumi, I glanced at the shopping basket in her right hand."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1055
translate english chapter3_39097420:

    # "쇼핑 바구니에는 샐러드용 채소, 칼로리밸런스, 탄산수, 그리고 무지방 우유 같은 것들이 들어있었다."
    "The shopping basket contained items such as vegetables for salad, calorie balance food, carbonated water, and fat-free milk."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1056
translate english chapter3_e3f0ad7e:

    # "나는 교복 차림의 유미에게 말을 건넸다."
    "I addressed Yumi who was still in her school uniform."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1063
translate english chapter3_eae50114:

    # 나 "“어디 갔다 오는 거야?”"
    나 "\"Where are you coming from?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1064
translate english chapter3_c8a20380:

    # voice "voices/yc3.ogg"
    # 유미 "“응, 오늘 첫 멘토링 날이었거든. 아침에 애들 만나고 오는 길이었어.”"
    voice "voices/yc3.ogg"
    유미 "\"Yeah, today was the first day of mentoring. I was on my way back from meeting the kids this morning.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1068
translate english chapter3_0530e6d9:

    # voice ""
    # "깜빡 잊고 있었다."
    voice ""
    "I had completely forgotten about it."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1070
translate english chapter3_69bb16ca:

    # "방금 막 일어난 터라 나의 시간 감각을 기준으로 말을 꺼냈었는데, 유미와 나는 하루의 출발점이 다르다는 것을 잊고 있었던 것이다."
    "I had just woken up and spoke based on my sense of time, forgetting that Yumi and I start our day at different times."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1071
translate english chapter3_d91c141c:

    # "잠시 우물쭈물하는 티를 보이던 나의 얼굴을 유미가 살핀다."
    "Yumi scrutinized my face, which showed a moment of hesitation."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1073
translate english chapter3_54802167:

    # voice "voices/yc4.ogg"
    # 유미 "“피곤해 보이네?”"
    voice "voices/yc4.ogg"
    유미 "\"You look tired?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1076
translate english chapter3_9b075366:

    # voice ""
    # "나의 안색을 확인한 유미는 금세 내 상태를 진단했다."
    voice ""
    "Having checked my complexion, Yumi quickly diagnosed my condition."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1079
translate english chapter3_c48eae16:

    # 나 "“어, 그래 보여?”"
    나 "\"Oh, do I look like that?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1086
translate english chapter3_9175d96a:

    # voice "voices/yc5.ogg"
    # 유미 "“혹시 방금 막 일어나서 마트 온 건 아니지?”"
    voice "voices/yc5.ogg"
    유미 "\"Did you just wake up and come to the supermarket?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1089
translate english chapter3_7b1ddf2c:

    # voice ""
    # "너무 정확한 진단이라 뜨끔 하는 소리가 절로 마음속에서 들려오는 것 같았다."
    voice ""
    "Her diagnosis was so accurate that I could almost hear a voice inside me cringing."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1100
translate english chapter3_6bb812e0:

    # "나 혼자뿐이라면 어제의 일 때문에 피곤해서 그런 거라고 변명하고 스스로 납득할 수 있었겠지만, 유미에게 그런 변명은 통하지 않을 게 뻔했다."
    "If I were alone, I could have excused myself for being tired from yesterday's events and convinced myself, but such an excuse wouldn't work on Yumi."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1101
translate english chapter3_81a0b0c8:

    # "나의 침묵이 대답을 대신하는 동안, 유미는 다 알겠다는 표정으로 나를 바라보았다."
    "As my silence served as a response, Yumi looked at me with an expression that said she understood everything."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1102
translate english chapter3_d97b14c4:

    # "나는 딴청을 피우며 계산대 쪽으로 카트를 밀었다."
    "I pushed the cart towards the checkout counter while trying to play dumb."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1103
translate english chapter3_feac6bd1:

    # "유미가 뒤따라왔다."
    "Yumi followed behind me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1104
translate english chapter3_3d85cbbc:

    # "아무래도 유미 역시 마찬가지로 장을 다 본 모양이었다."
    "Apparently, Yumi had also finished her shopping."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1105
translate english chapter3_43dd57c2:

    # "그동안 유미의 잔소리가 계산대에 도착할 때까지 이어졌다."
    "Yumi's nagging continued until we reached the checkout counter."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1112
translate english chapter3_0bd48a1b:

    # "마트에서 집으로 향하는 방향도 같은 쪽이었기에, 집으로 가는 길도 유미와 함께였다."
    "Since we were heading in the same direction from the supermarket to home, I was with Yumi on my way home."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1113
translate english chapter3_95bf447a:

    # "다행히 마트에서 빠져나온 뒤로 더 이상의 잔소리는 이어지지 않았다."
    "Fortunately, there was no more nagging after we left the supermarket."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1114
translate english chapter3_e75c3470:

    # "나는 유미와 사거리에서 나란히 서서는 신호가 바뀌기를 기다리고 있었다."
    "I was standing next to Yumi at the intersection, waiting for the signal to change."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1116
translate english chapter3_adb25c4a:

    # 나 "“멘토링은 어땠어?”"
    나 "\"How was the mentoring?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1118
translate english chapter3_7088613c:

    # "신호를 기다리다 말고, 나는 유미에게 먼저 말을 걸었다."
    "While waiting for the signal, I initiated the conversation with Yumi."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1120
translate english chapter3_3d7b11a7:

    # voice "voices/yc6.ogg"
    # 유미 "“히, 나 가르치는 데 소질 있나 봐. 그냥 선생님이나 할까?”"
    voice "voices/yc6.ogg"
    유미 "\"Heh, I seem to have a knack for teaching. Maybe I should just become a teacher?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1123
translate english chapter3_229a88fd:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“며칠 전엔 장래희망으로 연구원이라고 써내지 않았어?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Didn't you write 'researcher' as your future career a few days ago?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1126
translate english chapter3_575e73c6:

    # voice "voices/yc7.ogg"
    # 유미 "“그러게. 아무래도 부모님은 그런 쪽으로 전공을 정하길 바라는 것 같아서. 요즘 교사한다고 하면 다들 뜯어말리잖아.”"
    voice "voices/yc7.ogg"
    유미 "\"That's true. My parents seem to want me to choose a major in that direction. These days if you say you're going to be a teacher everyone tries to talk you out of it.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1128
translate english chapter3_b7cce17b:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“하긴, 그렇긴 하지.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Well, that's true.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1131
translate english chapter3_80e17a3f:

    # "횡단보도로 발을 내디디는 유미로부터 들려오는 심장박동을 느낀다."
    "I could feel the heartbeat coming from Yumi as she stepped onto the crosswalk."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1132
translate english chapter3_7e62c75d:

    # "항상 꿈을 이야기할 때면 묻어나오는 기분 좋은 두근거림은 마치 내게 딱 맞는 주파수처럼 들렸다."
    "The pleasant excitement that always emanates when she talks about her dreams felt like a frequency that perfectly matched me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1133
translate english chapter3_24f12c9e:

    # "오늘따라 조금, 잡음이 섞인 것 같긴 했지만."
    "Although today, it seemed a bit mixed with noise."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1137
translate english chapter3_0a701202:

    # 나 "“부모님 권유였구나.”"
    나 "\"So it was your parents' suggestion.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1138
translate english chapter3_42c9793c:

    # voice "voices/yc8.ogg"
    # 유미 "“그렇지만 가르치는 게 재밌기도 하고, 어떻게 해야 할지 모르겠어.”"
    voice "voices/yc8.ogg"
    유미 "\"Yes, but teaching is also fun, and I don't know what to do.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1141
translate english chapter3_efd196f3:

    # voice ""
    # "가볍게 한숨을 내쉰 유미가, 나를 바라보았다."
    voice ""
    "Yumi, who had let out a light sigh, looked at me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1146
translate english chapter3_08442755:

    # voice "voices/yc9.ogg"
    # 유미 "“너라면 어땠을 것 같아?”"
    voice "voices/yc9.ogg"
    유미 "\"What would you have done if you were me?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1148
translate english chapter3_84d705b4:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그런 질문 해도, 나는 네가 아니잖아…….”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Even if you ask that question, I'm not you...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1151
translate english chapter3_3f6faf24:

    # voice "voices/yc10.ogg"
    # 유미 "“에헤헷, 그런가.”"
    voice "voices/yc10.ogg"
    유미 "\"Eheheh, is that so?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1153
translate english chapter3_f1683dd5:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“뻔한 대답이지만, 네가 행복할 수 있는 선택을 했으면 좋겠네.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"It's a cliché answer, but I hope you make a choice that will make you happy.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1156
translate english chapter3_40d586c5:

    # voice "voices/yc11.ogg"
    # 유미 "“흐음, 뻔한 대답이라…….”"
    voice "voices/yc11.ogg"
    유미 "\"Hmm, a cliché answer...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1159
translate english chapter3_24d38efd:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그리고 무언가를 좋아한다는 건, 그 사람에게 있어 엄청 특별한 거니까.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"And to love something, that's a really special thing for that person.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1162
translate english chapter3_d7b2c48b:

    # "뻔한 대답이라고는 했지만, 평소와 다르게 제법 진지한 나의 목소리에 놀라기라도 한 걸까."
    "Perhaps she was surprised by my voice, unusually serious despite it being a cliché answer."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1163
translate english chapter3_fa61b688:

    # "눈을 천천히 깜빡이며 가볍게 생각에 잠기는 유미."
    "Yumi slowly blinked her eyes as she lightly immersed herself in thought."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1164
translate english chapter3_e5931229:

    # "유미는 마치 내가 볼 수 없는 것을 보는 듯, 새파란 하늘 어딘가에 시선을 고정하고선 집으로 발걸음을 옮겼다."
    "Yumi, as if seeing something I couldn't see, fixed her gaze somewhere in the clear blue sky and moved her steps towards home."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1174
translate english chapter3_59e7d35d:

    # "집으로 돌아온 나는 소녀와 함께 간단히 점심을 해결하고는 의자에 앉아 멍하니 생각에 빠졌다."
    "After returning home, I had a simple lunch with the girl and then sat down on a chair, lost in thought."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1175
translate english chapter3_e7d65c18:

    # "생각해야 할 것이 많았다."
    "There was a lot to think about."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1176
translate english chapter3_8903e403:

    # "유미와의 일, 현지와의 일, 그리고 유령 소녀와의 일."
    "The matter with Yumi, the matter with Hyeonji, and the matter with the ghost girl."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1177
translate english chapter3_f66fb640:

    # "무엇 하나 명료한 해답을 내리기 어려운 고민이었기에, 내가 할 수 있는 일은 고작해야 우선순위를 매기는 정도였다."
    "Since none of them had clear answers to be given, all I could do was prioritize them."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1178
translate english chapter3_e51fa985:

    # "의자를 당겨 데스크탑 앞에 앉았다."
    "I pulled up a chair and sat down in front of my desktop computer."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1179
translate english chapter3_2db63445:

    # "아직 몸에 남아있던 어제의 피로가 내게 하품을 강요했지만, 나는 애써 이를 억누르며 데스크탑을 켰다."
    "The fatigue from yesterday still lingered in my body forcing me to yawn but I suppressed it and turned on my desktop."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1180
translate english chapter3_73158667:

    # "고개를 돌려 침대 쪽을 힐긋 바라보자, 아까 전부터 크게 바뀌지 않은 자세로 나를 지켜보고 있던 소녀가 눈에 들어왔다."
    "As I turned my head to glance at the bed, I saw the girl who had been watching me in the same position since earlier."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1181
translate english chapter3_1d939385:

    # "두 명이 함께 있는 방치고는 너무 고요한 분위기가 아까 전부터 이어지고 있었다."
    "The atmosphere was too quiet for a room where two people were present, and it had been this way since a while ago."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1187
translate english chapter3_d8abfaa6:

    # "어제의 일 때문인 걸까."
    "Was it because of what happened yesterday?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:1188
translate english chapter3_2af167d1:

    # "소녀는 아침부터 피곤한 건지, 기운이 없는 건지, 집안일을 할 때를 제외하면 자신의 두 배보다 조금 더 큰 크기의 침대에서 대부분의 시간을 보내고 있었다."
    "The girl, whether she was tired since morning or just listless, spent most of her time on her bed that was slightly larger than twice her size, except when doing housework."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1189
translate english chapter3_ab23ce95:

    # "마치 그곳에서 벗어날 수 없는 것처럼 말이다."
    "As if she couldn't get out of there."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1193
translate english chapter3_dd1e66b7:

    # 나 "“으음…….”"
    나 "'Hmm...'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:1195
translate english chapter3_18c9e52f:

    # "소녀의 기운 없는 모습을 보고 있자니 새벽에 있었던 일이 자꾸만 떠올랐다."
    "Seeing the girl's listless appearance reminded me of what happened in the early morning."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1196
translate english chapter3_52836fcf:

    # "소녀에게 뭔가 말을 걸어보려 했지만, 마땅한 문장이 떠오르지 않았다."
    "I tried to say something to the girl, but no suitable sentence came to mind."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1197
translate english chapter3_9aa83802:

    # "할 수 없이 나는 우선순위 맨 윗부분에 올려두었던 일을 시작했다."
    "Helplessly, I started with the task that was on top of my priority list."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1198
translate english chapter3_a2da0bfa:

    # "침묵은 그대로 이어져, 방에는 마우스를 딸깍이는 소리와 키보드를 두드리는 소리만이 이따금 들려올 뿐이었다."
    "The silence continued, and only the sound of clicking the mouse and tapping the keyboard could be heard occasionally in the room."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1203
translate english chapter3_105ecd63:

    # "막상 두 번째로 찾아갈 장소를 정하자니 생각할 것들이 꽤나 많았다."
    "Once I decided on the second place to visit, there were quite a lot of things to think about."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1204
translate english chapter3_c54daa4f:

    # "정확히 이야기하자면, 마음에 걸리는 것들이 많았다고 해야겠지."
    "To be precise, there were many things that weighed on my mind."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1206
translate english chapter3_a1dfe709:

    # "그런 것들 중 소녀의 힘없어 보이는 모습이 없었다고 한다면 그건 거짓말일 것이다."
    "If someone said that there was no sight of the girl's powerless appearance among those things, that would be a lie."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1207
translate english chapter3_114a4a14:

    # "그렇기에, 장소를 정하기 이전에 찾아볼 장소의 범위를 줄일 필요가 있었다."
    "Therefore, before deciding on a place, it was necessary to narrow down the range of places to look for."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1211
translate english chapter3_5c6a64ca:

    # "그리고 그러기 위해선 힌트가 조금 더 필요했다."
    "And to do that, they needed a little more hint."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1215
translate english chapter3_98b7a76a:

    # "의자를 살짝 뒤로 밀고선, 기지개를 켜며 등 뒤의 소녀를 향해 시선을 슬쩍 옮겼다."
    "Pushing the chair slightly back, I stretched and glanced back at the girl behind me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1216
translate english chapter3_3a9bd2d4:

    # "이름도, 나이도, 자신이 누구였는지 아무것도 기억하지 못하는 소녀가 자신을 증명할 수 있는 증거란 단 하나뿐이었다."
    "The girl who didn't remember her name, age, or who she was had only one piece of evidence to prove herself."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1220
translate english chapter3_c4fd792f:

    # 나 "‘분명 어디서 본 기억이 있는데.’"
    나 "'I'm sure I've seen it somewhere.'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:1221
translate english chapter3_8083dd9d:

    # "꿈에서 본 것이 아니라면, 분명 언젠가, 어디선가 본 적이 있었던 교복이었다."
    "It was a uniform that I had seen somewhere, sometime, if not in a dream."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1222
translate english chapter3_4dfbe845:

    # "다만 문제라면 그 언젠가가 언제인지도, 어디선가가 어디에서인지도 명확하게 기억나지 않는다는 것."
    "The problem was that I couldn't remember clearly when or where I had seen it."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1224
translate english chapter3_8d936c55:

    # "소녀의 출신 중학교를 알게 된다면 의외로 쉽게 문제 해결의 핵심에 다가갈 수 있을지도 모르겠다고 생각했지만, 소녀가 입고 있는 교복이 어느 중학교의 것인지를 알아내는 건 쉬운 일이 아니었다."
    "I thought that if I knew the girl's middle school, I might be able to get closer to the core of the problem solving easily, but finding out which middle school the uniform belonged to was not an easy task."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1226
translate english chapter3_c475737e:

    # "엠블럼도, 이름표도, 아무것도 남아있지 않은 평범한 디자인의 교복."
    "A plain design of uniform with no emblem, name tag, or anything left."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1227
translate english chapter3_5e3361bd:

    # "오랫동안 주변 중학교의 웹 페이지를 찾아보았지만, 소녀가 입고 있는 것과 같은 디자인의 교복은 보이지 않았다."
    "I searched for the web pages of nearby middle schools for a long time, but I couldn't find any uniform with the same design as the one the girl was wearing."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1228
translate english chapter3_daafcc03:

    # "교복 디자인이 웹 페이지에 나와 있지 않은 곳도 있었고, 최근에 교복 디자인이 바뀌어 사진과 다른 곳도 더러 있는 것 같았다."
    "Some places didn't have the uniform design on their web pages, and some seemed to have changed their uniform design recently and looked different from the pictures."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1229
translate english chapter3_1f4d55dd:

    # "그렇다고 근처 중학교의 교복 디자인을 모아둔 자료가 있을 리도 없고."
    "And it's not like there's a collection of uniform designs from nearby middle schools."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1231
translate english chapter3_99f94837:

    # "결국 그래왔던 것처럼 사망 사고가 일어난 곳을 하나하나 찾아보는 수밖엔 없나."
    "Do I have no choice but to look for the places where the death accidents occurred one by one, as I have been doing?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:1238
translate english chapter3_a8fedba6:

    # "한참 제자리걸음을 한 것 같다며 얼빠진 얼굴로 다시 기지개를 켜려다 말고, 나는 문득 고개를 돌려 다시금 소녀를 바라보았다."
    "Feeling like I had been walking in place for a while, I stopped stretching with a pale face and turned my head to look at the girl again."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1240
translate english chapter3_7530018e:

    # 나 "“저기, 있잖아.”"
    나 "\"Hey, you know...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1242
translate english chapter3_77ea9c51:

    # "나의 부름에 소녀가 고개를 들었다."
    "The girl lifted her head at my call."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1244
translate english chapter3_4c70a666:

    # 나 "“혹시 사진 찍어본 적 있어?”"
    나 "\"Have you ever taken a picture?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1251
translate english chapter3_8fdcce36:

    # voice "voices/gc49.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“…… 사진 말인가요?”"
    voice "voices/gc49.ogg"
    소녀 "\"... A picture?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1254
translate english chapter3_e5900e14:

    # voice ""
    # "나의 질문을 들은 소녀는 ‘으음’하는 소리를 내며 고민을 하더니, 이내 평범한 대답을 내놓았다."
    voice ""
    "The girl who heard my question made a *hmm* sound and pondered, then gave a plain answer."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1257
translate english chapter3_b9ec36d4:

    # voice "voices/gc50.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“글쎄요. 찍어본 적이 한 번도 없는 것 같진 않지만…… 기억이 안 나네요.”"
    voice "voices/gc50.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Well, I don't think I've never taken one, but... I don't remember.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1259
translate english chapter3_28c19c5e:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“아니, 살아있을 때 말고. 유령이 되고 난 뒤에 말이야.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"No, not when you were alive. I mean after you became a ghost.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1267
translate english chapter3_e06c0c2a:

    # voice "voices/gc51.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“네……?”"
    voice "voices/gc51.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Yes...?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1274
translate english chapter3_e8ad2ecf:

    # voice ""
    # "당혹스러움이 섞인 시선이 나를 향한다."
    voice ""
    "A puzzled look is directed at me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1276
translate english chapter3_3f9a6731:

    # "소녀는 내 질문이 가진 의도를 도저히 모르겠다는 듯 나를 빤히 바라보았다."
    "The girl stared at me blankly, as if she had no idea what my question meant."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1278
translate english chapter3_8b80ad57:

    # 나 "“왜, 간혹 유령이 사진에 찍히는 경우가 있잖아. 심령사진이라든가. 그런 것처럼 네 모습이 다른 사람의 눈에는 안 보이더라도 사진에는 찍힐 수도 있지 않을까 해서.”"
    나 "\"Well, sometimes ghosts appear in pictures, right? Like psychic photos. I thought maybe your image could be captured in a picture even if other people can't see you.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1285
translate english chapter3_8a4f2161:

    # voice "voices/gc52.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“심령사진이라…… 그럴 수도 있겠네요. 그런데 갑자기 사진이라니, 제 사진이 필요한 일이라도 생긴 건가요?”"
    voice "voices/gc52.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Psychic photos... That might be possible. But why are you suddenly talking about pictures? Do you need my picture for something?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1287
translate english chapter3_bf92388e:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“맞아.”"
    voice ""
    나 "“Yes.”"

# game/chapter3.rpy:1290
translate english chapter3_59c75483:

    # "아주 잠깐, 여태껏 느꼈던 침묵과는 다른 느낌의 정적이 감돈다."
    "A very brief silence, different from the one I had felt before, hangs in the air."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1291
translate english chapter3_77f4e68d:

    # "곡해될 여지가 있는 발언이었던 걸까?"
    "Was it a statement that could be misunderstood?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:1293
translate english chapter3_9b0560df:

    # 나 "“으음…… 네 사진이 필요한 건 아니고. 정확하게 말하자면 네 교복 사진이 필요한 거지.”"
    나 "\"Hmm... I don't need your picture per se. To be precise, I need a picture of your uniform.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1295
translate english chapter3_c84f80cf:

    # "소녀는 그제야 내 의도를 파악했는지 고개를 끄덕였다."
    "The girl nodded her head as if she finally understood my intention."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1302
translate english chapter3_71af218c:

    # voice "voices/gc53.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“찾아보려는 거죠?”"
    voice "voices/gc53.ogg"
    소녀 "\"You're trying to find out, right?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1304
translate english chapter3_c8bd2bf4:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“응. 인터넷의 힘을 빌리려고.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Yeah. I'm going to use the power of the internet.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1307
translate english chapter3_382c3ef3:

    # "충전기 위에 올려져 있던 휴대용 태블릿을 꺼내 들고는 카메라 기능을 켰다."
    "I took out the portable tablet that was on the charger and turned on the camera function."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1309
translate english chapter3_913ac499:

    # "그러고는 침대 위에 앉아있는 소녀의 모습을 카메라 렌즈를 통해 바라보았다."
    "Then I looked at the girl sitting on the bed through the camera lens."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1310
translate english chapter3_3e5477ca:

    # "화면에 보이는 건 텅 빈 침대의 모습뿐이었다."
    "All I could see on the screen was an empty bed."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1314
translate english chapter3_f295f25c:

    # "태블릿의 화면을 한 번, 그리고 태블릿 너머의 현실을 한 번 번갈아 바라보았다."
    "I looked at the tablet screen once, and then at the reality beyond the tablet once alternately."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1316
translate english chapter3_ee90e49f:

    # "누가 거짓을 말하는 것이고, 누가 진실을 말하는 것일까."
    "Who was lying and who was telling the truth?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:1317
translate english chapter3_d83a4050:

    # "고작 태블릿 하나를 사이에 두고 비추어진 두 세상이 각기 다른 주장을 하고 있었다."
    "The two worlds reflected by a mere tablet in between had different claims."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1321
translate english chapter3_6e4bff9a:

    # "셔터 버튼을 누르자 찰칵하는 소리가 제법 날카롭게 들려왔다."
    "When I pressed the shutter button, a *click* sound was heard quite sharply."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1322
translate english chapter3_e51a5450:

    # "소녀를 향하고 있던 카메라 렌즈가 거둬지자마자 소녀는 곧장 침대에서 일어나 나를 향해 다가왔다."
    "As soon as the camera lens that was pointing at the girl was withdrawn, the girl got up from the bed and came towards me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1326
translate english chapter3_47967e28:

    # voice "voices/gc54.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“어떻게 됐나요?”"
    voice "voices/gc54.ogg"
    소녀 "\"How did it go?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1329
translate english chapter3_96698bed:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀도 궁금했던 모양이었다."
    voice ""
    "The girl seemed curious too."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1331
translate english chapter3_f56956c5:

    # "자신이 존재한다는 사실이 사진이라는 현상을 통해 증명될 것인지가 말이다."
    "Whether the fact that she exists would be proven through the phenomenon of a picture."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1333
translate english chapter3_afa4321d:

    # 나 "“…… 역시 안 찍히네.”"
    나 "\"... As expected, she doesn't show up.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1334
translate english chapter3_fce3216e:

    # voice "voices/gc55.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그러게요.”"
    voice "voices/gc55.ogg"
    소녀 "\"That's true.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1337
translate english chapter3_f5b12d2f:

    # voice ""
    # "갤러리에 저장된 사진에서 소녀의 모습은 찾을 수 없었다."
    voice ""
    "I couldn't find the girl's image in the photo stored in the gallery."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1339
translate english chapter3_d895edab:

    # "그저 텅 빈 침대만이 사진 속의 피사체로 덩그러니 놓여있을 뿐."
    "Only an empty bed was left as the subject of the photo."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1340
translate english chapter3_06a1b387:

    # "소녀는 뭔가 허무한 듯 다시 침대로 돌아가 풀썩 몸을 누였다."
    "The girl went back to the bed with a somewhat empty look and flopped down."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1342
translate english chapter3_c499ab0e:

    # "시계를 보니 벌써 여섯 시가 다되어 가는 중이었다."
    "When I looked at the clock, it was almost six o'clock."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1347
translate english chapter3_e99f316c:

    # "평소 같았다면 지금 침대에 누워 무기력하게 시간을 보내고 있는 사람은 소녀가 아닌 나였을 텐데."
    "If it had been normal, the person who would be lying on the bed and spending time listlessly would have been me, not the girl."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1348
translate english chapter3_c821d386:

    # "유령 소녀 덕분에 나는 지금 책상 앞에서 성실한 척을 하고 있었다."
    "Thanks to the ghost girl, I was now pretending to be diligent at my desk."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1349
translate english chapter3_525f32cf:

    # "유미도 그렇고, 소녀도 그렇고, 어쩌면 현지도 그렇고."
    "Yumi was like that, the girl was like that, and maybe Hyeonji was like that too."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1350
translate english chapter3_c9c83709:

    # "내 주변에 나를 타의적으로나마 성실한 사람을 연기하게 하는 사람이 있어서 다행이라고 해야 할까."
    "Should I be thankful that there are people around me who make me act like a diligent person, even if it's for their own sake?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:1351
translate english chapter3_33c1b929:

    # "연기라."
    "Acting."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1355
translate english chapter3_4cfa3913:

    # "생각해보니 나는 이미 다른 사람을 연기하고 있는 중이었지."
    "Come to think of it, I was already acting like someone else."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1357
translate english chapter3_95df357e:

    # shnvl "어쩌면 이 말도 안 되는 세상이 거짓을 말하고 있었다 해도, 나는 그리 놀라지 않을지도 모른다."
    shnvl "Maybe even if this absurd world was lying, I wouldn't be so surprised."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1358
translate english chapter3_87b8f573:

    # shnvl "다시 한번 갤러리에 저장된 사진을 바라보며, 그렇게 생각했다."
    shnvl "I thought so as I looked at the photo stored in the gallery again."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1362
translate english chapter3_f0b3bbaf:

    # "한 시간 정도를 더 컴퓨터 앞에 앉은 채 보냈다."
    "I spent another hour sitting in front of the computer."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1363
translate english chapter3_bfbf3a86:

    # "이렇게 오랫동안 한 가지 일에 집중을 한 적이 언제였나 싶을 정도로 오랜 시간을 보낸 듯하다."
    "It seemed like a long time since I had focused on one thing for so long."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1364
translate english chapter3_45625a9c:

    # "학교 웹 페이지와 사망 사고가 일어났던 장소들을 교차해가며 살펴보던 내가 문득 떠올린 것은, 모 학교에서 일어났던 자살 사고에 대해 좀 더 자세히 알아보자는 거였다."
    "What I suddenly thought of as I looked through the school web pages and the places where the death accidents occurred was to find out more about the suicide that happened at a certain school."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1365
translate english chapter3_67214bf3:

    # "확신은 없었지만, 나의 못 미더운 감이 그쪽을 향하고 있었다."
    "I wasn't sure, but my hunch was pointing me in that direction."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1366
translate english chapter3_c05fd9a2:

    # "생각이 거기까지 닿자, 나는 바로 소녀를 불렀다."
    "As soon as my thoughts reached there, I called the girl."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1368
translate english chapter3_70c0b8e2:

    # 나 "“내일 나가보려고 하는데. 어때?”"
    나 "\"I'm thinking of going out tomorrow. How about you?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1370
translate english chapter3_8ca7281f:

    # voice "voices/gc56.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“네. 아무 곳이나 상관없어요.”"
    voice "voices/gc56.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Yes. I don't mind anywhere.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1372
translate english chapter3_cc22aa52:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“아니, 그게 아니라. 몸은 좀 괜찮나 해서 물어본 거야.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"No, that's not what I meant. I was asking if you're feeling okay.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1375
translate english chapter3_3bc0d75d:

    # voice "voices/gc57.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“몸이요?”"
    voice "voices/gc57.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Feeling okay?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1377
translate english chapter3_8bf1cd33:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“으응. 어제 너무 많이 걸어서 피곤한 건 아닌가 해서.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Yeah. I was wondering if you were tired from walking too much yesterday.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1380
translate english chapter3_1243a5ac:

    # voice "voices/gc58.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“괜찮아요. 움직일 만은 하니까.”"
    voice "voices/gc58.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I'm fine. I can move around.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1382
translate english chapter3_17105d3f:

    # voice ""
    # "침대에 걸터앉아있던 소녀는 다리를 아래위로 두어 번 까닥대더니, 자리에서 폴짝 일어나 내 뒤로 다가왔다."
    voice ""
    "The girl who was sitting on the bed kicked her legs up and down a few times, then jumped up and came behind me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1387
translate english chapter3_01dc7670:

    # voice "voices/gc59.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“내일 갈 곳은 어디로 정했나요?”"
    voice "voices/gc59.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Where are you going tomorrow?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1389
translate english chapter3_53f41758:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“여기. B구역에 있는 중학교에 가보려고.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Here. I'm going to see a middle school in the B district.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1394
translate english chapter3_63228fd8:

    # "나는 의자를 살짝 옆으로 틀어 소녀에게 모니터 화면을 보여주었다."
    "I turned the chair slightly to the side and showed the girl the monitor screen."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1395
translate english chapter3_0e4c1f08:

    # "소녀는 모니터를 들여다보더니, ‘흐음’하고는 짤막한 소리를 내었다."
    "The girl looked at the monitor and made a short *hmm* sound."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1402
translate english chapter3_e45fb0a4:

    # voice "voices/gc60.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“다른 곳은 아직 생각 안 해뒀나요?”"
    voice "voices/gc60.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Have you not thought of any other places yet?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1404
translate english chapter3_2b4617c8:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“내일은 저기 한 곳만 가볼 거야.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"I'm just going to check out that one place tomorrow.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1407
translate english chapter3_10351f1e:

    # voice "voices/gc61.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“한 군데만요?”"
    voice "voices/gc61.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Just one place?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1409
translate english chapter3_9de4cbef:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“어제 너무 많이 걸었더니 피곤해서…….”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"I'm tired from walking too much yesterday...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1414
translate english chapter3_32ab15ad:

    # "실은 다른 이유에서였지만."
    "Actually, it was for a different reason."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1419
translate english chapter3_b77db8b8:

    # voice "voices/gc62.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“좋아요. 그렇게 해요.”"
    voice "voices/gc62.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Okay. Let's do that.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1422
translate english chapter3_c799ee0f:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀는 언제나 그랬듯 고개를 끄덕였다."
    voice ""
    "The girl nodded her head as she always did."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1424
translate english chapter3_339a71a3:

    # "자리에서 일어나 시각을 확인하고, 살짝 늦은 감이 없잖아 있는 저녁을 소녀와 함께 먹었다."
    "I got up from my seat, checked the time, and had a slightly late dinner with the girl."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1425
translate english chapter3_0f21e579:

    # "여전히 2인분 치를 요리하는 건 익숙지 않은지 식탁에 올려진 요리는 지난번보단 나았지만, 여전히 엉성한 건 그대로였다."
    "I still wasn't used to cooking for two people, and the food on the table was better than last time, but still sloppy."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1432
translate english chapter3_58b3e127:

    # "방학이 시작한 뒤 첫 번째 주말이 그렇게 지나갔다."
    "The first weekend after the start of the vacation passed like that."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1434
translate english chapter3_3064f5ab:

    # "이런 신기한 주말을, 나는 몇 번 정도 더 맞이할 수 있을까."
    "How many more times can I have such a miraculous weekend?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:1435
translate english chapter3_f708bb38:

    # "그리고 이런 주말이 끝나고 난 뒤엔, 나는 조금은 달라져 있을까."
    "And after such a weekend is over, will I be a little different?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:1442
translate english chapter3_370c6d33:

    # "어제보다는 조금 이른, 그제와 비교하자면 조금 늦은 시각에 잠에서 깬 우리는 간단히 뱃속을 채우고는 열차를 탔다."
    "We woke up at a slightly earlier time than yesterday, but a slightly later time than the day before, filled our stomachs briefly and took the train."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1443
translate english chapter3_47b74ca7:

    # "목적지는 어제 이야기했던 대로 B구역에 있는 한 중학교였다."
    "The destination was a middle school in the B district, as we had talked about yesterday."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1451
translate english chapter3_d92cf4c2:

    # "B구역 터미널에 도착해 밖으로 나오자 어제 잠에서 막 깨어났을 때 봤음직한 높이에서 태양이 우리를 비추고 있었다."
    "When we arrived at the B district terminal and came outside, the sun was shining on us from a high altitude, as if we had just woken up from a nap yesterday."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1453
translate english chapter3_19756f52:

    # "소녀와 함께 목적지를 향해 걸었다."
    "We walked towards our destination with the girl."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1455
translate english chapter3_a1352160:

    # "보도블럭 위로는 새까만 그림자가 드리운다."
    "A black shadow was cast over the sidewalk blocks."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1457
translate english chapter3_1b2ad93b:

    # "홀로 보도블럭 위를 떠다니는 새까만 그림자는 아무래도 소녀의 존재를 인정하지 않는 모양이었다."
    "The black shadow that floated alone over the sidewalk blocks seemed to ignore the girl's existence."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1469
translate english chapter3_62c83d65:

    # voice "voices/gc63.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“중학교라고 했죠? 거기선 어쩌다 사람이 죽은 건가요?”"
    voice "voices/gc63.ogg"
    소녀 "\"You said it was a middle school, right? How did someone die there?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1472
translate english chapter3_21fd5384:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“자살이래. 옥상에서 뛰어내렸다나.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"They said it was suicide. She jumped off the roof.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1481
translate english chapter3_a882ffda:

    # voice "voices/gc64.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그런가요.”"
    voice "voices/gc64.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I see.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1483
translate english chapter3_85c24c7b:

    # voice ""
    # "예상대로 무덤덤한 반응이었다."
    voice ""
    "It was a calm reaction as expected."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1486
translate english chapter3_90e3366d:

    # "일면식도 없는 생판 남의 이야기를 들은 것처럼 말이다."
    "It was like listening to someone else's story that I had never met before."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1487
translate english chapter3_4c9ac73c:

    # "나는 이야기를 이어갔다."
    "I continued the story."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1491
translate english chapter3_5e2850c5:

    # 나 "“자살이라는 것에 대해서는, 어떻게 생각해?”"
    나 "\"What do you think about suicide?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1496
translate english chapter3_130939c1:

    # "소녀가 조금이나마 이야기 속에 자신을 대입시키길 바랐던 걸까."
    "Did I hope that the girl would put herself in the story a little bit?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:1497
translate english chapter3_ce539bd6:

    # "속으로 주저하긴 했지만, 이미 그런 질문을 건넨 뒤였다."
    "I hesitated inwardly, but it was already after I had asked such a question."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1499
translate english chapter3_2737f2be:

    # "소녀는 입술을 슬며시 깨물더니, 이내 입을 열었다."
    "The girl bit her lips slightly, then opened her mouth."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1501
translate english chapter3_3eca5b3b:

    # voice "voices/gc65.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“글쎄요. 살아 있었을 적의 제가 어떻게 생각했을지는 잘 모르겠지만, 왠지 그리 멀리 있지는 않은 느낌이에요.”"
    voice "voices/gc65.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Well, I don't know what I thought when I was alive, but it feels like it's not too far away.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1506
translate english chapter3_b16e1f70:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“음…… 그렇구나.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Hmm... I see.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1511
translate english chapter3_349edf68:

    # "나의 입과 눈이 서로 상반된 반응을 보이고 있었다."
    "My mouth and eyes showed opposite reactions."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1513
translate english chapter3_9342943e:

    # "미묘하게 떨리는 나의 동공이 이해하지 못했다는 이야기를 소녀에게 건넨다."
    "My trembling pupils conveyed to the girl that I didn't understand."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1515
translate english chapter3_dfeff0f8:

    # "소녀는 나의 눈동자에 쓰인 메시지를 금방 포착한다."
    "The girl quickly caught the message written in my eyes."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1519
translate english chapter3_29306022:

    # "마치 눈동자에 쓰여진 건 뭐든 읽어낼 수 있다는 듯 말이다."
    "As if she could read anything written in the eyes."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1520
translate english chapter3_160cc29f:

    # "가벼운 한숨과 함께, 소녀가 말한다."
    "With a light sigh, the girl said."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1525
translate english chapter3_14ce3807:

    # voice "voices/gc66.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“잘 모르겠어요. 그냥 그런 기분이 들어요.”"
    voice "voices/gc66.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I don't know. I just feel that way.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1528
translate english chapter3_15743e65:

    # voice ""
    # "그런 이야기를 소녀는 아무렇지도 않게 읊조렸다."
    voice ""
    "The girl recited such a story as if it was nothing."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1535
translate english chapter3_9cbbb4ef:

    # "아무렇지도 않았던 건 아니었는지도 모르겠다."
    "Maybe it wasn't nothing."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1537
translate english chapter3_751b5dfe:

    # "소녀의 눈동자에서 느껴지던 공허함이 오늘따라 더욱 싸늘하게 다가왔으니까."
    "The emptiness I felt in the girl's eyes seemed colder today."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1543
translate english chapter3_f7209602:

    # "화창한 날씨를 머금은 학교 운동장의 분위기는 아까의 이야기가 무색할 정도로 밝았다."
    "The atmosphere of the school playground with the sunny weather was so bright that it made the previous story seem insignificant."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1544
translate english chapter3_483b2427:

    # "운동장에서는 마침 학교 간의 친선 야구 경기가 열리고 있었던 모양인지, 응원하는 학생들이 가득 들어차 있었다."
    "There were a lot of students cheering on the playground, as if there was a friendly baseball game between schools going on."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1545
translate english chapter3_f00c7a97:

    # "교문을 사이에 두고 나는 잠시 발걸음을 멈춰 세운 채 운동장을 바라보았다."
    "I stopped my steps for a moment and looked at the playground with the school gate in between."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1549
translate english chapter3_d6995602:

    # "사실 예상하지 못했던 장면이었다."
    "It was an unexpected scene."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1550
translate english chapter3_42b8c228:

    # "어제까지만 해도 분명 지금 이 시각의 중학교에는 사람이 없을 거라고 생각했었는데."
    "Until yesterday, I thought there would be no one in the middle school at this time of day."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1551
translate english chapter3_471d57aa:

    # "아무래도 중학교는 아직 방학이 시작되지 않았는지, 평소의 모습 그대로였다."
    "Maybe the middle school hadn't started its vacation yet, it was just as usual."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1552
translate english chapter3_7ec435ce:

    # "이래서야 학교 안으로 들어가는 건 아무래도 무리가 있어 보였다."
    "It seemed impossible to go inside the school like this."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1555
translate english chapter3_df1400f3:

    # 나 "“미처 생각 못했네. 아직 중학교는 방학이 아니었을 줄은.”"
    나 "\"I didn't think of that. I didn't expect the middle school to still be in session.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1559
translate english chapter3_0a5d6e0c:

    # "나는 머쓱한 얼굴로 마운드에서 공을 던지는 학생의 모습을 바라보았다."
    "I looked at the student throwing the ball from the mound with an awkward face."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1560
translate english chapter3_50388a61:

    # "{color=#00ccff}익숙한 느낌의 운동장과 그 전경이었다.{/color}"
    "{color=#00ccff}It was a familiar feeling of the playground and its view.{/color}"

# game/chapter3.rpy:1561
translate english chapter3_c1d70984:

    # voice "voices/gc67.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“다들 열심이네요.”"
    voice "voices/gc67.ogg"
    소녀 "\"They're all hardworking.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1563
translate english chapter3_085c8575:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그러게.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Seems so.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1568
translate english chapter3_7635b886:

    # "걸음을 멈춘 채 운동장을 바라보고 있는 것이 비단 우리뿐만은 아니었는지, 동적인 운동장의 전경과 대비되는 한여름날의 새털구름이 나의 시야를 스쳤다."
    "As we stopped walking and looked at the playground, a feather cloud of a summer day contrasted with the dynamic view of the playground swept my sight."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1569
translate english chapter3_2db5f3a9:

    # "옆으로 힐긋 시선을 돌리자, 운동장의 학생들을 빤히 바라보는 소녀가 보였다."
    "When I turned my eyes to the side with a smile, I saw the girl staring intently at the students on the playground."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1572
translate english chapter3_8be549ee:

    # "그녀의 눈동자에는 추억도, 기억도, 아무것도 담겨있지 않았다."
    "There was nothing in her eyes, no reminiscence, no memory, nothing."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1573
translate english chapter3_b0280374:

    # "흘러가는 지금만이 눈동자에 곧이곧대로 새겨질 뿐."
    "Only the passing present was engraved in her eyes as it was."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1575
translate english chapter3_396673fa_3:

    # 나 "“…….”"
    나 "\"...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1578
translate english chapter3_891b39fc:

    # "무심한 듯 운동장을 바라보는 소녀의 모습에서 떠올린 건, 또다시 그곳에서의 기억이었다."
    "What I thought of from the girl's appearance of looking at the playground indifferently was again the memory of that place."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1579
translate english chapter3_8a00f9c5:

    # "중학교에서의 마지막 여름."
    "The last summer in middle school."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1580
translate english chapter3_0d85d1e6:

    # "여느 때 보다 치열했고, 누구보다 간절했던 그 순간이었으련만, 어째서인지 그 기억은 흐릿하게 남아 막연한 감정만을 남겨 두고 있었다."
    "It was a moment that was more intense and more earnest than any other time, but for some reason, that memory remained faint and left only vague feelings."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1582
translate english chapter3_2e46540c:

    # "망각의 마법에라도 걸린 것처럼 흐릿해져 가는 2년 전의 기억을 움켜잡았다."
    "I grasped the memory of two years ago that was fading away as if it was under the magic of oblivion."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1584
translate english chapter3_1abdb23c:

    # "마치 수천 년 전의 기억 같은 그 여름의 일들이 어렴풋이 떠올랐다."
    "The things of that summer that seemed like thousands of years ago came to my mind vaguely."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1586
translate english chapter3_6ed0611f:

    # "마운드 위에서 공을 던지던 내 모습."
    "The image of me throwing the ball from the mound."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1587
translate english chapter3_dc1f1b61:

    # "그런 나를 진심으로 응원해주던 한 사람."
    "The one person who cheered me on sincerely."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1589
translate english chapter3_09df0610:

    # "하지만 불완전하게 재구성된 흐릿한 추억은 말 그대로 흐릿한 감상만을 남길 뿐이었다."
    "But the faint reminiscence that was incompletely reconstructed only left a faint impression as it was."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1597
translate english chapter3_fbaf4f85:

    # voice "voices/gc68.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“뭘 그렇게 골똘히 생각하는 건가요?”"
    voice "voices/gc68.ogg"
    소녀 "\"What are you thinking about so hard?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1599
translate english chapter3_8a327af7:

    # voice ""
    # "운동장을 바라보고 있던 소녀가 불쑥 말을 꺼냈다."
    voice ""
    "The girl who was looking at the playground suddenly spoke up."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1602
translate english chapter3_72bff69a:

    # 나 "“저기서 공 던지는 학생, 멋있어 보이지 않아?”"
    나 "\"Don't you think the student throwing the ball over there looks cool?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1611
translate english chapter3_34708149:

    # voice "voices/gc69.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“…… 그건 갑자기 왜요?”"
    voice "voices/gc69.ogg"
    소녀 "\"... Why do you ask that all of a sudden?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1613
translate english chapter3_9463d26f:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그냥, 갑자기 물어보고 싶었어.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"I just wanted to ask you something.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1616
translate english chapter3_72c82bd2:

    # "뭐라 대답을 해야 할지 모르겠다는 어색한 표정을, 소녀는 지어 보였다."
    "The girl made a awkward expression, as if she didn't know how to answer."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1618
translate english chapter3_64adebde:

    # 나 "“실은, 옛날 생각이 문득 나서 물어본 거야.”"
    나 "\"Actually, I asked you because I suddenly remembered the past.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1619
translate english chapter3_19aa6cf7:

    # voice "voices/gc70.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“옛날 생각이요?”"
    voice "voices/gc70.ogg"
    소녀 "\"The past?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1622
translate english chapter3_84d9a685:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“야구, 좋아했거든. 잘하기도 했고.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"I liked baseball. I was good at it too.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1624
translate english chapter3_6dec7e6c:

    # voice "voices/gc71.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그런가요.”"
    voice "voices/gc71.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I see.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1630
translate english chapter3_c92b1bb2:

    # voice ""
    # "흥미를 보인다고도, 그렇다고 흥미가 아예 없다고도 할 수 없는 애매한 목소리가 대답으로 돌아왔다."
    voice ""
    "A vague voice came back as an answer, neither showing interest nor completely lacking it."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1632
translate english chapter3_bfe4547a:

    # "소녀는 다시금 운동장 안쪽을 기웃대며 물었다."
    "The girl peered inside the playground again and asked."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1639
translate english chapter3_49283b00:

    # voice "voices/gc72.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“역시 지금 같이 들어가 보는 건 무리려나요?”"
    voice "voices/gc72.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Is it still impossible to go in there like this?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1641
translate english chapter3_5fc86f3c:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“으응, 그렇겠다.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Yeah, I guess so.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1643
translate english chapter3_42e342d9:

    # voice "voices/gc73.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그럼 저 혼자만이라도 들어갔다 와 볼까요?”"
    voice "voices/gc73.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Then can I go in and take a look by myself?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1647
translate english chapter3_374a9683:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“아냐, 나중에 나랑 같이 들어가자. 어차피 여기만 와보려 했으니까 시간도 충분하고. 수업이 끝난 뒤에 슬쩍 들어가면 될 것 같아.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"No, let's go in together later. We only came here to see this place, so we have plenty of time. I think we can sneak in after the class is over.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1656
translate english chapter3_00329dbb:

    # voice "voices/gc74.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그렇지만 수업이 끝난 뒤에도 경비 아저씨라든가, 여전히 남아있지 않을까요.”"
    voice "voices/gc74.ogg"
    소녀 "\"But what if there are still security guards or something after the class is over.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1662
translate english chapter3_65b668b4:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“실수로 두고 간 물건이 있어서 돌아왔다고 하면 괜찮지 않을까?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"What if we say we came back because we left something behind by mistake?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1664
translate english chapter3_c3b45cc9:

    # voice "voices/gc75.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그거야 그렇다 쳐도…….”"
    voice "voices/gc75.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Well, even if that's the case...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1668
translate english chapter3_911744df:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀의 시선이 아래위로 나를 훑었다."
    voice ""
    "The girl's eyes scanned me up and down."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1670
translate english chapter3_38efd398:

    # "머뭇대며 바로 말을 꺼내지 못하는 소녀였지만, 무슨 말을 하고 싶은지는 충분히 알 것 같았다."
    "She hesitated and couldn't say anything right away, but I thought I knew what she wanted to say."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1680
translate english chapter3_d018688f:

    # 나 "“나 정도면 중학생으로 보일 만하지 않아?”"
    나 "\"Don't I look like a middle school student?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1690
translate english chapter3_715d030a:

    # voice "voices/gc76.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“음…… 의심 받을 거라 생각해요.”"
    voice "voices/gc76.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Um... I think you'll be suspicious.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1694
translate english chapter3_e070edaf:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“생각보다 단호하네.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"You're more firm than I thought.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1696
translate english chapter3_0f549984:

    # "맛없는 요리를 먹으면서도, 불편한 시간을 보내면서도 항상 선의의 거짓말을 해주었던 소녀라도 이것까지는 무리인 모양이었다."
    "Even the girl who always told me white lies while eating tasteless food and spending uncomfortable time seemed to have a hard time with this."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1701
translate english chapter3_9454b870:

    # "그나저나, 내 몸이 내 몸 같지 않아서일까."
    "By the way, was it because my body didn't feel like my own?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:1702
translate english chapter3_edbabde3:

    # "소녀로부터 그런 말을 들었어도 특별한 대미지는 없었다."
    "I didn't feel any special damage from hearing such a thing from the girl."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1707
translate english chapter3_2f06201f:

    # 나 "“괜찮아. 잡아떼면 별문제 없겠지. 여차하면 도망치면 되고, 나쁜 짓 하려는 것도 아니잖아?”"
    나 "\"It's okay. It won't be a big problem if we bluff. We can run away if we have to, and we're not trying to do anything bad, right?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1709
translate english chapter3_b3a0c5e1:

    # voice "voices/gc77.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“알겠어요.”"
    voice "voices/gc77.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Okay.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1719
translate english chapter3_8fa75f9a:

    # voice ""
    # "태블릿을 꺼내 시각을 확인했다."
    voice ""
    "I took out the tablet and checked the time."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1721
translate english chapter3_aecf1baa:

    # "적어도 네 시는 되어야 하교 시간이려나."
    "It would probably be around four o'clock when school was over."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1724
translate english chapter3_be754df0:

    # "졸지에 세 시간 넘게 계획의 공백이 생겨버렸기에, 나는 즉흥적으로 소녀에게 주변을 돌아다녀 볼까 하는 제안을 건넸다."
    "Since there was a gap of more than three hours in the plan, I spontaneously suggested to the girl that we look around."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1731
translate english chapter3_fdda13be:

    # voice "voices/gc78.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그렇게 할까요.”"
    voice "voices/gc78.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Let's do that.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1738
translate english chapter3_490c3a89:

    # voice ""
    # "항상 군말 없이 내 제안을 받아들이는 소녀였다."
    voice ""
    "The girl always accepted my suggestions without hesitation."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1747
translate english chapter3_c098270c:

    # "무작정 길을 걷다 보면 어딘가에 필연적으로 도착하기 마련이다."
    "If you walk aimlessly, you will inevitably arrive somewhere."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1749
translate english chapter3_786cea01:

    # "집으로 돌아가는 길을 찾아 외딴 산속을 헤매던 헨젤과 그레텔이 그랬듯 말이다."
    "Just like Hansel and Gretel who wandered around the secluded mountains looking for their way home."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1754
translate english chapter3_befb4457:

    # "그렇다. 어쨌거나 최후에 발걸음이 닿는 곳은 달콤한 향이 풍겨오는 곳이라는 거다."
    "Yes. Anyway, the place where our footsteps end up is a place where a sweet scent comes from."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1755
translate english chapter3_807a28ad:

    # "나는 목적지 없이 아무렇게나 내딛던 발걸음을, 한 디저트 카페 앞에서 멈춰 세웠다."
    "I stopped my footsteps in front of a dessert cafe, without any destination."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1761
translate english chapter3_f3c55c12:

    # 나 "“여기 잠깐 들러서 시간이나 때우다 가는 건 어때?”"
    나 "\"How about we stop by here for a while and kill some time?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1762
translate english chapter3_831ef1ed:

    # voice "voices/gc79.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“디저트 카페인가요.”"
    voice "voices/gc79.ogg"
    소녀 "\"A dessert cafe?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1764
translate english chapter3_2cd48ea1:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀는 고개를 들어 ‘체스트넛’이라 쓰여있는 간판을 올려다보았다."
    voice ""
    "The girl lifted her head and looked up at the sign that said 'Chestnut'."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1769
translate english chapter3_3137c01d:

    # "왠지 달콤함이 묻어있는 것 같은 네이밍이었다."
    "It was a name that seemed to have a sweetness to it."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1770
translate english chapter3_797831b1:

    # "잠시 생각에 잠기더니, 소녀는 이내 나를 향해 말했다."
    "After a moment of thought, the girl spoke to me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1773
translate english chapter3_5213af76:

    # voice "voices/gc80.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“어울리지 않는 장소긴 하지만, 사람만 없다면 나쁘진 않을 것 같아요.”"
    voice "voices/gc80.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It's not a place that suits me, but I don't think it's bad if there's no one there.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1776
translate english chapter3_696cb77f:

    # voice ""
    # "어울리지 않는다는 건 나를 이야기하는 걸까, 소녀 자신을 이야기하는 걸까."
    voice ""
    "Did she mean that it didn't suit me, or herself?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:1779
translate english chapter3_00772145:

    # "나는 반투명에 가까운 유리벽을 통해 카페 내부를 들여다보았다."
    "I looked inside the cafe through the glass wall that was almost transparent."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1781
translate english chapter3_336397a9:

    # "마치 과자집 안을 몰래 훔쳐보던 헨젤과 그레텔처럼 말이다."
    "Just like Hansel and Gretel who secretly peeked inside the candy house."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1783
translate english chapter3_eab00c65:

    # 나 "“손님은 별로 없는 것 같아.”"
    나 "\"There don't seem to be many customers.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1785
translate english chapter3_65dbde55:

    # "애초에 평일 낮의 디저트 카페이니, 하교 시간이 다 될 때까지는 사람도 없을 것이다."
    "It was a dessert cafe on a weekday afternoon, so there wouldn't be anyone until school was over."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1786
translate english chapter3_d472c964:

    # "카페에 손님이 들어오기 시작하면 그때에 맞춰 학교로 향하면 되겠지."
    "We could head to the school when the cafe started to have customers."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1788
translate english chapter3_73944a58:

    # voice "voices/gc81.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그럼, 들어가요.”"
    voice "voices/gc81.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Then, let's go in.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1799
translate english chapter3_a719a476:

    # voice ""
    # "문을 열자 차임벨 소리가 들렸다."
    voice ""
    "As I opened the door, I heard the sound of a bell."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1801
translate english chapter3_7782f5ff:

    # "달콤한 향기가 코끝을 간질이고, 나이를 가늠하기 어렵게 만드는 복장과 함께 금발의 점원이 나를 맞이한다."
    "A sweet scent tickled my nose, and a blonde clerk greeted me with a dress that made her age hard to guess."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1802
translate english chapter3_c13dc4a3:

    # voice "voices/b1.ogg"
    # who "“어서오세요~”"
    voice "voices/b1.ogg"
    who "\"Welcome~\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1805
translate english chapter3_dddaa754:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀는 그런 환대가 자신을 향하는 것이 아니라는 걸 누구보다 잘 알고 있는 듯 점원의 눈길을 피했다."
    voice ""
    "The girl avoided the clerk's eyes as if she knew better than anyone that the welcome was not for her."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1809
translate english chapter3_c49b753b:

    # voice "voices/b2.ogg"
    # who "“몇 명이신가요?”"
    voice "voices/b2.ogg"
    who "\"How many are you?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1811
translate english chapter3_ef366adf:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“어…… 한 명이요.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Uh... one person.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1814
translate english chapter3_76493257:

    # "두 명 같은 한 명이란 바로 지금 같은 상황을 두고 말하는 거였나 싶었다."
    "I wondered if one person like two people meant a situation like this."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1818
translate english chapter3_38804ee8:

    # voice "voices/b3.ogg"
    # who "“한 명, 맞으신가요?”"
    voice "voices/b3.ogg"
    who "\"One person, are you sure?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1820
translate english chapter3_6522bee4:

    # voice ""
    # "일행도 없이 혼자서 디저트 카페에 오는 것은 아무래도 드문 일이었는지, 점원은 마치 내 옆에 서 있던 소녀의 존재를 인정해 주기라도 하려는 것처럼 내게 재차 질문을 건넸다."
    voice ""
    "Maybe it was rare for someone to come to a dessert cafe alone without any company, the clerk asked me again as if to acknowledge the existence of the girl who was standing next to me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1823
translate english chapter3_241e4b21:

    # "‘네’라며 고개를 끄덕이고선, 나는 자리를 안내해주려는 점원의 말보다 한발 앞서 인적 드문 구석 자리를 선점했다."
    "I nodded my head and said 'yes', and then I took a seat in a corner that was less crowded, ahead of the clerk who was trying to guide me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1830
translate english chapter3_6d4e883a:

    # "다른 손님이 거의 없는 카페는 꽤나 조용했다."
    "The cafe was quite quiet with hardly any other customers."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1832
translate english chapter3_58ef90fb:

    # "항상 유미와 함께 왔던 시끌벅적한 디저트 카페와는 확실히 다른 분위기였다."
    "It was a definitely different atmosphere from the noisy dessert cafe that I always came with Yumi."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1837
translate english chapter3_d59cddb0:

    # "카페의 미묘한 고요함이 전혀 어울리지 않을 것 같던 소녀와도 묘하게 어우러지는 것 같았으니까."
    "The subtle silence of the cafe seemed to strangely blend with the girl who seemed totally out of place in a dessert cafe."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1838
translate english chapter3_54668a4a:

    # "아무래도 소녀가 말한 디저트 카페와 어울리지 않는 쪽은 나였던 모양이다."
    "It seemed that the one who didn't fit in with the dessert cafe was me after all."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1840
translate english chapter3_88ddfda6:

    # "곧바로 점원이 내게 메뉴판을 건넸다."
    "The clerk soon handed me a menu."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1844
translate english chapter3_ae821140:

    # "메뉴판을 받아들고는 소녀에게 눈길을 건네자, 나의 맞은편에 앉아있던 소녀가 스르륵 나의 옆에 붙었다."
    "As I took the menu and looked at the girl, she slid over and stuck to my side."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1845
translate english chapter3_7bb59350:

    # "나는 소녀에게 네가 골라 보라는 무언의 신호를 보냈다."
    "I sent her a silent signal to choose something."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1847
translate english chapter3_d500ef67:

    # voice "voices/gc82.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“이거…… 그리고 요거요.”"
    voice "voices/gc82.ogg"
    소녀 "\"This... and this one.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1849
translate english chapter3_5846a7ad:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀가 맨 처음으로 고른 것은 몽블랑, 그리고 두 번째로 고른 것은 쇼트케이크였다."
    voice ""
    "The first thing the girl chose was a Mont Blanc, and the second thing she chose was a shortcake."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1855
translate english chapter3_494a5ecd:

    # "분명 하나만 고르려다 예쁘장한 모양의 쇼트케이크가 건네는 유혹에 결국 넘어가버린 것이리라."
    "She must have fallen for the temptation of the pretty-looking shortcake after trying to choose only one."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1856
translate english chapter3_932be8e7:

    # "점원에게 소녀가 고른 것에 더해 소프트드링크 두 잔을 주문하고는 고개를 돌려 옆을 바라보았다."
    "I ordered two soft drinks in addition to what the girl chose and turned my head to look at her."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1860
translate english chapter3_837aa0f0:

    # "소녀는 맞은편 자리로 돌아가지 않고 나의 옆에 가만히 앉아있었다."
    "The girl stayed still next to me without going back to the opposite seat."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1861
translate english chapter3_2c5067db:

    # "점원이 주문을 받아들고 다른 곳으로 향하자, 나는 그제야 조그마한 목소리로 말을 꺼냈다."
    "When the clerk took the order and went somewhere else, I finally spoke in a small voice."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1865
translate english chapter3_67eac37e:

    # 나 "“몽블랑 말이야, 먹어 본 기억 있어?”"
    나 "\"Do you remember eating Mont Blanc?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1871
translate english chapter3_49b089c3:

    # voice "voices/gc83.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“아뇨, 그런 기억은 없지만. 이름이 예뻐서 골라 봤어요.”"
    voice "voices/gc83.ogg"
    소녀 "\"No, I don't have such a memory. But I chose it because the name was pretty.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1874
translate english chapter3_ef27f720:

    # voice ""
    # "하긴, 보고 싶은 영화를 고를 때도, 읽고 싶은 책을 고를 때도 늘 그런 이유에서이기는 하지."
    voice ""
    "Well, that was always the reason when she chose a movie she wanted to see or a book she wanted to read."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1878
translate english chapter3_167b1592:

    # "소녀는 고개를 돌려 주변을 바라보았다."
    "The girl turned her head and looked around."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1879
translate english chapter3_f9c4220f:

    # "달콤한 분위기가 인테리어에서도 물씬 느껴지는 것 같은, 아늑한 디자인이라는 생각이 들었다."
    "It seemed like a cozy design that felt a sweet atmosphere from the interior."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1885
translate english chapter3_775600c2:

    # voice "voices/gc84.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“이런 곳에 자주 왔었나요?”"
    voice "voices/gc84.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Did you come to places like this often?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1888
translate english chapter3_bd9471db:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“자주까지는 아니지만, 친한 애가 이런 곳에 종종 같이 가자고 해서. 덕분에 몇 번 따라가 본 적은 있어.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Not too often, but there was a close friend who often asked me to go with her. Thanks to her, I've been there a few times.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1891
translate english chapter3_9c39620a:

    # "나의 발걸음이 굳이 디저트 카페 앞에서 멈춰 선 것도, 유미가 디저트 카페를 좋아해서라는 이유를 포함하고 있었다."
    "The reason why I stopped my footsteps in front of the dessert cafe was also because Yumi liked dessert cafes."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1893
translate english chapter3_949e3c7a:

    # "유미의 취미는 내가 알고 있는 나머지 한 명의 너드 후배와는 달리 여타의 여학생과 비슷하니까, 혹시나 소녀도 이런 걸 내심 좋아하지는 않을까 하는 지극히 개인적인 생각."
    "Yumi's hobby was similar to other girls, unlike the other nerd junior I knew, so I had a very personal thought that maybe the girl secretly liked this kind of thing too."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1895
translate english chapter3_33eba29c:

    # "그리고 지금, 그 지극히 개인적인 생각은 검증의 시간을 얼마 남겨놓지 않고 있었다."
    "And now, that very personal thought was not leaving much time for verification."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1896
translate english chapter3_474806ea:

    # "십여 분 정도가 흐르고, 테이블에는 주문했던 간식들이 놓여진다."
    "After about ten minutes, the snacks we ordered were placed on the table."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1898
translate english chapter3_e4bef7c4:

    # "검증의 시간이었다."
    "It was time for verification."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1906
translate english chapter3_ff2cc1e5:

    # 나 "“먹어보고 나서 무슨 맛인지 나한테도 알려줘.”"
    나 "\"Tell me what it tastes like after you try it.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1907
translate english chapter3_ec6a790b:

    # "접시 위에 놓인 몽블랑을 빤히 바라보고 있던 소녀에게 그런 이야기를 건네고 난 뒤에서야, 소녀는 몽블랑 하나를 집어 들었다."
    "After I said that to the girl who was staring at the Mont Blanc on the plate, she picked up one of them."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1909
translate english chapter3_5a19d105:

    # "나는 레몬티를 빨대로 한 모금 마시며, 소녀의 식후감을 기다렸다."
    "I took a sip of lemon tea with a straw and waited for the girl's aftertaste."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1911
translate english chapter3_9686ff83:

    # 나 "“어때?”"
    나 "\"How about that?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1914
translate english chapter3_d4ae888d:

    # voice "voices/gc85.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“…… 알고 싶지 않았던 맛이네요.”"
    voice "voices/gc85.ogg"
    소녀 "\"... It's a taste I didn't want to know.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1916
translate english chapter3_04f388ff:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“으응……?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Eh...?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1922
translate english chapter3_c4716e2a:

    # "몽블랑을 한 입 베어 문 소녀로부터 마치 반어법은 아닐까 하는 생각이 절로 들만한 감상이 들려왔다."
    "I heard an impression from the girl who bit a bite of Mont Blanc that made me think it might be sarcasm."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1923
translate english chapter3_23d32262:

    # "하지만 소녀의 진지한 어투는 자신의 이야기가 반어법이 아님을 또렷이 알려주고 있었다."
    "But the girl's serious tone clearly told me that her story was not sarcasm."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1924
translate english chapter3_33a6b573:

    # "소녀는 자신의 감상을 진심으로 이야기한 것이었다."
    "The girl was telling her feelings sincerely."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1925
translate english chapter3_afda5393:

    # "소녀답다고 할 수 있는 표현으로 말이다."
    "It was an expression that could be said to be typical of the girl."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1932
translate english chapter3_31aa80d5:

    # voice "voices/gc86.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“왠지 모르게 제가 살아있다고 착각하게끔 하는 맛이에요.”"
    voice "voices/gc86.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It's a taste that makes me feel like I'm alive for some reason.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1936
translate english chapter3_faaf9731:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“여태껏 내가 만들어 줬던 음식은 죽어있다고 확신하게끔 하는 맛이었겠구만.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"The food I've been making for you must have been a taste that made you sure you were dead.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1947
translate english chapter3_1142c5dc:

    # voice "voices/gc87.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“아, 아뇨. 그런 의미는 아니었…….”"
    voice "voices/gc87.ogg"
    소녀 "\"No, no. That's not what I meant...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1949
translate english chapter3_c4319e92:

    # voice ""
    # "당혹스러운 기색을 보이는 소녀."
    voice ""
    "The girl looked flustered."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1956
translate english chapter3_1f823ed7:

    # "평소에 보기 힘들었던 소녀의 당황하는 모습에, 나는 가벼운 웃음을 터뜨렸다."
    "Seeing the girl's embarrassed expression that was hard to see usually, I let out a light laugh."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1958
translate english chapter3_0eb888a4:

    # "누군가가 그런 내 모습을 보았다면, 나는 분명 혼자서 갑자기 웃어대는 이상한 사람이라 여겼겠지."
    "If someone had seen me like that, they would have thought I was a weird person who suddenly laughed by myself."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1959
translate english chapter3_d435b2ba:

    # "소녀도 자신의 반응이 조금 우습게 느껴졌던 건지, 나를 따라 쿡쿡대며 웃음을 지었다."
    "The girl also seemed to find her reaction a bit funny, and followed me with a chuckle."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1962
translate english chapter3_f91471ac:

    # "몽블랑의 단내가 덮인 소녀의 웃음소리는 덧없이 느껴질 정도로 달콤했다."
    "The girl's laughter covered with the sweetness of Mont Blanc was so sweet that it felt fleeting."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1965
translate english chapter3_f228b222:

    # "얼마 지나지 않아 간식이 담겨있던 접시가 바닥을 보였다."
    "Soon the plates with the snacks were empty."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1970
translate english chapter3_5837b4c1:

    # 나 "“더 먹고 싶은 게 있으면 저기서 골라보는 게 어때?”"
    나 "\"How about you pick something else from there if you want more?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1972
translate english chapter3_c6e6db3f:

    # voice "voices/gc88.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“네……? 아, 아뇨. 그럴 필요까진…….”"
    voice "voices/gc88.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Yes...? No, no. I don't need to...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1975
translate english chapter3_76b9cfed:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“왜, 먹고 죽은 귀신이 때깔도 곱다잖아.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Why, a ghost who eats and dies is pretty too.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1980
translate english chapter3_c0dcbcb1:

    # "지금 쓰는 게 맞는 말인지는 잘 모르겠지만."
    "I'm not sure if I'm using the right words."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1981
translate english chapter3_ebdf1afc:

    # "뭐, 어쨌거나."
    "Well, anyway."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1982
translate english chapter3_fc5851ac:

    # "나와 카운터 쪽을 번갈아 바라보며 머뭇대던 소녀가 몸을 일으켰다."
    "The girl got up, looking back and forth between me and the counter."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1984
translate english chapter3_385021c0:

    # voice "voices/gc89.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그런가요? 그럼 딱 하나만 더…….”"
    voice "voices/gc89.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Is that so? Then just one more...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:1987
translate english chapter3_8c741b6a:

    # voice ""
    # "여태껏 가끔씩 볼 수 있었던 소녀의 머뭇거림과는 조금 다른 느낌의 표현이었다."
    voice ""
    "It was a slightly different expression from the hesitation I had seen occasionally."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1990
translate english chapter3_74ae1d93:

    # "여러가지 감정이 조합되어 만들어진 수많은 머뭇거림들 중, 행복에 가까운 감정들이 뒤섞여 만들어진 지금의 표현."
    "Among the many hesitations made by a combination of various emotions, the expression now was mixed with emotions close to happiness."

# game/chapter3.rpy:1991
translate english chapter3_fe9d82cd:

    # "소녀도 내심 그런 감정을 싫어하지는 않는 것 같아 보였다."
    "The girl seemed to not dislike that feeling either."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2019
translate english chapter3_e99fa4aa:

    # "시간이 흘러 카페에 한 명씩 사람이 들어차기 시작하자, 우리는 예정했던 대로 자리에서 일어나 밖으로 향했다."
    "As time passed and people started to come into the cafe one by one, we got up from our seats and headed outside as planned."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2020
translate english chapter3_6a89e092:

    # "카페를 나서는 나의 등 뒤로 점원의 따가운 시선이 느껴졌다."
    "I felt the clerk's sharp eyes behind me as I left the cafe."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2021
translate english chapter3_47ee891f:

    # "분명 소녀와 이야기를 나누는 나의 모습이 중얼중얼 혼잣말을 늘어놓는 이상한 사람처럼 보였던 거겠지."
    "It must have looked like a weird person who muttered to himself while talking to the girl."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2025
translate english chapter3_cb2eb22b:

    # 나 "“하굣길이라 그런지 사람이 많네.”"
    나 "\"There are a lot of people because it's the way home from school.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2029
translate english chapter3_bed6176c:

    # "사람을 피해 카페 밖으로 나온 거라고 하기엔, 거리에도 제법 많은 사람들이 걸어다니고 있었다."
    "There were quite a lot of people walking on the street, too, not just because we came out of the cafe to avoid people."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2030
translate english chapter3_48718c50:

    # "인파에 섞여 길을 걸으며, 소녀는 이리저리 고개를 돌려 자신을 스쳐 지나가는 시선을 피했다."
    "Walking along the street among the crowd, the girl turned her head this way and that to avoid the eyes that passed by her."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2035
translate english chapter3_f1909ea3:

    # "그러다 잠시, 이곳저곳 타인의 시선이 닿지 않는 장소를 향하던 소녀의 눈길이 어느 한 자리에 머무른다."
    "Then for a moment, the girl's eyes that were looking for a place where no one's eyes could reach stayed in one place."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2036
translate english chapter3_09ef7d5a:

    # "잠시 다른 쪽으로 시선이 향하곤 했지만, 네댓 발걸음을 떼는 동안 소녀의 시선은 대부분 한 곳에 머물러 있었다."
    "She looked away for a while, but for most of the time she walked four steps, her eyes stayed in one place."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2040
translate english chapter3_2d037781:

    # "소녀를 따라 그곳을 바라보았다."
    "I looked at the place following the girl."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2050
translate english chapter3_a8119b2c:

    # "골목길로 접어드는 자리에 위치한 자그마한 게임 센터."
    "A small game center located at the corner of an alley."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2051
translate english chapter3_88711c89:

    # "소녀에게 이런 취미가 있다는 생각은 들지 않았다."
    "I didn't think the girl had such a hobby."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2060
translate english chapter3_bdd8624a:

    # "몇 걸음 더 게임 센터 쪽으로 가까워지자, 나는 그제야 소녀가 바라보고 있던 것이 무엇이었는지 알아챌 수 있었다."
    "As I got closer to the game center a few steps more, I finally realized what the girl was looking at."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2065
translate english chapter3_7ca8c9d9:

    # "나는 소녀의 눈길이 닿은 그곳에 발걸음을 우뚝 멈춰 세웠다."
    "I stopped my footsteps abruptly at the place where the girl's eyes met."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2066
translate english chapter3_b1fe70a2:

    # 나 "“저 인형, 갖고 싶은 거야?”"
    나 "\"Do you want that doll?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2072
translate english chapter3_ce768069:

    # voice "voices/gc90.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“아, 아뇨. 딱히 그런 건…….”"
    voice "voices/gc90.ogg"
    소녀 "\"No, no. Not really...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2081
translate english chapter3_4615b173:

    # voice ""
    # "나의 물음에 소녀는 머쓱한 티를 잔뜩 내며 대답을 건넸다."
    voice ""
    "The girl answered with a lot of awkwardness at my question."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2083
translate english chapter3_88183743:

    # "소녀에게 있어 타인의 눈동자란 운명의 창이듯, 내게 있어 소녀의 눈동자는 감정의 창이다."
    "As the eyes of others were like the window of fate for the girl, the eyes of the girl were the window of emotion for me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2084
translate english chapter3_aded1981:

    # "소녀도 이를 알고 있었는지, 고개를 돌려 나의 눈길을 피했다."
    "The girl knew this too, and turned her head to avoid my eyes."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2088
translate english chapter3_1bcefe5e:

    # "하지만 이내 소녀의 시선은 한 바퀴를 돌아, 원래의 자리로 돌아온다."
    "But soon her eyes came back to their original place after a round."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2089
translate english chapter3_4c17c67a:

    # "소녀가 바라보고 있던 건 각양각색의 인형이 들어있는 인형 뽑기 기계였다."
    "What the girl was looking at was a claw machine with various dolls inside."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2092
translate english chapter3_14127ed2:

    # "여러모로 중학생 답지 않은 면모를 보이는 소녀였지만, 어쩌면 그런 부분 하나하나를 모아 평균을 내어 본다면 정확히 중학생 정도로 맞아 떨어질지도 모르겠다는 생각이 들었다."
    "The girl showed aspects that were not like a middle school student in many ways, but I thought that maybe if I averaged out each of those aspects, it would be exactly like a middle school student."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2100
translate english ecg4_label_a919978b:

    # 나 "“우리, 조금만 더 시간을 낭비하는 건 어때?”"
    나 "\"How about we waste some more time?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2104
translate english ecg4_label_cd932e82:

    # voice "voices/gc91.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그래도 괜찮겠어요?”"
    voice "voices/gc91.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Are you sure that's okay?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2106
translate english ecg4_label_8afa37c5:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“어차피 어둑어둑해지기 전까지 이런 외부인 티 나는 차림으로 학교에 들어가면 경비 아저씨한테 곧장 의심받을 테고.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Anyway, if we go to school in this outfit that looks like an outsider before it gets dark, we'll be immediately suspected by the security guard.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2109
translate english ecg4_label_7fda96e8:

    # voice "voices/gc92.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그렇다면…… 어쩔 수 없죠.”"
    voice "voices/gc92.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Then... I guess we have no choice.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2115
translate english ecg4_label_03d1ad87:

    # voice ""
    # "나는 소녀를 이끌고 인형 뽑기 기계 앞으로 향했다."
    voice ""
    "I led the girl to the front of the claw machine."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2117
translate english ecg4_label_f9f17873:

    # "정말 어쩔 수 없어서 그러는 거라며, 소녀는 순순히 나의 뒤를 따랐다."
    "The girl followed me obediently, saying that she had no choice."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2118
translate english ecg4_label_24a7bf6f:

    # "사람은 그리 많지 않았다."
    "There weren't many people."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2119
translate english ecg4_label_36395667:

    # "오히려 한적하다는 편이 더 정확하겠지."
    "It would be more accurate to say that it was rather quiet."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2121
translate english ecg4_label_fe5fc6c5:

    # "인형 뽑기 기계 앞에 선 나는 소녀에게 꽤나 자신만만한 목소리로 말했다."
    "Standing in front of the claw machine, I said to the girl in a rather confident voice."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2124
translate english ecg4_label_767bb672:

    # 나 "“뭘로 뽑아줄까?”"
    나 "\"What do you want me to get for you?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2125
translate english ecg4_label_82e431b9:

    # voice "voices/gc93.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“…… 저기, 아래쪽에 보이는 곰인형으로 부탁해요.”"
    voice "voices/gc93.ogg"
    소녀 "\"... There, can you please get me the teddy bear at the bottom?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2127
translate english ecg4_label_8556873c:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀가 가리킨 건 인형 뽑기 기계 아래편에 놓여있는 흰색 곰인형이었다."
    voice ""
    "The girl pointed to a white teddy bear that was placed at the bottom of the claw machine."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2141
translate english ecg4_label_65d196bb:

    # 나 "“우왓, 아까워.”"
    나 "\"Wow, what a waste.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2148
translate english ecg4_label_fa2ef543:

    # 소녀 "“…….”"
    소녀 "\"...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2154
translate english ecg4_label_10195403:

    # 나 "“아아아…… 뭐 저기서 떨어져버리냐.”"
    나 "\"Ahhh... Why did it fall from there?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2155
translate english ecg4_label_30a6a72b:

    # 소녀 "“………….”"
    소녀 "\".........\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2157
translate english ecg4_label_70044eef:

    # "금방 뽑아낼 수 있을 줄 알았던 곰인형은 번번이 집게손 끝에서 아슬아슬하게 떨어져버렸다."
    "The teddy bear that I thought I could get out easily fell off the tip of the claw hand every time."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2158
translate english ecg4_label_a8d02254:

    # "처음엔 단순히 시간을 때우기 위해 인형 뽑기 기계로 코인을 넣었던 거였지만, 이젠 자존심 문제에 가까웠다."
    "At first, I just put coins into the claw machine to kill time, but now it was almost a matter of pride."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2159
translate english ecg4_label_ac6d29a5:

    # "나의 옆에 선 소녀는 인형이 집게손에서 떨어질 때마다 안타까운 반응을 보여주고 있었다."
    "The girl standing next to me showed a regretful reaction every time the doll fell from the claw hand."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2160
translate english ecg4_label_274df1b6:

    # "물론 얼마 정도 시간이 지나고 나자 안타까움이 묻어나야 할 반응에서는 안쓰러움이 그 자리를 대신했지만 말이다."
    "Of course, after some time passed, pity replaced the reaction that should have been regretful."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2162
translate english ecg4_label_fb24318b:

    # "결국 학교에 도착한 건 어슴푸레한 어둠이 발끝을 감싸기 시작했을 무렵이었다."
    "We finally arrived at school when the faint darkness began to wrap around our feet."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2170
translate english ecg4_label_768ec48a:

    # voice "voices/gc94.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“인형 하나 뽑는다고 얼마나 쓴 거예요?”"
    voice "voices/gc94.ogg"
    소녀 "\"How much did you spend on getting one doll?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2175
translate english ecg4_label_dca54884:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“걱정 마. 그리 많이는 안 썼으니까.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Don't worry. I didn't spend that much.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2184
translate english ecg4_label_f7aacce7:

    # "소녀의 손에는 그녀가 원했던 새하얀 곰인형이 쥐어져 있었지만, 상처뿐인 영광이라는 말이 딱 어울려 보였다."
    "The girl had the white teddy bear she wanted in her hand, but it looked like a perfect fit for the phrase 'a glory full of wounds'."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2185
translate english ecg4_label_7ba48171:

    # "철없는 동생을 나무라는 듯한 소녀의 말투에 나는 머쓱한 웃음으로 일관하며 교문 근처를 서성였다."
    "I lingered near the school gate with a sheepish smile, as if scolding a childish younger sibling, at the girl's tone of voice."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2190
translate english ecg4_label_c62f1b92:

    # "최대한 경비의 감시를 받지 않으며 교내로 들어갈 수 있는 최적의 장소가 어디일까."
    "Where would be the best place to enter the school without being watched by the security guard?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:2191
translate english ecg4_label_735c34a6:

    # "해답은 의외로 금세 찾을 수 있었다."
    "The answer was surprisingly easy to find."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2194
translate english ecg4_label_6f0bd62c:

    # 나 "“여기, 넘어갈 수 있겠어?”"
    나 "\"Here, can you get over this?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2196
translate english ecg4_label_3ecc6765:

    # "주차장과 연결된 학교 건물 뒤편의 담자락을 시범 삼아 넘어 보이며, 나는 소녀에게 물었다."
    "I asked the girl as I showed her how to jump over the wall behind the school building connected to the parking lot."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2203
translate english ecg4_label_d650549d:

    # voice "voices/gc95.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“불량학생이네요. 담 넘는 거, 엄청 능숙해 보이는걸요.”"
    voice "voices/gc95.ogg"
    소녀 "\"You're a bad student. Jumping over the wall, you look very skilled.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2205
translate english ecg4_label_c32ef28d:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그러는 너도, 능숙해 보이는데?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"You look skilled too, don't you?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2208
translate english ecg4_label_dafe37f6:

    # voice "voices/gc96.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“기분 탓일 뿐이에요.”"
    voice "voices/gc96.ogg"
    소녀 "\"It's just your imagination.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2214
translate english ecg4_label_c314ef8f:

    # voice ""
    # "그런 이야기를 하며, 소녀는 자신의 눈높이 정도 되는 담장에서 폴짝 뛰어내렸다."
    voice ""
    "Saying that, the girl jumped off the wall that was about her eye level."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2216
translate english ecg4_label_e35c0dec:

    # voice "voices/gc97.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“이제 어디로 가면 되나요?”"
    voice "voices/gc97.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Where do we go now?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2218
translate english ecg4_label_1654a8b0:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“옥상 쪽으로 갈 거야.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"We're going to the rooftop.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2221
translate english ecg4_label_1def844a:

    # voice "voices/gc98.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“아 맞다. 학교 옥상에서 뛰어내렸다고 했죠.”"
    voice "voices/gc98.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Oh right. You said you jumped off the school roof.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2224
translate english ecg4_label_c90f1eb4:

    # voice ""
    # "낮의 학교에서 들려오던 시끌벅적함은 어디로 가고, 밤을 맞이하는 학교에 남아있는 건 오직 고요함뿐이었다."
    voice ""
    "The noise that came from the school during the day was gone, and all that was left in the school at night was silence."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2228
translate english ecg4_label_2e1980f0:

    # "나는 발걸음 소리를 최대한 죽여가며 소녀와 함께 학교 옥상으로 향했다."
    "I walked to the school roof with the girl, trying to make as little noise as possible."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2229
translate english ecg4_label_b4173ba2:

    # "어둠이 슬슬 깔리기 시작하는 복도의 분위기는 마치 게임 속으로 들어온 듯한 느낌이기도 했다."
    "The atmosphere of the corridor that began to darken was like entering a game."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2231
translate english ecg4_label_67125da6:

    # "계단을 걸어 올라가며 주변을 슬쩍 기웃거려 보았지만, 학교 건물 안에 있는 사람은 오직 나밖에 없는 모양이었다."
    "I glanced around as I walked up the stairs, but it seemed that I was the only person in the school building."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2233
translate english ecg4_label_34fc98ae:

    # "다들 이미 퇴근을 한 뒤인지, 교무실에서도 아무런 인기척이 느껴지지 않았으니 말이다."
    "Everyone must have left already, as I didn't feel any sign of life from the staff room."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2240
translate english ecg4_label_5d953538:

    # "계단을 오르는 발걸음 소리가 옥상으로 향하는 마지막 길목 앞에서 끊어졌다."
    "The sound of footsteps climbing the stairs stopped in front of the last corner leading to the roof."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2241
translate english ecg4_label_a1731941:

    # "옥상으로 이어지는 문 앞에 선 나는, 당혹스러운 기색을 내비치는 수밖에 없었다."
    "I stood in front of the door leading to the roof, showing a bewildered expression."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2247
translate english ecg4_label_2c671f5a:

    # 나 "“닫혀있네.”"
    나 "\"It's closed.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2249
translate english ecg4_label_173d865a:

    # voice "voices/gc99.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그런 일도 있었으니, 닫혀있을 만도 하지 않을까요?”"
    voice "voices/gc99.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Maybe it's closed because of what happened?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2259
translate english ecg4_label_767667b8:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“하긴, 그렇겠다.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Yeah, I guess so.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2261
translate english ecg4_label_397030c0:

    # "문은 굳게 잠겨 있었다."
    "The door was firmly locked."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2267
translate english ecg4_label_cf5904e8:

    # "손잡이에 손을 갖다 대자 묻어있던 먼지 조각이 만져졌다."
    "When I touched the handle, I felt the dust debris that was stuck on it."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2268
translate english ecg4_label_4ba47ac1:

    # "그런 일이 있고 난 뒤로부터 이 정도의 시간이 흘렀다는 걸 알려주는 흔적이었다."
    "It was a sign that this much time had passed since that incident."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2274
translate english ecg4_label_370a17d6:

    # voice "voices/gc100.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그럼 이제 어떡하죠?”"
    voice "voices/gc100.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Then what do we do now?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2281
translate english ecg4_label_de91b5a2:

    # voice ""
    # "‘어쩔 수 없네요’라고 말하는 듯한 소녀의 눈길이 내게 닿는다."
    voice ""
    "The girl's eyes met mine, as if saying 'we have no choice'."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2286
translate english ecg4_label_96269440:

    # "어쩔 수 없네. 돌아가야겠다."
    "We have no choice. We have to go back."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2287
translate english ecg4_label_14e2faf9:

    # "라고 대답하며 발걸음을 돌리는 것이 일반적인 나의 반응이었겠지만."
    "That would have been my usual response, turning my footsteps around."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2292
translate english ecg4_label_d54e81d8:

    # 나 "“교무실에 열쇠함이 있지 않을까?”"
    나 "\"Isn't there a key box in the staff room?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2294
translate english ecg4_label_c986ce25:

    # voice "voices/gc101.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“…… 나쁜 짓은 안 한다지 않았나요?”"
    voice "voices/gc101.ogg"
    소녀 "\"... Didn't you say you wouldn't do anything bad?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2296
translate english ecg4_label_a11c0ab5:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“으음…… 내가 그랬었나.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Hmm... Did I say that?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2301
translate english ecg4_label_ff7996c1:

    # "가끔, 그런 날이 있다."
    "Sometimes, there are such days."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2302
translate english ecg4_label_b8392046:

    # "이렇게 평소와는 엇나가고 싶은 날이."
    "Days when you want to deviate from the usual."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2306
translate english ecg4_label_12afdcae:

    # 나 "“그래서 말인데. 옥상 열쇠, 네가 찾아와 줄 수 있겠어?”"
    나 "\"So, can you find and bring the rooftop key?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2307
translate english ecg4_label_260a75d9:

    # voice "voices/gc102.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“알겠어요.”"
    voice "voices/gc102.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Okay.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2309
translate english ecg4_label_1e82e49e:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀는 난간 아래쪽으로 고개를 내밀어 주변을 살피더니, 이내 교무실로 향했다."
    voice ""
    "The girl peered around by leaning over the balustrade, then headed towards the staff room."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2314
translate english ecg4_label_fdb0f92c:

    # "소녀가 아래층으로 내려가 열쇠를 찾는 동안, 나는 쥐 죽은 듯 조용히 시간을 보내는 것밖에는 달리 할 일이 없었다."
    "While the girl went downstairs to find the key, I had nothing else to do but pass the time in silence as if I were dead."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2316
translate english ecg4_label_ca08c5d5:

    # "조용했다."
    "It was quiet."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2317
translate english ecg4_label_4b530797:

    # "내뱉는 숨소리, 침 삼키는 소리, 그리고 내 안의 누군가가 나를 부르는 소리가 또렷이 들려오기 시작했다."
    "The sound of my breath exhaling, swallowing saliva, and someone inside me calling out to me started to become clearly audible."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2324
translate english ecg4_label_aad84167:

    # "오랜만이었다."
    "It had been a long time."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2325
translate english ecg4_label_d33d3df0:

    # "밤의 학교에서 이런 소리를 듣는 것은."
    "Hearing such sounds in a school at night."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2331
translate english ecg4_label_25ff12c6:

    # "문 앞에 서서는 아무것도 하지 않은 채 몇 분 정도를 흘려 보냈던 걸까."
    "I wonder how many minutes I wasted standing in front of the door without doing anything."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2333
translate english ecg4_label_0d6bdb1c:

    # "들려오는 소리에 가만히 귀를 기울이던 중, 아래층에서 이질감이 느껴지는 발걸음 소리가 들려왔다."
    "As I listened to the sounds coming from inside, I heard a strange sound of footsteps from downstairs."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2335
translate english ecg4_label_e8ecc148:

    # "난간 아래로 고개를 내밀자 그대로 위쪽을 바라보며 계단을 걸어 올라오던 소녀와 눈이 마주친다."
    "As I leaned my head over the balustrade, I met eyes with the girl who was walking up the stairs looking up at me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2337
translate english ecg4_label_3fa94f1d:

    # "소녀는 내게 열쇠를 건넸다."
    "\"Here's the key.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2342
translate english ecg4_label_672f539f:

    # "소녀가 건넨 열쇠에는 그녀에게서 느껴지던 한기가 그대로 묻어 있었다."
    "The key that the girl handed me had the same coldness that I felt from her."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2346
translate english ecg4_label_1624b708:

    # "문이 열리며 삐걱대는 소리가 순식간에 사방으로 흩어졌다."
    "The sound of the door creaking open scattered around in an instant."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2347
translate english ecg4_label_a34fcda5:

    # "혹시나 하는 생각에 주변을 살폈지만, 다행히 인기척은 전혀 느껴지지 않았다."
    "I looked around with a slight worry, but fortunately I didn't feel any signs of life."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2360
translate english ecg4_label_cbba197d:

    # "문틈으로는 밤하늘과 맞닿은 시멘트 재질의 공간이 펼쳐져 있었다."
    "Through the gap of the door, a cement space that touched the night sky was spread out."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2362
translate english ecg4_label_baad7212:

    # "미적지근한 여름의 바람이 불어오는 곳으로, 나와 소녀는 발걸음을 내딛었다."
    "The girl and I stepped into the place where the lukewarm summer wind blew."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2364
translate english ecg4_label_977949e0:

    # "익숙한 바람이라는 생각이 들었다."
    "It felt like a familiar wind."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2376
translate english ecg5_label_f136db5c:

    # voice "voices/gc103.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“아무것도 없네요.”"
    voice "voices/gc103.ogg"
    소녀 "\"There's nothing here.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2379
translate english ecg5_label_82f31643:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그야, 옥상일 뿐이니까.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Well, it's just a rooftop.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2381
translate english ecg5_label_69ff8cb7:

    # "텅 빈 옥상을 바라본 소녀의 감상이 전해진다."
    "The girl's impression of the empty rooftop was conveyed."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2386
translate english ecg5_label_b4802214:

    # "나는 소녀와 함께 난간 쪽으로 터벅터벅 걸어갔다."
    "I walked with the girl to the balustrade."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2387
translate english ecg5_label_708c58d5:

    # "차가운 철제 난간대에 팔을 얹으며 익숙하다는 감각을 느꼈다."
    "I felt a familiar sensation as I rested my arm on the cold iron railing."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2393
translate english ecg5_label_f1a9f928:

    # "시선 아래로 펼쳐지는 적당한 배율의 풍경부터 마치 소리 없는 아우성처럼 산들산들 불어오는 바람까지."
    "From the scenery below with a moderate scale to the wind that blew like a soundless roar."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2395
translate english ecg5_label_4f49b5d5:

    # "익숙하디 익숙한 감각에, 오늘따라 나답지 않은 선택을 연발한 이유도 어렴풋이 알 것 같다는 생각이 들었다."
    "With the familiar feeling, I had a vague idea of why I made some choices that were unlike me today."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2396
translate english ecg5_label_5f41656d:

    # "가만히 불어오는 바람을 느끼며, 나는 소녀와 함께 가만히 그 순간을 흘려 보내고 있었다."
    "Feeling the wind quietly blowing, I was letting go of that moment with the girl."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2398
translate english ecg5_label_7527717f:

    # "무엇을 위해 이곳으로 온 건지도 잠시 잊은 채 말이다."
    "Forgetting for a moment why I came here."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2405
translate english ecg5_label_fe0ff98c:

    # voice "voices/gc104.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“{color=#00ccff}누군가가 당신에게 ‘죽고 싶다’라고 이야기한다면, 그땐 어쩔 건가요?{/color}”"
    voice "voices/gc104.ogg"
    소녀 "\"{color=#00ccff}What would you do if someone told you 'I want to die'?{/color}\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2407
translate english ecg5_label_640c5736:

    # voice ""
    # "나의 옆에서 밤하늘을 멍하니 바라보고 있던 소녀가, 대뜸 엉뚱한 이야기를 꺼냈다. "
    voice ""
    "The girl who was staring blankly at the night sky next to me suddenly brought up a strange topic."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2409
translate english ecg5_label_66513ae5:

    # "엉뚱한 이야기였을 것이다. "
    "It must have been a strange topic."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2410
translate english ecg5_label_57473f5d:

    # "대뜸 그런 이야기를 꺼내면 누구라도 엉뚱한 이야기라 생각할 테니 말이다. "
    "Anyone would think it was a strange topic if you suddenly brought it up."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2411
translate english ecg5_label_2b39ac75:

    # "하지만 어째서인지, 심장에서부터 무언가가 쿵쿵 울려 퍼지고 있었다."
    "But for some reason, something was pounding in my heart."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2413
translate english ecg5_label_fbb7d75c:

    # 나 "“글쎄.”"
    나 "\"I don't know.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2415
translate english ecg5_label_4e95ae89:

    # voice "voices/gc105.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“하긴, 이런 이야기 저랑 해봤자 아무런 의미도 없겠죠.”"
    voice "voices/gc105.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Well, I guess there's no point in talking about this with me.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2417
translate english ecg5_label_1fbf0303:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“…….”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2420
translate english ecg5_label_4d96a76a:

    # "자조하는 듯한 목소리로, 소녀가 허무한 표정을 지었다."
    "The girl made a hollow expression with a self-mocking voice."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2422
translate english ecg5_label_6978d54f:

    # voice "voices/gc106.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“이곳에서 떨어진 여학생은 죽기 전까지도 그 이야기를 되새겼나 봐요.”"
    voice "voices/gc106.ogg"
    소녀 "\"The girl who fell from here must have repeated that story until she died.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2425
translate english ecg5_label_784526b0:

    # voice ""
    # "그랬던 건가."
    voice ""
    "Was that so?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:2428
translate english ecg5_label_7dd26382:

    # "밤하늘을 보고 있는 줄로만 알았던 소녀의 눈동자에는, 달빛 대신 죽음의 색이 새겨졌던 모양이었다."
    "The girl's eyes, which I thought were looking at the night sky, had the color of death instead of moonlight."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2429
translate english ecg5_label_fde04d3d:

    # "소녀는 아무렇지도 않은 척, 이야기를 계속 이어갔다."
    "The girl acted as if nothing happened and continued the story."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2432
translate english ecg5_label_1f04eaa8:

    # voice "voices/gc107.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“자기가 누군가에게 건넨 '죽고 싶다'라는 말에 대한 대답을요.”"
    voice "voices/gc107.ogg"
    소녀 "\"The answer to the 'I want to die' that she gave to someone.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2435
translate english ecg5_label_4c24461b:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“어떤 대답을 들었길래?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"What answer did you hear?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2440
translate english ecg5_label_e7680f10:

    # voice "voices/gc108.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“글쎄요. 저도 잘 모르겠어요. 하지만 그 여학생이 내린 결론은, 아무래도 '나는 죽어도 괜찮다'였던가 봐요.”"
    voice "voices/gc108.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I don't know. I'm not sure. But the conclusion that the girl came to was, I guess, 'I'm fine even if I die.'\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2442
translate english ecg5_label_58a114ae:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“으응…….”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Ugh...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2446
translate english ecg5_label_641c43c9:

    # voice "voices/gc109.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“잘 모르겠어요. 정말 아무것도 아닌 것 같은 기분이에요.”"
    voice "voices/gc109.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I don't know. It feels like nothing at all.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2448
translate english ecg5_label_862b0b44:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“그렇구나.”"
    voice ""
    나 "'I see.'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:2450
translate english ecg5_label_b627ab27:

    # voice "voices/gc110.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“…… 조금만 더 시간을 낭비하다 갈까요?”"
    voice "voices/gc110.ogg"
    소녀 "\"...Shall we waste some more time before we go?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2455
translate english ecg5_label_5f5dad13:

    # voice ""
    # "의도치 않게 소녀의 팔이 나의 팔꿈치에 닿는다."
    voice ""
    "The girl's arm unintentionally touched my elbow."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2460
translate english ecg5_label_1d2a6c07:

    # "심장은 지치지도 않고 무언의 아우성을 질러대고 있었다."
    "My heart was screaming without getting tired."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2461
translate english ecg5_label_3d3a4d5d:

    # "익숙한 기분이 들었다. "
    "It felt familiar."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2462
translate english ecg5_label_2e8abe50:

    # "매번, 이렇게 옥상에 앉아있으면 외계인이 내게 교신을 보내듯 누군가의 목소리가 들렸으니까."
    "Every time, when I sat on the rooftop like this, I heard someone's voice as if an alien was sending me a message."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2467
translate english ecg5_label_b7743371:

    # "그날의 일처럼, 내게서 익숙한 선이 그려졌다."
    "Like that day, a familiar line was drawn from me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2468
translate english ecg5_label_660d9dce:

    # "다만, 한 가지 다른 점이 있었다."
    "But there was one difference."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2470
translate english ecg5_label_0456cc5e:

    # "언제나 방향을 잃고 뭉개지던 목소리가 이번엔 주파수를 올바르게 잡은 라디오의 음성처럼 차분히 들려왔다."
    "The voice that always lost direction and became cloudy sounded calm like a radio voice that caught the right frequency."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2471
translate english ecg5_label_40ced738:

    # "천천히 선이 이어지기 시작했다."
    "The line slowly began to connect."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2473
translate english ecg5_label_5b001578:

    # "그 선의 도착지점은 다름 아닌, 나의 옆에 앉아있던 소녀였다."
    "The destination of the line was none other than the girl sitting next to me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2478
translate english ecg5_label_bafd3e32:

    # "알 수 없었다."
    "I didn't know."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2479
translate english ecg5_label_2b765b45:

    # "이 이어짐이 의미하는 바가 무엇이었는지. "
    "What this connection meant."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2482
translate english ecg5_label_ce915d4e:

    # "낮과 밤이 이어지듯, 소녀와의 이어짐에서 떠올린 기억은 또다시 그때의 일이었다."
    "As day and night connected, the memory that came to mind from the connection with the girl was again that time."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2483
translate english ecg5_label_b8800f68:

    # "한여름 밤의 바람을 맞으며 떠올린 기억은, 또다시 그때의 추억이었다."
    "The memory that came to mind in the midsummer night breeze was again that reminiscence."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2484
translate english ecg5_label_60adc061:

    # "지금은 막연해져 버린 꿈이라는 것이 또렷했을 그 무렵의 이야기."
    "The story from when the now vague dream was clear."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2486
translate english ecg5_label_be0f6e05:

    # who "“들었어? 우리 학교 야구부가 처음으로 전국대회에 진출했다는 거?”"
    who "\"Did you hear? Our school's baseball team made it to the national tournament for the first time?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2487
translate english ecg5_label_504b0136:

    # who "“어제 최종 예선전 구경했는데, 선발로 나온 3학년 선배 말이야. 완전 멋져보인 거 있지?!”"
    who "\"I watched the final qualifying match yesterday, and the third-year senpai who came out as the starter. He looked so cool, you know?!\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2491
translate english ecg5_label_64eccd32:

    # "중학교 3학년생이었던 과거의 나는, 전국대회에서 우승하겠다는 일념만으로 마운드에서 공을 던진 모양이었다."
    "The past me who was a third-year middle school student threw the ball from the mound with the sole idea of winning the national tournament."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2495
translate english ecg5_label_1ddbab7f:

    # "그해 여름은, 꼭 나를 중심으로 돌아가고 있는 것만 같았다."
    "That summer, it seemed like everything was revolving around me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2496
translate english ecg5_label_72adf405:

    # "유미에게서 느껴졌던 그 기분 좋은 두근거림이, 과거의 내게서도 느껴지고 있었다."
    "The pleasant throbbing that I felt from Yumi, I also felt it from the past me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2497
translate english ecg5_label_ed0d0462:

    # "무언가를 위해."
    "For something."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2501
translate english ecg5_label_a604741e:

    # "그리고 누군가를 위해."
    "And for someone."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2502
translate english ecg5_label_e03ed132:

    # "…… 분명 기억하기론, 결승까지 올라갔던 것 같은데."
    "...I'm sure I remember, I think I made it to the final."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2505
translate english ecg5_label_64ea6830:

    # "귓가에 맴도는 응원 소리가 익숙하게 느껴졌다."
    "The cheering sound in my ears felt familiar."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2507
translate english ecg5_label_396673fa:

    # 나 "“…….”"
    나 "\"...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2511
translate english ecg5_label_b0074bbd:

    # "익숙한 시선과 음성."
    "Familiar eyes and voice."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2512
translate english ecg5_label_289086c5:

    # "따뜻한 목소리와 시선이 흐릿한 기억에 뒤섞여 사라져간다."
    "The warm voice and eyes disappeared mixed with the blurry memory."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2513
translate english ecg5_label_4b624fd5:

    # "그 목소리가 나의 귓가를 맴돌았지만, 라디오를 막 켰을 때 흘러나오는 항상 듣던 채널의 주파수인 것처럼 익숙한 목소리라는 느낌만이 애매하게 들 뿐이었다."
    "That voice lingered in my ears, but it only felt vaguely familiar like the voice of the always-listened channel's frequency when I just turned on the radio."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2518
translate english ecg5_label_64021e1d:

    # "소녀와 나는 그로부터 몇 분 정도를 더 말없이 난간대에 기대어 시간을 보냈다."
    "The girl and I spent some more time leaning on the balustrade without saying a word."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2519
translate english ecg5_label_ab3d8e08:

    # "조금만 더, 조금만 더 이대로 있고 싶다는 생각이 나로부터 뻗어가던 직선처럼 이어졌지만, 먼저 난간대에서 손을 뗀 건 소녀 쪽이었다."
    "I wanted to stay like this for a little longer, a little longer, like the line that extended from me, but the one who let go of the balustrade first was the girl."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2520
translate english ecg5_label_ff8a306f:

    # "소녀가 난간대에서 손을 떼자, 서로를 종이컵 무전기처럼 이어주던 실도 그대로 툭 끊어져 버렸다."
    "As the girl let go of the balustrade, the thread that connected us like a paper cup phone also snapped."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2523
translate english ecg5_label_f483caca:

    # "난간대에서 손을 떼고 계단을 내려오기 시작할 무렵, 소녀가 넌지시 이야기를 꺼냈다."
    "As she let go of the balustrade and started to go down the stairs, the girl casually brought up a topic."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2525
translate english ecg5_label_8771fcc5:

    # voice "voices/gc111.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“저, 기억나는 사람이 있어요.”"
    voice "voices/gc111.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I remember someone.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2527
translate english ecg5_label_a444a887:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“정말? 그게 누군데?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Really? Who is it?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2536
translate english ecg5_label_319bdc1a:

    # voice "voices/gc112.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“말 그대로예요. 기억나는 사람이 있다. 그뿐이에요.”"
    voice "voices/gc112.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Just like I said. I remember someone. That's all.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2539
translate english ecg5_label_ff0e613d:

    # voice ""
    # "그렇게 이야기하고는, 소녀는 나의 손을 슬며시 붙잡았다."
    voice ""
    "As she said that, the girl gently grabbed my hand."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2544
translate english ecg5_label_bb0dad41:

    # "그녀의 한기가 손을 타고 느껴졌다."
    "I felt her coldness through my hand."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2546
translate english ecg5_label_a7c65786:

    # "손끝에 느껴지는 감촉과 어울리는 침묵이 역에 도착할 때까지 우리의 주변을 맴돌았다."
    "The silence that matched the feeling at my fingertips lingered around us until we arrived at the station."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2560
translate english ecg5_label_868af227:

    # "소녀가 다시 입을 연 건, 열차에서 내려 A구역 터미널 의자에 앉아 집 근처까지 가는 호버크라프트를 기다리고 있던 때였다."
    "The girl opened her mouth again when we got off the train and sat on a terminal chair in A district, waiting for a hovercraft that would take us near home."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2563
translate english ecg5_label_1ca92a0e:

    # voice "voices/gc113.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“저 있죠, 이름도, 생김새도, 무엇하나 제대로 기억나는 건 없어도 '있었다'라는 것만큼은 또렷이 기억나는 누군가가 있어요.”"
    voice "voices/gc113.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I have someone, who I don't remember anything clearly, not their name, not their appearance, but I remember vividly that they 'existed.'\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2565
translate english ecg5_label_0d2bbe3a:

    # voice ""
    # "나는 소녀의 말을 두 번 정도 곱씹고 나서야 의미를 제대로 파악할 수 있었다."
    voice ""
    "I had to chew on the girl's words twice before I could understand the meaning properly."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2570
translate english ecg5_label_d2a39a52:

    # 나 "“즉, 네가 기억하는 건 그 사람의 존재뿐이라는 거네.”"
    나 "\"So, what you remember is just their existence.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2574
translate english ecg5_label_ca4a1fce:

    # voice "voices/gc114.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“정확히는, 온기지만요.”"
    voice "voices/gc114.ogg"
    소녀 "\"To be precise, warmth.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2576
translate english ecg5_label_52c145b0:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“온기?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Warmth?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2579
translate english ecg5_label_15d44a30:

    # voice "voices/gc115.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“네. 따뜻함이라고나 할까. 난간대에서 느껴지던 것과는 정반대의 감각 말이에요.”"
    voice "voices/gc115.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Yes. The opposite of what I felt on the balustrade.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2581
translate english ecg5_label_85cfdf6d:

    # 나 "“무슨 느낌인지 알 것 같아.”"
    나 "\"I think I know what you mean.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2585
translate english ecg5_label_357a1b82:

    # "모호한 대답과 함께 나는 고개를 끄덕였다."
    "With a vague answer, I nodded my head."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2587
translate english ecg5_label_5bf57ac3:

    # voice "voices/gc116.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“잘 기억나진 않지만, 저는 그 온기를 무척이나 좋아했던 것 같아요.”"
    voice "voices/gc116.ogg"
    소녀 "\"I don't remember well, but I think I really liked that warmth.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2589
translate english ecg5_label_f715c793:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“얼마나?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"How much?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2597
translate english ecg5_label_f5ea5543:

    # voice "voices/gc117.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“살아있어서 다행이라고 느낄 정도로요.”"
    voice "voices/gc117.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Enough to feel glad that I was alive.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2599
translate english ecg5_label_bdd9a630:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“엄청 좋아했나 보네.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"You must have liked it a lot.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2604
translate english ecg5_label_01520896:

    # voice "voices/gc118.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그렇죠.”"
    voice "voices/gc118.ogg"
    소녀 "\"That's right.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2609
translate english ecg5_label_0a2dead7:

    # voice ""
    # "고개를 숙이고는 버릇처럼 다리를 위아래로 까닥이는 소녀."
    voice ""
    "The girl who lowered her head and habitually shook her legs up and down."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2611
translate english ecg5_label_89245a9c:

    # "소녀가 나의 손을 계속 붙잡으려던 것도 그런 이유에서였을까."
    "Was it for that reason that the girl kept trying to hold my hand?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:2615
translate english ecg5_label_c0072674:

    # voice "voices/gc119.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“앗.”"
    voice "voices/gc119.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Ah.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2618
translate english ecg5_label_61f543ec:

    # voice ""
    # "다리를 까닥이다 말고 무언가를 발견한 소녀가 짤막한 소리를 내었다."
    voice ""
    "The girl made a short sound as she found something while shaking her legs."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2621
translate english ecg5_label_2bd97e7e:

    # "소녀의 시선이 향한 쪽으로 고개를 돌리자, 그곳에서는 A구역 여기저기서 볼 수 있는 환경 미화 로봇이 소녀를 향해 다가오고 있었다."
    "As I turned my head to where the girl's eyes were, there was an environmental cleaning robot that could be seen everywhere in A district coming towards the girl."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2623
translate english ecg5_label_ed387fe5:

    # "자신을 향해 다가오는 로봇을 바라보며, 소녀는 살짝 난감한 표정을 지어 보였다."
    "Looking at the robot coming towards her, the girl made a slightly awkward expression."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2624
translate english ecg5_label_553aae43:

    # "소녀가 왜 그런 얼굴을 했는지는, 금세 알 수 있었다."
    "I soon found out why she made that face."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2626
translate english ecg5_label_3fed658c:

    # voice "voices/gc120.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“으음…….”"
    voice "voices/gc120.ogg"
    소녀 "'Hmm...'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:2629
translate english ecg5_label_cc176224:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀는 자신을 향해 다가오던 로봇에게 다리를 저으며 이리로 오지 말라는 신호를 보냈지만, 로봇의 시선에 그녀가 보일 리가 없었다."
    voice ""
    "The girl sent a signal to the robot that was approaching her to not come this way by stretching out her leg, but she was not visible in the robot's eyes."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2636
translate english ecg5_label_55054291:

    # "로봇의 움직임이 멈춘 건 소녀와 로봇의 거리가 20cm 정도로 좁혀졌을 때쯤이었다."
    "The robot stopped moving when the distance between the girl and the robot narrowed to about 20cm."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2637
translate english ecg5_label_49cd6d9d:

    # "갑작스레 더듬이가 잘려나간 벌처럼 불규칙하게 움직이기 시작하는 로봇."
    "The robot started to move irregularly like a vulture whose feeler was cut off suddenly."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2640
translate english ecg5_label_ce20189f:

    # "소녀와 처음 대면했던 그날 보았던 것과 똑같은 현상이었다."
    "It was the same phenomenon that I saw the first day I met the girl."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2645
translate english ecg5_label_eb1dd17e:

    # voice "voices/gc121.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“제 주변으로 다가오는 로봇들은 하나같이 저렇게 되어버리더라고요.”"
    voice "voices/gc121.ogg"
    소녀 "\"All the robots that come near me end up like that.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2647
translate english ecg5_label_017e6bac:

    # voice ""
    # "소녀는 마치 이런 상황이 익숙하다는 듯한 반응이었다."
    voice ""
    "The girl reacted as if she was used to this situation."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2651
translate english ecg5_label_917c89ef:

    # "이미 알고 있었구나."
    "She already knew."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2653
translate english ecg5_label_8e487e8b:

    # "자신의 곁에 로봇이 다가오면 이런 일이 일어난다는 걸."
    "That this would happen when a robot came near her."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2655
translate english ecg5_label_875c178f:

    # voice "voices/gc122.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“…… 꼭 살아있을 때 저를 피하던 길고양이 같아요.”"
    voice "voices/gc122.ogg"
    소녀 "\"...It's like the stray cats that avoided me when I was alive.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2657
translate english ecg5_label_896bb9b1:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“다른 건 기억 안 난다면서, 길고양이가 너를 피했다는 건 기억하는 거야?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"You don't remember anything else, but you remember that stray cats avoided you?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2667
translate english ecg5_label_fde7e55c:

    # voice "voices/gc123.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“그러게요.”"
    voice "voices/gc123.ogg"
    소녀 "\"That's true.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2669
translate english ecg5_label_29fab332:

    # voice ""
    # "농담조로 던진 이야기였지만, 소녀는 듣고 보니 정말 그렇다며 무척이나 어이없다는 웃음을 흘렸다."
    voice ""
    "It was a joke, but the girl laughed as if it was really true and absurd."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2673
translate english ecg5_label_fd280060:

    # voice "voices/gc124.ogg"
    # 소녀 "“고양이를 만지려고 할 때마다 정전기가 일었거든요. 지금 로봇들이 저렇게 되는 것도, 제 몸에서 정전기 같은 게 흐르기 때문일지도 몰라요.”"
    voice "voices/gc124.ogg"
    소녀 "\"Every time I tried to touch a cat, static electricity occurred. Maybe the reason why the robots are like that now is because something like static electricity flows from my body.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2684
translate english ecg5_label_b51fff55:

    # voice ""
    # "그 뒤로는 한가한 잡담이 이어졌다."
    voice ""
    "After that, we had a casual chat."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2686
translate english ecg5_label_6484638c:

    # "불규칙한 동선을 그리며 소녀로부터 멀어지던 환경 미화 로봇은 어느새 제기능을 되찾았는지, 바닥에 떨어져 있을 쓰레기를 찾아 나의 시야 밖으로 사라진 뒤였다."
    "The environmental cleaning robot that moved away from the girl with an irregular trajectory seemed to have regained its function, and disappeared out of my sight after finding the trash on the floor."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2692
translate english ecg5_label_d357193b:

    # "신경 쓰이는 것이 하나 생겼다."
    "There was one thing that bothered me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2693
translate english ecg5_label_236ea19a:

    # "소녀가 기억한다는 그 사람."
    "The person that the girl remembered."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2695
translate english ecg5_label_a15d8995:

    # "가족에 대해서조차 아무것도 기억하지 못하는 소녀가 기억할 만한 사람이라면, 분명 그녀에겐 무척이나 소중한 존재가 아니었을까."
    "If he was someone worth remembering for the girl who didn't remember anything about her family, he must have been very precious to her."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2700
translate english ecg5_label_3f2dc34b:

    # "너무 내멋대로 넘겨짚는 건 아닐까 하는 생각도 들었지만, 충분히 그럴 법한 추측이었다."
    "I wondered if I was overinterpreting it too much, but it was a plausible guess."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2701
translate english ecg5_label_7ad03e85:

    # "어쩌면 소녀가 이곳을 떠돌게 된 이유도, 그 사람과 관련된 일일 수도 있고."
    "Maybe the reason why the girl wandered around here was also related to that person."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2705
translate english ecg5_label_e1e35273:

    # "그저 소녀의 소원을 이루어 줄 힌트일 뿐이라고 생각할 수도 있었겠지만, 어째서인지 나는 소녀가 한 말을 신경 쓰고 있었다."
    "I could have thought of it as just a hint to fulfill the girl's wish, but for some reason I was bothered by what the girl said."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2706
translate english ecg5_label_0d61dcbd:

    # "자료를 찾아보는 도중에도 끊임없이 소녀가 이야기했던 존재에 대해 생각하고 있었으니까."
    "I was thinking about the existence that the girl talked about even while I was looking for information."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2722
translate english ecg5_label_4ff63118:

    # 나 "“……?”"
    나 "\"......?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2724
translate english ecg5_label_799b4c1e:

    # "자료를 찾는 도중 태블릿이 울렸다."
    "The tablet rang while I was looking for information."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2725
translate english ecg5_label_359f5d25:

    # "의아한 눈치로 태블릿을 확인하려다 이내 내게 문자를 보낼 사람은 한 명밖에 없다는 것을 떠올린다."
    "I was about to check the tablet with a curious look, but then I remembered that there was only one person who would text me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2726
translate english ecg5_label_acdec395:

    # "예상했던 대로, 메신저함에는 현지의 문자가 언제 봐도 적응하기 힘든 이모티콘과 함께 도착해 있었다."
    "As expected, Hyeonji's text had arrived in the messenger box with emoticons that were hard to get used to no matter how many times I saw them."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2732
translate english ecg5_label_2c4362b6:

    # shnvl_hy "선배! 혹시 지금까지 알아낸 거 있어요? (　{font=fonts/GothicA1-Regular.ttf}ﾟ{/font}д{font=fonts/GothicA1-Regular.ttf}ﾟ{/font})??"
    shnvl_hy "Senpai! Have you found out anything so far? (　{font=fonts/GothicA1-Regular.ttf}ﾟ{/font}д{font=fonts/GothicA1-Regular.ttf}ﾟ{/font})??"

# game/chapter3.rpy:2734
translate english ecg5_label_6b4f572e:

    # "평소엔 이런 표정 짓지도 않으면서, 문면으로 드러나는 감정 변화만큼은 여느 여학생과 비교해도 뒤지지 않는단 말이지."
    "She didn't even make such expressions in person, but her emotional changes in the text were no less than any other female student."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2735
translate english ecg5_label_0685e382:

    # "발신자를 가리고 읽으면 꼭 유미가 썼을 법한 분위기의 문자 메시지인데, 오히려 평소 표정에서 감정 변화가 확연히 드러나는 유미는 문자 메시지에서만큼은 용건만을 전달하는 편이었다."
    "If I hid the sender and read it, it would look like a text message that Yumi would have written, but Yumi, who showed clear emotional changes in her usual expressions, tended to deliver only her purpose in text messages."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2736
translate english ecg5_label_3da1f59c:

    # "태블릿을 만지작대며, 나는 현지에게 간략한 답장을 보냈다."
    "Fiddling with the tablet, I sent Hyeonji a brief reply."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2740
translate english ecg5_label_20d9c427:

    # "‘조금’이라는 답장을 보내기가 무섭게, 곧장 메신저함에 문자가 도착했다는 알림이 나타났다."
    "As soon as I sent the reply 'a little', a notification appeared in the messenger box that a text had arrived."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2741
translate english ecg5_label_097366ae:

    # "무섭다는 말이 이보다 잘 어울릴 수 없는 속도였다."
    "It was a speed that could not be more frightening."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2746
translate english ecg5_label_ed88d559:

    # shnvl_hy "＼＼＼{font=fonts/MarkaziText-Regular.ttf}٩{/font}({font=fonts/Sarabun-Regular.ttf}๑{/font}`^´{font=fonts/Sarabun-Regular.ttf}๑{/font}){font=fonts/MarkaziText-Regular.ttf}۶{/font}//／／ \n알아낸 거 있으면 곧장 연락 준다고 했잖아요?!!"
    shnvl_hy "＼＼＼{font=fonts/MarkaziText-Regular.ttf}٩{/font}({font=fonts/Sarabun-Regular.ttf}๑{/font}`^´{font=fonts/Sarabun-Regular.ttf}๑{/font}){font=fonts/MarkaziText-Regular.ttf}۶{/font}//／／ \nYou said you'd contact me as soon as you found out something?!!\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2754
translate english ecg5_label_632f0b27:

    # "아, 맞다. 그랬었지."
    "Oh, right. I did say that."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2755
translate english ecg5_label_5cf0c361:

    # "화면에는 잔뜩 토라진 듯한 표정의 이모티콘이 줄을 가득 메우고 있었다."
    "The screen was full of emoticons with a crumpled expression."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2756
translate english ecg5_label_03c59b3c:

    # "그나저나, 현지가 저런 표정을 짓는다면 어떤 느낌일까?"
    "By the way, what would it feel like if Hyeonji made that expression?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:2757
translate english ecg5_label_e00424d7:

    # "잠시 그런 생각을 하고 있는데, 또다시 태블릿이 울렸다."
    "I was thinking about that for a moment, when the tablet rang again."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2767
translate english ecg5_label_a0274b18:

    # "이번엔 문자가 아닌 전화였다."
    "This time it was a call, not a text."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2772
translate english ecg5_label_4fc3d3c7:

    # voice "voices/hc1.ogg"
    # 현지 "“뭔가 알아낸 게 있으면 곧장 연락 준다고 했잖아요.”"
    voice "voices/hc1.ogg"
    현지 "\"You said you'd contact me as soon as you found out something.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2774
translate english ecg5_label_b9c872ae:

    # voice ""
    # "전화를 받자마자 들려오는 현지의 목소리는 역시나 평소처럼 차분한 톤이었다."
    voice ""
    "Hyeonji's voice that came as soon as I answered the phone was still calm as usual."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2776
translate english ecg5_label_48695bec:

    # "물론 어딘가 날카로운 음색이 배어있는 것이, 나를 추궁하는 것처럼 들리기도 했지만 말이다."
    "Of course, there was a sharp tone in her voice somewhere, which sounded like she was interrogating me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2777
translate english ecg5_label_25a41d38:

    # "혹시 현지는 방금 보냈던 이모티콘과 같은 표정을 짓고 있는 게 아닐까."
    "Maybe Hyeonji was making the same expression as the emoticon she just sent."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2778
translate english ecg5_label_5e180608:

    # "당장 수화기 너머에 있는 현지의 얼굴을 확인할 수 없는 게 조금 아쉽게 느껴졌다."
    "I felt a little sorry that I couldn't see Hyeonji's face on the other side of the receiver right now."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2780
translate english ecg5_label_718b6af0:

    # 나 "“으음, 그게…….”"
    나 "\"Well, that...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2782
translate english ecg5_label_9b3e9361:

    # "내가 뭐라 변명을 꺼낼 새도 없이 현지는 말을 이어갔다."
    "Before I could say anything to excuse myself, Hyeonji continued to speak."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2787
translate english ecg5_label_4af6a412:

    # voice "voices/hc2.ogg"
    # 현지 "“어쨌거나, 선배. 내일 시간 돼요?”"
    voice "voices/hc2.ogg"
    현지 "\"Anyway, senpai. Do you have time tomorrow?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2789
translate english ecg5_label_25c509ea:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“내일? 시간은 많은데. 그건 갑자기 왜?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Tomorrow? I have plenty of time. But why all of a sudden?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2795
translate english ecg5_label_808d921d:

    # voice "voices/hc3.ogg"
    # 현지 "“왜긴요. 만나서 이야기할 게 있으니까 그렇죠.”"
    voice "voices/hc3.ogg"
    현지 "\"Why? Because I have something to talk to you about when we meet.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2797
translate english ecg5_label_7618b8eb:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“알겠어. 언제 만나는 걸로 할까?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Okay. When do you want to meet?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2799
translate english ecg5_label_b5675f59:

    # voice "voices/hc4.ogg"
    # 현지 "“음…… 내일 한 시에 학교 옥상에서 만나는 걸로 해요.”"
    voice "voices/hc4.ogg"
    현지 "\"Um... Let's meet at the school rooftop at one o'clock tomorrow.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2801
translate english ecg5_label_6e341f25:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“어…….”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Uh...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2806
translate english ecg5_label_b1b58f87:

    # "갑자기 뇌 정지가 왔다."
    "I suddenly had a brain freeze."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2807
translate english ecg5_label_4d47ae5c:

    # "학교 옥상?"
    "The school rooftop?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:2808
translate english ecg5_label_c337ff99:

    # "왜 굳이 학교 옥상인 거지?"
    "Why the school rooftop of all places?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:2812
translate english ecg5_label_20d80c53:

    # 나 "“야, 잠깐만. 꼭 학교 옥상에서 만나야 해?”"
    나 "\"Hey, wait a minute. Do we have to meet at the school rooftop?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2813
translate english ecg5_label_d78cdab1:

    # voice "voices/hc5.ogg"
    # 현지 "“어라, 장소가 신경 쓰이는 거예요?”"
    voice "voices/hc5.ogg"
    현지 "\"Oh, are you bothered by the place?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2817
translate english ecg5_label_2061a436:

    # voice ""
    # "수화기 너머에서 가벼운 웃음소리가 들려왔다."
    voice ""
    "A light laugh came from the other side of the receiver."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2819
translate english ecg5_label_d02c8b19:

    # "나는 전화로 전해지지 않을 정도의 크기로 한숨을 내쉬고는, 아무렇지도 않은 척 대답했다."
    "I sighed a sigh that was not big enough to be heard over the phone, and answered casually."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2821
translate english ecg5_label_4f7a2a17:

    # 나 "“아냐. 괜찮아. 그럼 내일 오후 한 시에 학교 옥상에서 만나는 걸로.”"
    나 "\"No. It's fine. Then let's meet at the school rooftop at one o'clock tomorrow afternoon.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2822
translate english ecg5_label_974fcd91:

    # voice "voices/hc6.ogg"
    # 현지 "“네~ 그럼 그때 봐요, 선배.”"
    voice "voices/hc6.ogg"
    현지 "\"Okay~ See you then, senpai.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2825
translate english ecg5_label_37cd20e7:

    # voice ""
    # "신경이 안 쓰인다면 그건 거짓말이겠지."
    voice ""
    "It would be a lie if I said I didn't care."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2827
translate english ecg5_label_b2d09a93:

    # "전화를 끊으려다 말고, 나는 깜빡한 게 있다며 급히 이야기를 덧붙였다."
    "Before hanging up the phone, I quickly added something that I had forgotten."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2829
translate english ecg5_label_afb535bd:

    # 나 "“아, 그리고 네가 그날 이야기했던 거 있잖아.”"
    나 "\"Oh, and you know what you talked about that day.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2830
translate english ecg5_label_e443d7b9:

    # voice "voices/hc7.ogg"
    # 현지 "“이야기했던 거요?”"
    voice "voices/hc7.ogg"
    현지 "\"What I talked about?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2832
translate english ecg5_label_8f582b69:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“으응, 방학식 날 집에 가는 길에 이야기했던 거. 그 로봇 말인데…….”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Yeah, the thing you talked about on the way home from the holiday ceremony. The robot thing...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2834
translate english ecg5_label_c398e4dd:

    # voice "voices/hc8.ogg"
    # 현지 "“유령 근처에서 로봇들이 오작동하는 게 맞다고 이야기하려는 거죠?”"
    voice "voices/hc8.ogg"
    현지 "\"You mean to say that it's true that robots malfunction near ghosts?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2836
translate english ecg5_label_797f4f58:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“어, 맞아. 어떻게 알았어?”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Yeah, right. How did you know?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2838
translate english ecg5_label_61299f00:

    # voice "voices/hc9.ogg"
    # 현지 "“다 아는 수가 있죠~”"
    voice "voices/hc9.ogg"
    현지 "\"I have a way of knowing everything~\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2841
translate english ecg5_label_81916d36:

    # voice ""
    # "차분하면서도 절제된 웃음소리가 귀를 간지럽힌다."
    voice ""
    "A calm but restrained laugh tickled my ears."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2843
translate english ecg5_label_bdc3d8fe:

    # "자신이 소리 내어 표현할 수 있는 감정은 정확히 여기까지라는 느낌의 웃음소리였다."
    "It was a laugh that felt like it was the exact limit of the emotion she could express out loud."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2844
translate english ecg5_label_76963c08:

    # "‘자세한 이야기는 직접 만난 뒤에’라고 이야기하는 듯하기도 했다."
    "It also seemed like she was saying 'I'll tell you more when we meet in person'."

# game/chapter3.rpy:2846
translate english ecg5_label_0e0dc6f5:

    # 나 "“…… 알겠어. 그럼 내일 봐.”"
    나 "\"...Okay. See you tomorrow.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:2853
translate english ecg5_label_71fb293a:

    # "전화를 끊고 기지개를 켜려는데, 어느새 슬그머니 다가와 있던 소녀와 눈이 마주쳤다."
    "I hung up the phone and tried to stretch, but I met eyes with the girl who had quietly approached me."

