    "As I passed by Hyeonji, I asked her a favor."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3014
translate english ecg5_label_00460be5:

    # 나 "“아, 그리고 방금 있었던 일은 유미한테는 비밀로 해줘. 부탁할게.”"
    나 "\"Oh, and can you keep what just happened a secret from Yumi? I'm asking you.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3017
