    현지 "\"Please tell me why you were sitting on the balustrade.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3041
translate english ecg5_label_8c1a71af:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“으음…….”"
    voice ""
    나 "'Hmm...'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:3044
translate english ecg5_label_bd1683c7:

    # "난감한 듯 고개를 돌리려다 말고, 현지의 눈동자를 읽었다."
    "I tried to turn my head away awkwardly, but I read Hyeonji's eyes."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3045
translate english ecg5_label_126dd072:

    # "질문을 철회할 생각 같은 건 일절 없어 보이는 단호한 눈빛이 현지의 얼굴에서 또렷이 읽혔다."
    "A determined look that showed no sign of withdrawing her question was clearly visible on Hyeonji's face."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3047
translate english ecg5_label_f20222bb:

    # "어쩔 수 없나."
    "I had no choice."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3048
translate english ecg5_label_8d1aaffb:

    # "발걸음의 방향이 바뀌었다."
    "The direction of my steps changed."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3049
translate english ecg5_label_9c7ae7fd:

    # "나는 다시금 난간 쪽으로 향하고 있었다."
    "I was heading towards the balustrade again."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3053
translate english ecg5_label_943fef85:

    # voice "voices/hc21.ogg"
    # 현지 "“잠깐만요. 뭐 하려는 거예요?”"
    voice "voices/hc21.ogg"
    현지 "\"Wait a minute. What are you trying to do?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3055
translate english ecg5_label_bbf5eeb9:

    # voice ""
    # "그런 나를 향해, 현지의 당혹스러운 외침이 들려왔다."
    voice ""
    "I heard Hyeonji's bewildered cry towards me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3057
translate english ecg5_label_3dd6e6a0:

    # "하지만 나는 아랑곳하지 않고선 그대로 몸을 난간에 기대었다."
    "But I ignored her and leaned my body on the balustrade."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3058
translate english ecg5_label_3c6264bf:

    # "별일 아니라는 것처럼."
    "As if it was nothing."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3060
translate english ecg5_label_af8936fb:

    # 나 "“그냥, 이렇게 해야 이야기가 잘 나올 것 같아서.”"
    나 "\"Just, I feel like I can talk better when I do this.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3065
translate english ecg5_label_d38fdd7c:

    # "철제 난간의 차가운 감촉이 등에 닿는다."
    "The cold touch of the metal balustrade touched my back."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3066
translate english ecg5_label_4847cbc2:

    # "차가운 경계선에 맞닿아 있는 나는, 그 경계선 바깥의 것들과 최대한 가까워진 상태이다."
    "Being in contact with the cold boundary, I was as close as possible to the things outside of that boundary."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3067
translate english ecg5_label_481b184f:

    # "난간에 몸을 기댄 채, 나는 현지에게 여태껏 있었던 일들을 설명해주었다."
    "Leaning on the balustrade, I explained to Hyeonji what had happened so far."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3069
translate english ecg5_label_9815ce6b:

    # "과거에서 현재로 오게 된 일부터, 이때까지 과거로 돌아갈 방법을 찾아보기도 했다는 이야기."
    "From the story of how I came from the past to the present, to the story of how I tried to find a way to go back to the past."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3070
translate english ecg5_label_32de4316:

    # "그리고 이러한 노력에도 불구하고 그다지 진전이 없다는 것까지."
    "And despite these efforts, there was not much progress."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3072
translate english ecg5_label_9a45b114:

    # "이야기를 끝내고 현지를 바라보았을 땐, 가볍게 고개를 끄덕이고 있는 현지의 모습이 보였다."
    "When I finished the story and looked at Hyeonji, I saw her nodding lightly."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3073
translate english ecg5_label_472af8c0:

    # "그러던 현지가 옆으로 고개를 홱 돌렸다."
    "Then Hyeonji turned her head to the side."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3074
translate english ecg5_label_90c5bbe7:

    # "시선이 마주치고, 시선을 교차했다."
    "Our eyes met, and crossed."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3076
translate english ecg5_label_0f3af42e:

    # "나는 난간대에 기대어 있던 몸을 일으켰다."
    "I got up from leaning on the balustrade."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3078
translate english ecg5_label_d4c5a89d:

    # 나 "“그럼 됐지? 유미에겐 정말 비밀로 부탁해.”"
    나 "\"Is that all? Please keep it a secret from Yumi.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3085
translate english ecg5_label_9a2cf6af:

    # voice "voices/hc22.ogg"
    # 현지 "“안 돼요.”"
    voice "voices/hc22.ogg"
    현지 "\"No.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3087
translate english ecg5_label_1fbf0303_2:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“…….”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3090
translate english ecg5_label_f9930fc0:

    # "전혀 예상치 못한 반응이었다."
    "It was an unexpected response."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3091
translate english ecg5_label_3c28d808:

    # "앞으로 나아가려던 나는, 여전히 난간대 앞에 멀뚱히 선 채였다."
    "I was still standing in front of the balustrade, trying to move forward."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3095
translate english ecg5_label_e51f9bb4:

    # 나 "“이야기 다 해줬는데. 이러면 약속이랑 다르잖아.”"
    나 "\"I told you everything. This is different from the promise.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3096
translate english ecg5_label_6183dd23:

    # voice "voices/hc23.ogg"
    # 현지 "“하나만 부탁한다고는 안 했는걸요?”"
    voice "voices/hc23.ogg"
    현지 "\"I didn't say I only had one request, did I?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3098
translate english ecg5_label_389095a6:

    # voice ""
    # "그랬었나."
    voice ""
    "Was that so?"

# game/chapter3.rpy:3100
translate english ecg5_label_c6f0bae7:

    # "하지만 어느 쪽이었던지 간에, 속았다는 느낌이 드는 건 당연하다."
    "But either way, it was natural to feel cheated."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3101
translate english ecg5_label_8065f3d9:

    # voice "voices/hc24.ogg"
    # 현지 "“딱 하나만 더 들어주면 정말 이야기 안 할게요.”"
    voice "voices/hc24.ogg"
    현지 "\"Just one more thing and I'll really keep quiet.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3103
translate english ecg5_label_8c1a71af_1:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“으음…….”"
    voice ""
    나 "'Hmm...'"

# game/chapter3.rpy:3106
translate english ecg5_label_bf748d29:

    # "부탁 같은 말이었지만, 사실 내게 달리 방법이 있는 것도 아니었다."
    "It sounded like a request, but in fact I had no other choice."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3107
translate english ecg5_label_21d9ad1b:

    # "선택지가 하나뿐인 게임이라."
    "It was a game with only one option."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3108
translate english ecg5_label_ef579c49:

    # "이런 게임은 별로 안 좋아하는데 말이다."
    "I don't like this kind of game very much."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3110
translate english ecg5_label_baf086c5:

    # 나 "“그래. 무슨 부탁인데.”"
    나 "\"Fine. What's your request?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3112
translate english ecg5_label_6d45eeca:

    # "선심 쓰듯 이야기를 꺼낸 나였지만, 대화를 리드하는 쪽은 현지임에 틀림 없었다."
    "I spoke as if I was doing a favor, but there was no doubt that Hyeonji was leading the conversation."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3113
translate english ecg5_label_d8b6111f:

    # "그렇다고 해도, 직후 현지가 꺼낸 이야기는 내 예상과 완벽히 틀어진 방향을 향하고 있었다."
    "Even so, the story that Hyeonji brought up right after was completely different from what I expected."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3115
translate english ecg5_label_e6b84d37:

    # voice "voices/hc25.ogg"
    # 현지 "“앞으로는 ‘신경 쓰지 마’라는 말, 하기 없기예요.”"
    voice "voices/hc25.ogg"
    현지 "\"From now on, don't say 'don't mind me'.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3117
translate english ecg5_label_2a1ca89e:

    # voice ""
    # "여태껏 맺힌 게 많았다고 이야기하는 듯한 현지의 눈빛이 내게 날아와 꽂혔다."
    voice ""
    "Hyeonji's eyes, as if to say that she had a lot of grudges, flew and stuck to me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3120
translate english ecg5_label_785eb295:

    # voice "voices/hc26.ogg"
    # 현지 "“매번 제가 말 걸려고 할 때마다 신경 쓰지 말라고 했었잖아요.”"
    voice "voices/hc26.ogg"
    현지 "\"Every time I tried to talk to you, you told me not to mind you.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3123
translate english ecg5_label_bb497157:

    # voice "voices/hc27.ogg"
    # 현지 "“같은 동아리 부원인데, 너무한 거 아니에요?”"
    voice "voices/hc27.ogg"
    현지 "\"Isn't that too much for a club member?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3125
translate english ecg5_label_0bc89780:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“아, 으응…… 그렇지만…….”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Ah, um... but...\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3127
translate english ecg5_label_2bf591b2:

    # voice "voices/hc28.ogg"
    # 현지 "“왜 그랬는지는 이제 알았으니까, 앞으로는 제가 신경 써도 받아 줘야 해요?”"
    voice "voices/hc28.ogg"
    현지 "\"Now that I know why you did that, you have to accept me caring about you from now on, okay?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3129
translate english ecg5_label_8fc53323:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“…… 알겠어.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"... Okay.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3132
translate english ecg5_label_313eed97:

    # "묘하게 흘러가는 기류 속에서, 나는 고개를 끄덕일 수밖에 없었다."
    "In the strange flow of the conversation, I had no choice but to nod."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3133
translate english ecg5_label_64eae842:

    # "그 뒤로 몇 마디 이야기를 더 나누긴 했지만, 정확히 기억나는 내용은 머릿속에 얼마 남아 있지 않았다."
    "We exchanged a few more words after that, but I didn't remember much of what we said in my head."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3134
translate english ecg5_label_4ce5561c:

    # "계단을 내려오며 교문을 나설 때쯤이었나."
    "It was around the time when we came down the stairs and left the school gate."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3135
translate english ecg5_label_c410fadf:

    # "집으로 가는 방향이 같다며 나를 따라오던 현지가, 이런 이야기를 했었다."
    "Hyeonji, who followed me saying that she was going in the same direction as home, said this to me."

# game/chapter3.rpy:3136
translate english ecg5_label_4f452c86:

    # voice "voices/hc29.ogg"
    # 현지 "“그리고 과거로 돌아가고 싶다고 했죠?”"
    voice "voices/hc29.ogg"
    현지 "\"And you said you wanted to go back to the past, right?\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3138
translate english ecg5_label_50843019:

    # voice ""
    # 나 "“응.”"
    voice ""
    나 "\"Yeah.\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3143
translate english ecg5_label_68e5f0a2:

    # voice "voices/hc30.ogg"
    # 현지 "“{color=#00ccff}저, 그 일 도와줄 수 있어요.{/color}”"
    voice "voices/hc30.ogg"
    현지 "\"{color=#00ccff}I can help you with that.{/color}\""

# game/chapter3.rpy:3146
translate english ecg5_label_139d94d6:

    # voice ""
    # "회상이 끝자락에 도달했을 때쯤, 옥상 문이 열리는 소리가 들려왔다."
    voice ""
    "When the flashback was about to end, I heard the sound of the rooftop door opening."

